NK067(ju)002:1: // dpal ldan gsang ba snying po'i spyi don gyi bshad
NK067(ju)002:2: pa'i zin bris bla ma'i man ngag don gsal snying
NK067(ju)002:3: po legs bshad rol mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK067(ju)002:5: // gdod ma'i dbyings su rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK067(ju)002:6: rnam par grol las rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun //
NK067(ju)002:7: spro dang bsdu ba'i byed po bcom ldan 'das //
NK067(ju)002:8: kun bzang lha yi lha la dang por 'dud //
NK067(ju)002:9: mtha' yi rtogs pas mi bskyod rdo rje'i thugs //
NK067(ju)002:10: mtha' bral chos dbyings ngang du rtogs gyur pas //
NK067(ju)002:11: mtha' dang dbus med rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor cher //
NK067(ju)002:12: mtha' yas rgyud don 'chad pa'i skyes bu rgyal //
NK067(ju)002:13: rab 'byams bde bar gshegs pa ma lus pa'i //
NK067(ju)002:14: rmad byung thugs kyi gsang ba rdo rje'i mdzod //
NK067(ju)002:15: 'dzin mdzad rgyas sras thu bo gang lags pa //
NK067(ju)002:16: de la dngos po kun gyis phyag bagyi'o //
NK067(ju)002:17: chos dbyings mkha' la thabs shes mkha' lding gis //
NK067(ju)002:18: drangs pa'i lam rgyud shing rta la bskyon nas //
NK067(ju)002:19: rnam grol gling du bde bar 'khrid mdzad pa'i //
NK067(ju)002:20: lam mkhan rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs la 'dud //
NK067(ju)002:21: khyad par gsang bdag drin las gsang chen gyi //
NK067(ju)002:22: bka' babs d+r+wa ma lnga dang rgyal po dzah rgyud don rnam par 'grel la zla bral pa //
NK067(ju)002:23: sgeg rdor sangs rgyas gsang ba rnam gnyis mchod //
NK067(ju)002:24: bsil ldan mkha' la thugs rje'i rta bdun gyis //
NK067(ju)002:25: gsang chen nyi ma 'dren mdzad pad 'byung dang //
NK067(ju)002:26: bi ma mi tra lo chen rma gnyags zung //
NK067(ju)002:27: bka' srol gcig 'dus gnubs chen rnams la 'dud //
NK067(ju)002:28: gangs can ri yi sul du theg mchog gi //
NK067(ju)002:29: 'jigs med chos sgras lta ngan ri dwags kun //
NK067(ju)002:30: skrag mdzad phyogs las rnam rgyal mi'i seng ge //
NK067(ju)002:31: zur gyi rigs 'khrungs mes dbon rnam gsum rgyal //
NK067(ju)002:32: gang gi bka' srol kho nas 'dzin ma'i khyon //
NK067(ju)002:33: khyab mdzad bshes gnyen tshogs dang de las gzhan //
NK067(ju)002:34: legs bshad gtam gyi 'byung gnas rong zom dang //
NK067(ju)002:35: dri med 'od zer rnams la'ang gus phyag 'tshal //
NK067(ju)002:36: khyad par gsang bdag dgongs pa'i gnad ji bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:37: mngon du gyur nas 'gro la gsal mdzad pa //
NK067(ju)002:38: bka' drin mtshungs med gter chen chos kyi rje //
NK067(ju)002:39: byang chub bar du rigs kyi bdag por mchod //
NK067(ju)002:40: dpal ldan rdo rje gsum dngos kun tu bzang //
NK067(ju)002:41: sgyu 'phrul zhi dang khro gar rdo rje sems //
NK067(ju)002:42: spros bsdu'i byed po don gyi dpa' chen po //
NK067(ju)002:43: gsang ba snying por nges pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK067(ju)002:44: gzung 'dzin 'pho ba 'gyur meda bde chen klong //
NK067(ju)002:45: yongs bcings dwangs ma tshe dbang rdo rje'i sku //
NK067(ju)002:46: bde mchoga kun tu bzang dang mi gnyis pa //
NK067(ju)002:47: grub dbang bla ma'i byin rlabs snying la sim //
NK067(ju)002:48: dri bcas brtags gzhir ldan pa ngo bo'i gzhi //
NK067(ju)002:49: sgra dang rtog pa'i mtshan ma nyer zhi yang //
NK067(ju)002:50: dbang po'i yul la 'tshams pa'i phrin las bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:51: nges gsang snying po'i gan mdzod 'di na'o //
NK067(ju)002:52: sh+loo ka gnyis po 'di phyag tsha sprul pa'i sku'i gsung yin /
NK067(ju)002:53: zhes yul mchog dam pa rnams la phyag dang mchod
NK067(ju)002:54: pa brjod pa brtsam par dam bca' ba sngon du
NK067(ju)002:55: btang nas / slob ma'i skabs sgrib sbyong dang nyan dbang 'chad dbang bcas 'gro dgos pa /
NK067(ju)002:57: de yang rna rgyud lung gi phreng ba las //
NK067(ju)002:58: rgyal ba rnams ni 'jig rten byon pa'i tshe //
NK067(ju)002:59: de yis gsungs pa'i lung chen rnams la ni //
NK067(ju)002:60: phyi rol rgol ba ngan pa'ang 'byung srid kyis //
NK067(ju)002:61: dang por srid pa chos kyi lo rgyus smos //
NK067(ju)002:63: rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di nyid kyi lo rgyus cung zad brjod pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK067(ju)002:64: dang po ston pas gsungs tshul dang /
NK067(ju)002:65: de las ji ltar brgyud tshul dang gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:66: dang po ni 'di la bzhed tshul mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig snang ste /
NK067(ju)002:67: slob dpon nyi 'od seng ges ni /
NK067(ju)002:68: 'og min du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus gsang sngags kyi chos gsungs pa'i tshe /
NK067(ju)002:69: de dang dus mtshus par mi yul du mchog gi
NK067(ju)002:70: sprul skus rdo rje gdan du sangs rgyas tshul ma
NK067(ju)002:71: bstan pa'i gong du gsungs pa yin no zhes gsungs
NK067(ju)002:72: te / nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel du de ltar bshad /
NK067(ju)002:73: yang slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje ni /
NK067(ju)002:74: mchog gi sprul sku'i mi yul du thun mong gi
NK067(ju)002:75: theg pa bshad pa dang dus mtshungs par ston pas
NK067(ju)002:76: 'og min du gsungs par bzhed de /
NK067(ju)002:77: des mdzad pa'i 'grel pa spar khab tu de ltar bshad pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:78: don la de gnyis kyang dgongs pa'i gnad gcig pas 'gal ba med kyang /
NK067(ju)002:79: sngon gyi zur pa rnams kyis spar khab kyi lugs
NK067(ju)002:80: ltar mdzad pas 'dir yang re zhig spar khab kyi
NK067(ju)002:82: don la de gnyis 'gal med du 'chad thub ste /
NK067(ju)002:83: gdul bya'i mthong snang gi dbang gis rgyud gzhung gcig
NK067(ju)002:84: la gleng gzhi bshad tshul tha dad pa gzhan las
NK067(ju)002:85: kyang 'byung ste / 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i bshad rgyud las /
NK067(ju)002:86: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te /
NK067(ju)002:87: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtse //
NK067(ju)002:88: 'dzam bu'i gling du grags pa yin //
NK067(ju)002:89: byang chub sems dpa' lha rnams dang //
NK067(ju)002:90: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK067(ju)002:91: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK067(ju)002:92: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK067(ju)002:93: sprul sku 'khor los sgyur ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:94: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK067(ju)002:95: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i dus //
NK067(ju)002:98: gnyis pa de las ji ltar brgyud tshul ni /
NK067(ju)002:100: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK067(ju)002:101: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK067(ju)002:105: gang zag snyan brgyud dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:107: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos 'og min chen po'i
NK067(ju)002:108: gnas su nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor rgyal ba
NK067(ju)002:109: rigs lnga la chos 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa zang
NK067(ju)002:110: thal du gsungs pa ni rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud
NK067(ju)002:111: pa / rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:112: rgyal ba rigs lngas rgyal sras sems dpa' sogs la
NK067(ju)002:113: brjod med rig pa'i gsung dbyangs kyi brdas go bar
NK067(ju)002:114: mdzad pa ni rigs 'dzin brda brgyud /
NK067(ju)002:115: gang zag snyan khung du brgyud pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:116: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor rnams kyi nang nas rigs
NK067(ju)002:117: gsum gyis gdul bya rang rang gi skal pa dang
NK067(ju)002:119: 'jam dpal gyis lha yi gnas su lha grags ldan
NK067(ju)002:120: mchog skyong la bshad de lha'i rig 'dzin rnams la
NK067(ju)002:121: dar bar byas / spyan ras gzigs kyi klu'i gnas
NK067(ju)002:122: su klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad de
NK067(ju)002:123: dar bar byas / dar bar byas / phyag na
NK067(ju)002:124: rdo rjes gnod sbyin gyi gnas su gnod sbyin kun
NK067(ju)002:125: tu bzang po la bshad de dar bar byas pa
NK067(ju)002:126: ni gang zag snyan khung du brgyud pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:127: de'i dus su ston pas las can gyi gdul bya
NK067(ju)002:128: dag pa la gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa gsungs
NK067(ju)002:129: nas lha klu mi'i 'jig rten du gsang thabs kyis
NK067(ju)002:130: spyod pa las / gsang sngags kyi sgra yongs su ma grags te /
NK067(ju)002:132: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK067(ju)002:134: des na re zhig rdo rje theg pa 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab par gzigs nas /
NK067(ju)002:135: rigs can lnga rigs can lnga ni /
NK067(ju)002:139: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK067(ju)002:140: mi'i rig 'dzin li ts+aa bi dri med grags pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:142: dang rgyal po zla bzang sogs la gsungs te /
NK067(ju)002:143: 'jig rten na gsang sngags kyi sgra yongs su grags pa phyis 'byung ba lung bstan te /
NK067(ju)002:144: sdom 'byung gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK067(ju)002:145: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK067(ju)002:146: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK067(ju)002:147: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK067(ju)002:148: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK067(ju)002:149: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK067(ju)002:150: rgyal po dzah zhes bya ba la //
NK067(ju)002:151: bsod nams chen po'i mthus snang ba'i //
NK067(ju)002:152: gsang ba'i bdag pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK067(ju)002:153: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun par ston pa mya ngan
NK067(ju)002:154: las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'das pa
NK067(ju)002:155: na dam pa'i rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga nang du
NK067(ju)002:156: yang dag 'jog pa la gnas pa rang rang gi
NK067(ju)002:157: mngon par shes pas mkhyen te ri ma la ya
NK067(ju)002:158: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtser rdzu 'phrul gyi bya bas
NK067(ju)002:159: 'dus nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad yid la
NK067(ju)002:160: byas te / kye ma kye hud kye ma klong //
NK067(ju)002:161: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK067(ju)002:162: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK067(ju)002:163: zhes sogs gdung tshig nyer gsum bton pas /
NK067(ju)002:164: ston pa rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po nyid
NK067(ju)002:165: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje'i rnam par
NK067(ju)002:166: bstan nas / sngar 'og min du gsungs pa nyid slar yang bzlas te gsungs par dgongs te /
NK067(ju)002:168: sems kyi dkyil 'khor me long bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:169: bstan pa de ltar bdag gis kyang //
NK067(ju)002:170: thog ma tha ma med pa ru //
NK067(ju)002:171: bdag gis dam bca' mi 'dor bas //
NK067(ju)002:172: bskul ba'i don ni gang byung ba //
NK067(ju)002:173: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK067(ju)002:174: zhes rmad du byung ba'i cho 'phrul gyis ri ma la ya'i rtser gshegs te /
NK067(ju)002:175: rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga dang rig 'dzin phal mo
NK067(ju)002:176: che'i 'khor gyi dbus su gsang bdag phyag na rdo
NK067(ju)002:177: rje'i sku'i rnam par bstan nas /
NK067(ju)002:180: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas rnams su grags pa'i gsang ba'i theg pa nyid ston par mdzad cing /
NK067(ju)002:181: de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyis gser
NK067(ju)002:182: gyi glegs bam la beed+aur+ya zhun mas bris nas dgongs
NK067(ju)002:183: pa'i rtsal bdun gyis nam mkha' la sbas so //
NK067(ju)002:184: de'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa ho ra'i rgyal
NK067(ju)002:185: po dzahl rmi ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun rmis te
NK067(ju)002:187: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:188: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:189: chos kyi bgro ba byas pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:190: kun gyis dam par bsgrags pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:191: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:192: rin chen char du babs pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:193: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:194: zhes pa'i rmi ltas dang mthun par rgyud sde'i glegs bam rnams mi yul du dngos su babs te /
NK067(ju)002:195: kri ya'i rgyud rnams w+aa r+aa nas+ai'i yul du babs /
NK067(ju)002:196: u pa ya'i rgyud rnams ri bo bya rkang can dang bsil ba'i tshal du babs /
NK067(ju)002:197: yo ga'i rgyud rnams dur khrod me ri 'bar ba'i rtse mor babs /
NK067(ju)002:198: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams sa ho ra'i yul
NK067(ju)002:199: du rgyal bo chen po dzah'i khang steng du tan+t+ra
NK067(ju)002:200: chen po sde bco brgyad kyi char babs /
NK067(ju)002:201: a nu yo ga'i rgyud rnams sing+ga la'i gling du glegs bam dang bcas te babs /
NK067(ju)002:202: a ti yo ga'i rgyud rnams ni nub phyogs oo
NK067(ju)002:203: d+ai y+aa na'i yul du slob dpon chen po dga'
NK067(ju)002:204: rab rdo rjes dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la dngos
NK067(ju)002:205: su gsan nas glegs bam la bkod par mdzad do
NK067(ju)002:206: // de ltar tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad po /
NK067(ju)002:207: rgyal po dzahs slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza la /
NK067(ju)002:209: des seng ha r+aa dza la /
NK067(ju)002:210: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK067(ju)002:211: des sras mo go ma de w+aa la /
NK067(ju)002:212: des sgeg pa rdo rje dang sangs rgyas gsang ba gnyis la /
NK067(ju)002:213: de gnyis kyis pan chen bi ma la mi tra la /
NK067(ju)002:214: des lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog dang gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra gnyis la /
NK067(ju)002:215: rma rin chen mchog gis gtsug ru rin chen gzhon nu dang gye re mchog skyong gnyis la /
NK067(ju)002:216: de gnyis kas dar rje dpal gyi grags pa dang zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan gnyis la bshad /
NK067(ju)002:217: zhang gis gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la bshad pa ste bka' srol gcig go //
NK067(ju)002:218: yang slob dpon pad+ma dang bi ma la gnyis kas gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la /
NK067(ju)002:219: des sog po dpal gyi ye shes la /
NK067(ju)002:220: des gnubs chen la bshad pas bka' srol gcig go //
NK067(ju)002:221: yang rma gnyags thun mong gi slob ma khu byang
NK067(ju)002:222: chub 'od nas mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis la
NK067(ju)002:223: brgyud de gnubs la bshad pas bka' srol gcig go
NK067(ju)002:224: // de ltar gnubs la brgyud pa'i bka' srol gyi chu bo thams cad 'dus shing /
NK067(ju)002:225: de la thugs zin gyi sras bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:229: sru legs pa'i sgron ma bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)002:231: sras kyi dam pa gcig sras kyi dam pa gcig ni gnubs yon tan rgya matsho'o //
NK067(ju)002:234: de nas rim par brgyud pa'i mthar /
NK067(ju)002:235: nyang ye shes 'byung gnas kyi lha rje zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas la bshad /
NK067(ju)002:236: de la slob ma rtse mo bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:241: lta rje zur chung pa shes rab grags pa rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:244: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs pa byung /
NK067(ju)002:245: zur sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyis zur chur shes rab grags pa la /
NK067(ju)002:246: de la slob ma ka ba bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:248: rdzogs chen gyi ka ba skyo ston sh+aaka ye /
NK067(ju)002:249: mdo'i ka ba yang khyed bla ma /
NK067(ju)002:250: sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK067(ju)002:251: phrin sgrub kyi ka ba mda' tig chos sh+aaka go //
NK067(ju)002:255: dral ma sum cu so gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:256: yus po che mi gnyis la sogs pa byung par grags /
NK067(ju)002:258: sras gsang bdag sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge la /
NK067(ju)002:259: de nas zur gyi rigs las rim par brgyud pa'i mthar /
NK067(ju)002:260: zur chen bkra shis kun dga' /
NK067(ju)002:261: des smyos ston gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub la bstsal /
NK067(ju)002:262: des gter chen chos kyi rgyal po gter bdag gling pa la /
NK067(ju)002:263: des mkhan chen d+har+m+aa sh+r+ai la /
NK067(ju)002:264: des mdo sngags lung rig rab 'byams smra ba'i dbang phyug o rgyan chos grags /
NK067(ju)002:265: des mdo rgyud rgya mtsho'i dbang phyug o rgyan phrin las bstan 'dzin /
NK067(ju)002:266: des rigs brgya'i khyab bdag bka' drin gsum ldan don
NK067(ju)002:267: gyi slad du mtshan nas smos na dpal chos kyi
NK067(ju)002:268: rdo rje 'gyur med kun bzang grub pa'i dbang phyug
NK067(ju)002:269: gam / sbas pa'i grub thob rta mchog dbang gi
NK067(ju)002:270: rnam par rol pa pad+ma gar dbang phrin las rnam
NK067(ju)002:271: gam / rgyal / de nyid kyi bka' drin las
NK067(ju)002:272: bdag sh+aakya'i btsun pa 'gyur med tshe dbang mchog grub
NK067(ju)002:273: nges don bstan 'phel la brgyud pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:274: de la 'dir dang po bshad bya dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:275: 'chad byed kyi chos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:276: ji ltar 'chad pa'i tshul dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:277: dang po bshad bya dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:278: ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK067(ju)002:279: tan+t+ra chen po sde bco brgyad yod pa las /
NK067(ju)002:280: 'di'i grangs la bzhed pa mang yang /
NK067(ju)002:281: rang lugs gter chen bla ma'i dgongs pa la /
NK067(ju)002:282: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK067(ju)002:283: sku'i rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK067(ju)002:284: gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le /
NK067(ju)002:285: thugs gyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK067(ju)002:286: yon tan gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po /
NK067(ju)002:287: phrin las kyi rgyud karma m+aa le dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:289: sgrub pa lag len du ston pa rol pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK067(ju)002:290: he ru ka rol pa'i rgyud /
NK067(ju)002:294: phur pa bcu gnyis pa 'byung ba'i rgyud /
NK067(ju)002:296: spyod pa yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK067(ju)002:301: glang chen rab 'bog gi rgyud dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:303: ma tshang ba kha skong bar byed pa rgyud phyi ma lta bu gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:304: dkyil 'khor gyi las la 'jug pa'i yan lag tu gyur pa rnam snang sgyu d+r+wa dang /
NK067(ju)002:305: dngos grub sgrub pa'i cha rkyen cho ga'i yan lag
NK067(ju)002:306: tu gyur pa 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i
NK067(ju)002:309: de thams cad kyi bsdus don lta bu'i rgyud sde
NK067(ju)002:310: chen po gcig spyi rgyud sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud
NK067(ju)002:313: de'i phyi ma thams cad kyi bsdus don lta bu'i rgyud sde ni /
NK067(ju)002:314: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba
NK067(ju)002:315: snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud kyi
NK067(ju)002:316: rgyal po chen po 'di nyid yin la /
NK067(ju)002:317: de ni bshad bya dam pa'i chos ngos bzung ba de yin /
NK067(ju)002:318: gnyis pa 'chad byed kyi chos ngos bzung ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:319: rgyud dang lung rig man ngag gsum gyis 'chad la /
NK067(ju)002:324: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang snang dbyer med
NK067(ju)002:325: du ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK067(ju)002:326: ba / las tshogs rgyas par ston pa rnam snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK067(ju)002:327: sde snod yongs la khyab par ston pa 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK067(ju)002:328: dkyil 'khor rgyas par ston pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad pa /
NK067(ju)002:329: phrin las rgyas par ston pa bzhi bcu pa /
NK067(ju)002:330: dbang gtso bor ston pa bla ma /
NK067(ju)002:331: yon tan mthar phyin par ston pa brgyad cu pa /
NK067(ju)002:332: dam tshig mchog du ston pa le lag dang brgyad do //
NK067(ju)002:334: rgyud sde 'di yi bshad bya'i gtso bo thabs lam grol lam gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:335: grol lam rim gyis dang gcig car du ston pa ye shes snying po dang /
NK067(ju)002:337: thabs lam rim gyis dang gcig car du ston pa sgyu 'phrul rgya mtsho dang /
NK067(ju)002:338: thal ba ste bshad rgyud sde bzhi'i lung tshad ma'o //
NK067(ju)002:339: de dag gi dgongs 'grel rgya gar gyi bi ma'i khog gzhung dang /
NK067(ju)002:340: sgeg pa rdo rje'i spar khab dang /
NK067(ju)002:341: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim la sogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:342: bod kyi klong chen pa'i phyogs bcu mun sel dang /
NK067(ju)002:343: rong zom pa'i dkon mchog 'grel dang /
NK067(ju)002:344: g.yung ston pa'i rgyud don gsal byed me long /
NK067(ju)002:345: sman lung pa'i snying gi d+ai ka /
NK067(ju)002:346: kahthoga pa dam gtsang byams gsum gyi snying gi t+ai ka sogs so //
NK067(ju)002:348: rgya bod kyi mkhas grub rnams kyi mdzad pa'i man ngag tshad ma /
NK067(ju)002:349: de gnyis dang rjes su 'brel ba'i rig pa tshad ma /
NK067(ju)002:350: de gsum gyi gtan la phab pas rgyud don rtogs par 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)002:352: lung dang rig pa man ngag gi //
NK067(ju)002:353: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal ba'i //
NK067(ju)002:354: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK067(ju)002:357: rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyi mtshan nyid la /
NK067(ju)002:359: 'brel zhing rgyun chags pas dngos grub bsgrub pa'i yan
NK067(ju)002:360: lag thams cad tshang ba phun sum tshogs pa lnga
NK067(ju)002:367: 'brel dang ma tshang med phyir dang //
NK067(ju)002:368: phun sum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK067(ju)002:371: mdo rgyud nas tshig dum bur phyung zhing yid ches su byed pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:372: lung ni yid ches tshig yin te //
NK067(ju)002:373: nyes pa zad pa rdzun gyi tshig /
NK067(ju)002:374: smra bar mi 'gyur rgyu med phyir //
NK067(ju)002:375: nyes zad lung du shes par bya //
NK067(ju)002:376: man ngag gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK067(ju)002:377: tshegs chung ngus don dpag tu med pa rtogs sla ba'i thabs su gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:379: tshegs chung don che thabs dpag med //
NK067(ju)002:380: bya sla dpag dka' man ngag go //
NK067(ju)002:382: ji ltar 'chad pa'i tshul la 'chad tshul mang du yod de /
NK067(ju)002:383: ma h+aa yo ga spyi yi 'chad tshul dang zur lugs kyi 'chad tshul sogs yod pa las /
NK067(ju)002:385: he ru ka gal po'i rgyud las /
NK067(ju)002:386: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyan bdun yang //
NK067(ju)002:387: gleng bslang ba dang sangs rgyas tshul //
NK067(ju)002:388: rgyas bshad mtha' dang bshad pa'i tshul //
NK067(ju)002:389: dbye ba'i rnam pa gang zag snod //
NK067(ju)002:390: bden pa'i dgongs pa shes par bya //
NK067(ju)002:391: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyan bdun gyi sgo nas 'chad de /
NK067(ju)002:393: dri ba dri lan gyi sgo nas 'chad pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:395: rgyud 'di'i ming ni ci zhig bya //
NK067(ju)002:396: rgyud 'di su yi don du mdzad //
NK067(ju)002:397: ces sogs gsungs pa ltar yin /
NK067(ju)002:400: sangs rgyas pa yi tshul bzhi ste //
NK067(ju)002:401: rgyud dang gleng gzhi nges tshig rgyu //
NK067(ju)002:402: zhes gsungs pa ltar tshul bzhi'i sgo nas 'chad de /
NK067(ju)002:403: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang po ni /
NK067(ju)002:404: tshul bzhi'i sgo nas sangs rgyas par 'jig rten du grags te /
NK067(ju)002:405: mi'i rigs rgyud du 'khrungs pas rgyud kyi tshul dang /
NK067(ju)002:406: de la khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung bas gleng gzhi'i tshul dang /
NK067(ju)002:407: rab tu byung nas kyang 'dul sdom bsrung bar nges pas nges tshig gi tshul dang /
NK067(ju)002:408: de ltar bsrungs nas lam la bslab pas rnam grol thob pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir rgyu'i tshul te /
NK067(ju)002:409: tshul bzhi'i sgo nas 'chad par bzhed pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:412: rgyas bshad mtha' ni rnam pa drug /
NK067(ju)002:413: drang don nges don dgongs pa bshad //
NK067(ju)002:414: dgongs min sgra ni ji bzhin pa //
NK067(ju)002:415: ji bzhin ma yin nyid du bshad //
NK067(ju)002:416: ces gsungs pa ltar drang nges gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:419: ji bzhin ma yin pa gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:420: tshig don 'di drug las mi 'da' bas na mtha' drug ces bshad pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:423: tshig spyi sbas dang mthar thug yin //
NK067(ju)002:424: zhes gsungs pa ltar bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:426: yi ge'i 'bru bsnon mtshams la gzhol ba'i bshad pa sgra tshad kyi gzhung dang mthun par 'chad pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:428: sngags lam bde zhing myur ba la mi zhugs par /
NK067(ju)002:429: mdo lam bul zhing dka' thub kyi lam la zhugs par 'gyod na /
NK067(ju)002:430: de dag kyang 'di'i lam stegs yin tshul du 'chad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:431: yang sngags lam gtsang dme med pa khyi phag lta bu dang sbyor sgrol sogs /
NK067(ju)002:432: 'tshe ba chos su smra bas mu stegs kyi chos snyam du 'gyod na /
NK067(ju)002:433: mdo lam du'ang gtsang dmer zhen 'dzin ma spangs na /
NK067(ju)002:434: mnyam nyid kyi don mi mthong ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:435: dge sems kyi spyod pa la 'dzin pa ma zhugs na /
NK067(ju)002:436: gang yang bsod nams kyi tshogs su gsungs te /
NK067(ju)002:437: mi nag mdung thung can bsad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:438: ded dpon gyi bu mor bgrod pa sogs bsod nams 'phel ba'i rgyur song tshul 'chad pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:440: bskyed rim las rgya sogs dang rdzogs rim rtsa rlung
NK067(ju)002:441: thig le'i byed bcings sogs sbas don du 'chad pa'o
NK067(ju)002:443: don dam 'od gsal gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:444: bden gnyis zung 'jug gi gnas lugs mthar thug yin tshul 'chad pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:446: nyan bshad dbye bas rnam pa gnyis //
NK067(ju)002:447: tshogs dang slob ma dag tu 'dod //
NK067(ju)002:449: tshogs bshad ni sgra bzhin pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:450: theg pa thun mong gi spyi don 'chad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:451: slob bshad ni sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:452: nges don mthar thug gi don 'chad par byed pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:455: snod kyi gang zag rnam pa lnga //
NK067(ju)002:457: tsan+dana rin po che yi dpe //
NK067(ju)002:459: ut+pala lta bu'i gang zag dang /
NK067(ju)002:460: pad+ma dkar dmar lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:462: rin po che lta bu'i gang zag lnga'i snod la brtags nas 'chad par byed ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:465: bden pa'i dgongs pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK067(ju)002:466: kun rdzob don dam bshad par gyis //
NK067(ju)002:467: zhes gsungs pa ltar snga ma drug la brten nas
NK067(ju)002:468: rgyud don bden pa gnyis su bsdus te 'chad par
NK067(ju)002:469: byed pa'o // de ltar rgyan bdun gyi 'chad tshul
NK067(ju)002:470: 'di ni rgyud 'di'i 'chad thabs kyi bka' srol ma
NK067(ju)002:471: yin kyang ma h+aa yo ga spyi'i 'chad thabs yin
NK067(ju)002:472: byed pa'o // gsungs / gnyis pa snga rabs pa rnams kyi 'chad tshul ni /
NK067(ju)002:473: mda' ltar rtse mo nas bzung ste 'chad pa zhes
NK067(ju)002:474: bya ba mtshan gyi nang du chos thams cad gzhi
NK067(ju)002:475: lam 'bras gsum du bsdus nas 'chad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:476: mdung ltar sked pa nas bzung ste 'chad pa zhes
NK067(ju)002:477: bya ba le'u lnga pa'i nang du chos thams cad
NK067(ju)002:478: mtshan nyid gsum rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba
NK067(ju)002:479: / rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK067(ju)002:480: lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)002:483: ral gri ltar yu ba nas bzung ste 'chad pa
NK067(ju)002:484: zhes bya ba le'u tha mar chos thams cad snang
NK067(ju)002:485: ba bzhir bsdus nas 'chad pa yin gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:486: gsum pa bka' sde zur pa'i bshad srol ni /
NK067(ju)002:488: rang bzhin dngos po'i gnas tshul /
NK067(ju)002:490: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs tshul /
NK067(ju)002:491: brtse ba'i thugs rje skye tshul /
NK067(ju)002:492: 'gro don ji ltar byed tshul de lnga'i sgo nas 'chad gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:493: 'dir slob dpon chen po bi ma la'i rjes su 'brangs nas 'chad de /
NK067(ju)002:494: bi ma'i khog gzhung gsal sgron las /
NK067(ju)002:495: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK067(ju)002:498: rab la mtshan bstan zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:499: dbang po yang rab la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:501: dbang po 'bring la rgyud kyi spyi don rnam par dbye ba'i don yin /
NK067(ju)002:504: dbang po tha ma la 'bru re re'i sgo nas dkrol te bshad pa'i don yin /
NK067(ju)002:505: dbang rab la rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:507: rab mtshan tha snyad gsum du grags //
NK067(ju)002:508: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK067(ju)002:509: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK067(ju)002:510: skal ba can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:514: dbang rab la bstan pa'i mtshan de la gsum du yod de /
NK067(ju)002:515: sgyu 'phrul snying po zhes pas sgyu 'phrul ni rdo
NK067(ju)002:516: rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes rgyud dang
NK067(ju)002:517: mthun pa'i mtshan / snying po ni /
NK067(ju)002:518: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa zhes man ngag dang mthun pa'i mtshan /
NK067(ju)002:519: lung gi spyi zhes pa ni rgyud lung man ngag
NK067(ju)002:520: mtshan nyid thams cad kyi lung gi spyi lta bur
NK067(ju)002:521: gyur ba'i phyir lung gi mtshan no //
NK067(ju)002:522: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK067(ju)002:523: zhes pas sman pas nad pa'i lag gi rtsa la
NK067(ju)002:524: bltas na lus mgo mjug gi nad ngos zin pa
NK067(ju)002:525: bzhin / dbang rab des kyang rgyud lung man ngag
NK067(ju)002:526: gi mtshan gsum la brten nas rgyud dbu zhabs kyi
NK067(ju)002:527: don thams cad bde blag tu rtogs pa'i don no
NK067(ju)002:528: bzhin / // skal ba can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:530: de skal ldan dbang rab ma gtogs gzhan gyis ni ma yin no //
NK067(ju)002:531: de ltar rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo 'chad
NK067(ju)002:532: pa'i skyes bu gsum gyi mtshan thun mong du bstan
NK067(ju)002:533: pa ni / rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK067(ju)002:534: ba zhes pa'i mtshan la dbye na zur gnyis te
NK067(ju)002:535: pa ni / / rdo rje sems dpa' bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:537: dang po la zur gnyis te rdo rje bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:541: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK067(ju)002:542: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)002:544: rdo rje ni rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa'i stong pa nyid yin la /
NK067(ju)002:545: stong pa nyid la rdo rje zhes bya ste /
NK067(ju)002:547: rdo rje stong pa nyid du bshad //
NK067(ju)002:548: sems dpa' ye shes chen po ste //
NK067(ju)002:549: zhes pas chos thams cad sems su 'dus la sems
NK067(ju)002:550: nyid stong ba nyid la rdo rje zhes brjod pa
NK067(ju)002:551: ni / 'jig rten rdzas rdo rje pha lam zhes
NK067(ju)002:552: pas dngos po gzhan thams cad phar 'joms par nus
NK067(ju)002:553: ni / pa / tshur de'i ngo bo la gzhan gang gis kyang mi tshugs /
NK067(ju)002:554: de bzhin du stong pa nyid kyis mtshan ma'i chos thams cad 'joms par byed la /
NK067(ju)002:555: mtshan ma'i chos kyis stong pa nyid la mi tshugs pa'i phyir rdo rje'i sgras brjod pa yin /
NK067(ju)002:556: de yang rdo rje ni chos bdun dang ldan pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:562: thams cad du thogs pa med pa /
NK067(ju)002:563: thams cad du ma pham pa /
NK067(ju)002:565: zhes bdun ldan du gsungs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:566: gnyis pa sems dpa' zhes pa'i don ni /
NK067(ju)002:567: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK067(ju)002:568: rang rig byang chub sems nyid do //
NK067(ju)002:570: de yang sems dpa' zhes pa sa t+wa'i sgra las don drug tsam du 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)002:577: 'dir brtan bsdus rtogs gsum la 'jug pa'i skabs yin te /
NK067(ju)002:578: gong gi shes rab stong pa nyid de'i snang cha
NK067(ju)002:579: thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes yin la
NK067(ju)002:580: / de dang shes rab stong pa nyid zung du
NK067(ju)002:581: 'jug pa'i sems nyid snang stong gnyis med rang byung
NK067(ju)002:582: gi ye shes de sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK067(ju)002:583: bar du rang bzhin la bzang ngan med cing /
NK067(ju)002:584: mi 'gyur bar gnas pas na brtan pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bshad de /
NK067(ju)002:586: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:587: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK067(ju)002:590: sems nyid rang byung ye shes de'i ngos nas gzhal
NK067(ju)002:591: na 'khor ba dang myang 'das zhes pa'i bzang ngan
NK067(ju)002:592: gnyis tha dad du ma grub par sems nyid de'i
NK067(ju)002:593: klong du mnyam pa nyid du bsdus pa ni bsdus
NK067(ju)002:596: gnas lugs la 'khor 'das gnyis bzang ngan med kyang /
NK067(ju)002:597: snang lugs la bzang ngan ltar snang bas rnam grol
NK067(ju)002:598: don gnyer gyi gang zag gis lam thabs grol gnyis
NK067(ju)002:599: la 'bad pas sems sangs rgyas su rtogs pa de
NK067(ju)002:600: la rtogs pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' 'am 'bras bu'i
NK067(ju)002:601: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:602: des rgyud la rdo rje sems dpa' zhes btags pa'i don song /
NK067(ju)002:603: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo la rdo rje sems dpa' zhes btags pa'i don ni /
NK067(ju)002:604: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de nyid ngo bo mtshan med stong pa nyid yin kyang /
NK067(ju)002:605: sems can gyi blo ngor rig pa nyid ye shes
NK067(ju)002:606: kyi 'khor lo mtshan ma'i phyag rgyar snang ba yin
NK067(ju)002:608: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK067(ju)002:612: tshogs lam du mos spyod kyi lha sku /
NK067(ju)002:613: sbyor lam du rlung sems kyi lha sku /
NK067(ju)002:614: mthong lam du 'od gsal gyi lha sku /
NK067(ju)002:615: sa gnyis pa nas bcu pa'i bar slob pa'i zung 'jug gi lha sku /
NK067(ju)002:616: sangs rgyas kyi sar mi slob pa'i zung 'jug gi
NK067(ju)002:617: lha sku gtso 'khor gyi tshul du snang ba rnams
NK067(ju)002:618: la'ang rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan du btags pa yin
NK067(ju)002:619: / 'chad pa'i skyes bu la rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan btags pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:620: spyir rgyud 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga ste /
NK067(ju)002:621: 'dir ston pa kun tu bzang po'i mdun na bzhugs
NK067(ju)002:622: pa'i thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo
NK067(ju)002:623: rje mi bskyod pa la yang de ltar du grags
NK067(ju)002:624: so // des mtshan gyi zur dang po rdo rje sems dpa'i bshad pa song /
NK067(ju)002:625: gnyis pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes pa'i don ni /
NK067(ju)002:627: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i don //
NK067(ju)002:628: sgyu 'phrul zhes ni bzhir bshad do //
NK067(ju)002:630: dang po rtogs tshogs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:631: rgyu 'byung ba lnga sgyu ma ltar snang ba ris su ma chad pa /
NK067(ju)002:633: phung po lnga ste 'byung ba lnga la sgyu ma dang /
NK067(ju)002:634: phung po lnga la 'phrul pa de gnyis ngo bo
NK067(ju)002:635: bdag gcig gis 'brel pa la d+r+wa ba zhes pa'i
NK067(ju)002:637: gnyis pa nges don sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:638: stong pa nyid ni chos thams cad ma 'gags pa'i 'char gzhi sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:639: de'i snang cha thabs rig pa rang byung gi ye shes zung du 'jug pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:640: de'i phyir stong pa nyid la sgyu ma /
NK067(ju)002:641: rig pa'i ye shes la 'phrul ba /
NK067(ju)002:642: de gnyis zung du 'jug pa la d+r+wa ba zhes btags so //
NK067(ju)002:643: gsum pa drang don brda'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:644: nges don gyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba de nyid rtogs pa 'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:645: de'i mtshon byed lha yab yum zung du 'jug pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:646: stong pa nyid mtshon byed lha yum /
NK067(ju)002:647: rig pa'i ye shes mtshon byed lha yab /
NK067(ju)002:648: zung 'jug mtshon byed lha yab yum 'khril sbyor du bzhugs pas na /
NK067(ju)002:649: yab la sgyu 'phrul yum la d+r+wa ba zhes bshad do //
NK067(ju)002:650: bzhi pa lha rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:651: lha'i ngo bo rtog tshogs kyi rang bzhin du 'phrul pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:652: rtog tshogs kyi rang bzhin lhar 'phrul pas na lha
NK067(ju)002:653: rtog dbyer med kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bshad
NK067(ju)002:654: do // gnyis pa che ba la mtshan du btags pa lung gi mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)002:656: so sor ston pa rgya mtsho'i rgyud //
NK067(ju)002:658: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK067(ju)002:659: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK067(ju)002:660: zhes pas 'dir ston zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:661: ston pas gsungs pa'i chos zab cing /
NK067(ju)002:662: gting dpag dka' ba rgya mtsho lta bu /
NK067(ju)002:663: tshig rgya che zhing don mtha' yas pa de thams
NK067(ju)002:664: cad rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid kyi
NK067(ju)002:665: nang du rdzogs par ston pas na 'dir ston zhes
NK067(ju)002:666: bshad de / sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa las /
NK067(ju)002:667: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK067(ju)002:668: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK067(ju)002:669: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK067(ju)002:670: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK067(ju)002:673: bstan pa dang theg pa'i don ma lus pa rgyud
NK067(ju)002:674: kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid las 'phros te
NK067(ju)002:675: ston pas na 'dis ston zhes bshad de /
NK067(ju)002:677: phyogs bcu rnams su rab grags pa //
NK067(ju)002:678: gsang ba snying po las 'phros te //
NK067(ju)002:681: theg pa'i sgo gang nas zhugs kyang mthar thug theg
NK067(ju)002:682: pa 'di las mi 'da' bas theg pa gzhan thams
NK067(ju)002:683: cad 'di nyid kyi lam stegs kyi tshul du gsungs
NK067(ju)002:685: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK067(ju)002:686: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK067(ju)002:688: don de rnams kyi phyir na /
NK067(ju)002:689: rgyud 'di la lung gi spyi zhes bshad do //
NK067(ju)002:690: de yang mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi yin pas /
NK067(ju)002:691: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin te /
NK067(ju)002:692: rgya ma las kyi lung mtshan nyid sde gsum /
NK067(ju)002:693: ye shes lha'i lung phyi rgyud sde gsum /
NK067(ju)002:694: bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung nang rgyud sde gsum /
NK067(ju)002:695: de thams cad kyi lung gi spyir 'gyur pas na lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin no //
NK067(ju)002:696: gsum pa man ngag gi mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)002:697: de la glegs bam gyi klad du bkod pa'i mtshan la /
NK067(ju)002:698: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:701: rang bzhin gsang bzhes bya la //
NK067(ju)002:702: che ba zhes bya snying po'i don //
NK067(ju)002:703: de kho na nyid mtshan nyid de //
NK067(ju)002:704: nges pas nges don mdor bstan pa //
NK067(ju)002:706: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i don bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)002:707: dang po gsang ba la rang bzhin gyi gsang ba /
NK067(ju)002:709: sbas pa'i gsang ba gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:711: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud /
NK067(ju)002:712: sems nyid gnas lugs de bzhin nyid rang la rang chas su yod kyang /
NK067(ju)002:713: dbul bo'i khyim gyi sa 'og gi gter ltar ma mthong bas na rang bzhin gyi gsang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:715: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin yin tshul mdo rgyud du ma nas gsungs kyang /
NK067(ju)002:716: rang sems sangs rgyas yin pa bor nas sangs rgyas
NK067(ju)002:717: gzhan du 'tshol ba ni rang gi rang la gab
NK067(ju)002:718: ste gnas pa'o // sbas pa'i gsang ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:719: gsang sngags kyi lta spyod zab mo snod min gyi
NK067(ju)002:720: mi rtogs par bya ba'i phyir sbas pa'i gsang pa'o
NK067(ju)002:721: // bi ma las mi bstan pa'i gsang ba dang bzhir bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)002:722: bsdu na rang bzhin gyi gsang ba gab pa'i khong su 'dus /
NK067(ju)002:723: mi bstan pa ni sbas pa'i nang du 'dus pas gab spas gnyis su 'du la /
NK067(ju)002:725: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par /
NK067(ju)002:726: sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel te /
NK067(ju)002:728: gnyis pa snying po'i don ni /
NK067(ju)002:730: pa ra zhes pa gcig las du ma 'phro ba'i gzhi lta bur 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)002:731: sems nyid 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i 'phro gzhi yin zhing /
NK067(ju)002:732: de ston byed kyi rgyud 'di yang bstan pa dang
NK067(ju)002:733: rgyud thams cad kyi 'byung khungs sam 'phro gzhir gyur
NK067(ju)002:735: hri da ya zhes pa srog gam snying ltar gces spras su byed pa'i don la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)002:736: sangs rgyas mi bsgrub na phar zhog /
NK067(ju)002:737: bsgrub na theg pa'i sgo gang nas zhugs kyang /
NK067(ju)002:738: mthar thug theg pa 'di la 'jug dgos pas /
NK067(ju)002:739: theg pa gzhan thams cad kyi srog lta bu yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:740: gar+b+ha zhes pa shun pa'i nang gi snying po lta bu la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)002:741: chos thams cad kyi dbus na gnas pa'i snying po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:742: gsum pa de kho na nyid kyi don ni /
NK067(ju)002:744: lam gyis gzhi yi don nyams su blangs pas 'bras bu 'byung ba la mi bslu ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:745: gzhi 'bras lto 'byor bas ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid ces bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:746: bzhi pa nges pa'i don ni /
NK067(ju)002:747: skal dman gyi gdul bya drang ba'i thabs tsam du bstan pa ma yin par /
NK067(ju)002:748: skal ldan dbang rno rnams la rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i
NK067(ju)002:749: mthar thug thun mong ma yin par bstan pas na
NK067(ju)002:750: nges pa'o // de yan chad kyis dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa de song /
NK067(ju)002:751: gnyis pa dbang po 'bring po rnams la rgyud kyi
NK067(ju)002:752: spyi don rnam par dbye bas bshad pa la don
NK067(ju)002:753: gyi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:754: tshig gi rnam grangs rnam par dbye ba gnyis kyi dang po la'ang lnga ste /
NK067(ju)002:759: 'khor la gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa dang lnga las /
NK067(ju)002:762: ston pa la sogs rab dbye ba //
NK067(ju)002:763: phun sum tshogs pa lngar brjod do //
NK067(ju)002:767: 'khor gang dang lhan cig tshogs pa'i tshe /
NK067(ju)002:768: rgyud don 'byung nges pas gleng gzhi zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:770: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:771: thun mong gi gleng gzhi gnyis las dang po ni /
NK067(ju)002:772: nang thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar nas bshad rgyud rgya mtshos bshad pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:773: gsang ba 'og sgo dang sbyar nas bshad rgyud thal bas bshad pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:777: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK067(ju)002:778: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK067(ju)002:779: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK067(ju)002:780: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK067(ju)002:781: ye shes myong bas bsdus par bshad //
NK067(ju)002:782: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes par //
NK067(ju)002:783: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK067(ju)002:784: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK067(ju)002:785: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK067(ju)002:787: de la phun sum tshogs pa lnga yi sgo nas 'chad de /
NK067(ju)002:789: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK067(ju)002:791: rkang pa dang po gnyis kyis gnas phun sum tshogs pa bstan /
NK067(ju)002:792: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i dbus na rtsa 'dab brgyad yod pa /
NK067(ju)002:794: mdun gyi rtsa gsum chos nyid skye ba med pa
NK067(ju)002:795: 'char ba'i las byed pas chos nyid kyi rtsa zhes
NK067(ju)002:796: bya / dbyibs mdog zlum po dkar po'i rnam pa /
NK067(ju)002:797: g.yas kyi gcig ni ye shes 'char ba'i las byed pas ye shes kyi rtsa /
NK067(ju)002:798: dbyibs mdog gru bzhi ser po /
NK067(ju)002:799: g.yon na gcig ni yon tan 'char ba'i las byed pas yon tan gyi rtsa /
NK067(ju)002:800: dbyibs mdog zla gam dmar po'i rnam par gnas pa /
NK067(ju)002:801: rgyab na gsum ni gnyid rmugs kyi las byed pas rang rgyud kyi rtsa zhes bya /
NK067(ju)002:802: dbyibs gru gsum dmar nag gi rnam par gnas pa /
NK067(ju)002:803: e sogs las bzhi'i zhi rgyas dbang drag /
NK067(ju)002:804: dbyibs can de ni don dam 'od gsal ye shes kyi bzhugs gnas yin pas gnas so //
NK067(ju)002:805: gnyis pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:806: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK067(ju)002:807: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK067(ju)002:809: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i dbus na dwangs ma ched po lnga bzhugs te /
NK067(ju)002:810: sa'i dwangs ma rtsa dar dkar gyi skud pa lta bu rta rnga bcu gshags tsam /
NK067(ju)002:811: de'i dbus na chu'i dwangs ma rgya mtshal cog la'i khu ba lta bu /
NK067(ju)002:812: de'i dbus na me'i dwangs ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam pa /
NK067(ju)002:813: de'i dbus na rlung gi dwangs ma gser sa 'og
NK067(ju)002:814: na yod pa'i rlabs pa nam mkha' la rgyu ba
NK067(ju)002:815: tsam / de'i dbus na nam mkha'i dwangs ma bar snang go 'byed pa'i rnam par gnas pa /
NK067(ju)002:816: de ltar dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi dbus na ye
NK067(ju)002:817: shes snying po'i thig le stong gsal 'gags med yi
NK067(ju)002:818: ge wam dbyibs kyi rnam par gnas pa de ni
NK067(ju)002:819: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:820: de nyid mar me gsal byed gzhan la ltos mi
NK067(ju)002:821: dgos pa ltar rang gis rang la bde ba gsal
NK067(ju)002:822: bar ston pas na ston pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:824: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK067(ju)002:825: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK067(ju)002:826: mi shigs thig le bde chen po //
NK067(ju)002:827: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK067(ju)002:828: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK067(ju)002:831: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK067(ju)002:832: rtog pa thams cad yang dag spangs //
NK067(ju)002:833: dngos po kun la khyab pa po //
NK067(ju)002:834: lus gnas lus las ma skyes pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:836: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK067(ju)002:837: ma nu yid sogs rnam shes bzhi //
NK067(ju)002:838: ye shes myong bas bsdus par bshad //
NK067(ju)002:839: ces pas yid la sogs pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad de /
NK067(ju)002:840: mdun chos nyid kyi rtsa la kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK067(ju)002:841: g.yas ye shes kyi rtsa la yid kyi rnam shes /
NK067(ju)002:842: g.yon yon tan gyi rtsa la nyon yid kyi rnam shes /
NK067(ju)002:843: rgyab rang rgyud kyi rtsa la sgo lnga'i rnam shes te /
NK067(ju)002:844: tshogs brgyad po des ye shes lnga nyams su myong ba'i cha nas 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:845: bzhi pa chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:846: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes par //
NK067(ju)002:847: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK067(ju)002:848: zhes pas steng sgo'i lam nyams su myong ba'i bde
NK067(ju)002:849: gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can
NK067(ju)002:850: rgyud la skyes pa de nyid /
NK067(ju)002:851: pa ra m+aar+tha zhes pa'i sgra don dam pa don
NK067(ju)002:852: zab mo gnas lugs kyi chos nyid de chos phun
NK067(ju)002:853: sum tshogs pa'o // lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:854: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK067(ju)002:855: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK067(ju)002:857: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs can rgyud la skyes pa
NK067(ju)002:858: de'i tshe snga phyir 'dzin pa'i rtog pa thams cad
NK067(ju)002:859: dang bral ba'i bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i dus de
NK067(ju)002:860: ni dus phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:861: gnyis pa gsang ba ltar 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad rgyud thal bas bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:862: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK067(ju)002:863: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs su gnas //
NK067(ju)002:864: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK067(ju)002:865: wam yig thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:866: ma d+aa ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK067(ju)002:867: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK067(ju)002:868: gsal ba'i go bar bshad pa 'dod //
NK067(ju)002:869: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK067(ju)002:870: ya na theg chen 'di yin te //
NK067(ju)002:871: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK067(ju)002:872: n+aa ma de ming zhes byar 'dod //
NK067(ju)002:874: dang po gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:876: es mtshon pa'i yum gyi mkha' sgo gru gsum /
NK067(ju)002:879: dbyings phyug gi sna rtse zlum po ste las bzhi'i
NK067(ju)002:880: dbyibs can de ni gsang ba'i ston 'khor bzhugs pa'i
NK067(ju)002:882: gnyis pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:883: skad ces gsal byed las ming can /
NK067(ju)002:884: wam yig thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:886: yab kyi rdo rje nor bu'i dbus su rtsa sa
NK067(ju)002:887: ya phrag bcu gsum gyi bcud 'dus pa kun rdzob
NK067(ju)002:888: kyi thig le yi ge wam dbyibs kyi rnam par
NK067(ju)002:889: gnas pa des / yab yum gnyis ka'i rgyu la bde ba gsal bar ston pa'i phyir ston pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:890: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:891: ma d+aa ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK067(ju)002:892: lus can rnam shes de dag la //
NK067(ju)002:893: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK067(ju)002:894: ces pas ma d+aa na sdom byed /
NK067(ju)002:895: ma nu yid de 'du shes gsum 'du shes gsum ni /
NK067(ju)002:896: bdag nyid lha yab dang rig ma yum du sgom pa ni lha'i 'du shes /
NK067(ju)002:897: mkha' gsang rdo rje pad+mara sgom pa sngags kyi 'du shes /
NK067(ju)002:898: thabs 'di la brten nas bde ba chen po'i ye
NK067(ju)002:899: shes bsgrub par bagyi'o snyam pa ni chos kyi 'du
NK067(ju)002:901: ldan gyis mtshan rtog sdom par byed pa'i gsang ba'i
NK067(ju)002:902: rnam shes kyis reg bde nyams su myong bar byed
NK067(ju)002:904: bzhi pa chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:905: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK067(ju)002:906: ya na theg chen 'di yin te //
NK067(ju)002:908: thabs bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong bya /
NK067(ju)002:909: sems lnga rdzogs pa'i dga' ba bcu drug gi ye
NK067(ju)002:910: shes de ni rnam thar bzhi ldan gyi rang bzhin
NK067(ju)002:911: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi chos so //
NK067(ju)002:912: lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:913: dus ni bsam gyi mi khyab dus //
NK067(ju)002:915: ye shes de nyams su myong ba'i tshe dus 'di
NK067(ju)002:916: zhes mtshon du med pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK067(ju)002:917: dus so // n+aa ma de ming zhes byar 'dod //
NK067(ju)002:919: phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i mjug sdud de ston pa
NK067(ju)002:920: phun sum tshogs pa zhes bya'o zhes pa la sogs
NK067(ju)002:921: pa'i don no // gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng gzhi la gsum ste /
NK067(ju)002:924: sprul sku'i gleng gzhi dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:926: rgyud 'di nyid kyi le'u dang pos ston te /
NK067(ju)002:927: de la phun sum tshogs pa lnga yod pa las /
NK067(ju)002:928: dang po chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:929: 'di skad bshad pa zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:931: rgyud don ma lus pa'i mtshon byed de /
NK067(ju)002:932: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don sdud pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:933: de yang ston 'khor dbyer med pa'i bshad pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:935: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste //
NK067(ju)002:936: 'chad dang nyan pa'ang nga nyid yin //
NK067(ju)002:938: gnyis pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:940: 'di ni longs sku'i gleng gzhi yin pas /
NK067(ju)002:941: dus res 'ga' ba gcig gi nges pa las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:942: rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor chos gsungs pa'i dus yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:943: gsum pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK067(ju)002:944: ston pa'i rang bzhin dang ngo bo gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:946: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das /
NK067(ju)002:948: phyogs bcu'i dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK067(ju)002:951: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dang /
NK067(ju)002:952: so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK067(ju)002:954: de la rang bzhin bdun dang ldan pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:955: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:956: yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:957: ye shes mtha' dbus dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:958: 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad kyang ngo bo bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:959: mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:960: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:961: dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin dang bdun no //
NK067(ju)002:963: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:967: de yang spyir ta th+aa ga ta zhas pa'i sgra las /
NK067(ju)002:973: 'di ni chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi don la
NK067(ju)002:974: sgrib byed kyi zhen pa dang bral bas nar son
NK067(ju)002:975: cing / de'i ngo bo mngon du gyur pas na gshegs pa zhes brjod pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:977: yon tan ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:979: yang dag par rdzogs pa zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:980: rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo bo la spang bya ma grub pas /
NK067(ju)002:981: ma nor mi 'gyur mi bslu ba'i yang dag pa'i
NK067(ju)002:982: chos nyid de'i klong na 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK067(ju)002:983: shes kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs par rang snang ba'i phyir
NK067(ju)002:984: spangs thob bral ba'i don yin no //
NK067(ju)002:986: ye shes mtha' dbus bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:989: sgrib bral gyi ye shes de nyid mtha' dbus med par brdal ba'i rang bzhin yin cing /
NK067(ju)002:991: gnyid sad pa ltar sangs pa dang pad+ma kha phye ba ltar rgyas pa'i don la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)002:993: ma rig gnyid las sangs ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:994: shes bya la yang blo rgyas phyir //
NK067(ju)002:998: 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad cing ngo bo bstan du med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:1001: sgrib pa'i cha shas phra mo tsam yang mi gnas
NK067(ju)002:1002: pas bdud bzhi bcom zhing che ba'i yon tan gyi
NK067(ju)002:1003: 'bras bu la mnga' mdzad cing ngo bo bstan du
NK067(ju)002:1005: 'khor 'das srid zhi gnyis kyi mtha' la mi gnas pa'i don gyis 'das pa yin te /
NK067(ju)002:1007: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdengs kyis bcom /
NK067(ju)002:1008: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK067(ju)002:1009: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK067(ju)002:1011: bdud bzhi nyon mongs pa'i bdud /
NK067(ju)002:1017: nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor dag pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK067(ju)002:1018: de dag pas phung po lnga gzugs /
NK067(ju)002:1024: rigs lnga'i rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK067(ju)002:1030: ngo bor gnas gyur pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK067(ju)002:1031: de'i tshe dag pa lha dang ma dag pa rnam
NK067(ju)002:1032: rtog gi 'ching ba las grol bas 'dod lha'i bar
NK067(ju)002:1033: chad kyis mi tshugs pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK067(ju)002:1034: sems nyid skye 'chi las grol bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1036: mnyam pa nyid mngon du mdzad cing spyod yul dang bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:1038: longs spyod chen po zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:1039: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi don mdzad kyang 'khor
NK067(ju)002:1040: 'das kyi chos thams cad la spyad bya spyod byed
NK067(ju)002:1041: du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa thams cad dang bral bar
NK067(ju)002:1044: gcig dang du ma bral ba'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:1046: phyogs bcu phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og bcu /
NK067(ju)002:1048: dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid /
NK067(ju)002:1050: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku
NK067(ju)002:1051: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga la lnga lngar
NK067(ju)002:1052: phye ba'i 'bras chos nyer lngar snang bas gcig gi
NK067(ju)002:1054: 'bras chos nyer lnga po rang byung gi ye shes su 'dus /
NK067(ju)002:1055: rigs lnga po yang drug kun tu bzang po rdo rje 'chang chen /
NK067(ju)002:1056: par 'dus pas du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba yin /
NK067(ju)002:1058: dus gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:1060: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad
NK067(ju)002:1061: dang so so ma yin tha mi dad pa dbyer
NK067(ju)002:1064: rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po de nyid khams
NK067(ju)002:1065: gsum dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi
NK067(ju)002:1066: chos thams cad dang so so ma yin tha mi
NK067(ju)002:1067: dad dbyer med pa'i don yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1068: gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1069: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa sogs nas zhal thal
NK067(ju)002:1070: le ba dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pa'i bar
NK067(ju)002:1071: gyis bstan / de yang sngar ston pa'i rang bzhin
NK067(ju)002:1072: bshad pa de nyid gdul bya la sku gsung thugs
NK067(ju)002:1073: kyi mtshan mar snang ba'i rnam 'gyur gyi cha la
NK067(ju)002:1075: de la ston pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags /
NK067(ju)002:1076: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtags /
NK067(ju)002:1077: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i don rtags /
NK067(ju)002:1078: rnam thar gsum dang ldan pa'i don rtags dang bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:1079: dang po chos sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags ni /
NK067(ju)002:1080: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa thams cad du zhal
NK067(ju)002:1081: thal le bar gsal zhing gzugs sku'i yon tan mi
NK067(ju)002:1082: 'gag pa'i ye shes kyi sku yin pa'i phyir ro
NK067(ju)002:1083: // gnyis pa longs sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags ni /
NK067(ju)002:1084: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:1085: de la thun mong dang khyad par gyi mtshan dpe gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:1087: dbu gtsug tor sogs mtshan so gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:1088: sen mo zangs mdog sogs dpe byad brgyad cu ste /
NK067(ju)002:1089: mtshan bzang bo sum cu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK067(ju)002:1091: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK067(ju)002:1092: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:1093: phyag ni zhabs bcas 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags //
NK067(ju)002:1094: 'di yi sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:1095: sor mo ring dang rting yangs sku che drang //
NK067(ju)002:1096: zhabs 'bur mi mngon spu ni gyen du phyogs //
NK067(ju)002:1097: byin pa ee na ya'i 'dra phyag ring mdzes //
NK067(ju)002:1098: 'doms kyi lba ba sbubs su nub pa'i mchog /
NK067(ju)002:1099: pags pa gser mdog pags pa srab pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1100: spu ni re re nas g.yas legs 'khrungs dang //
NK067(ju)002:1101: zhal mdzod spus brgyan ro stod seng ge'i 'dra //
NK067(ju)002:1102: 'di yi dpung ba'i mgo zlum thal gong rgyas //
NK067(ju)002:1103: 'di la ro mi zhim pa'ang ro mchog snang //
NK067(ju)002:1104: sku ni ny+aa gro ta ltar chu zheng gab //
NK067(ju)002:1105: gtsug tor dbur ldan ljags ring mdzes pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1106: tshangs dbyangs 'gram pa seng ge'i 'dra dang tshems //
NK067(ju)002:1107: shin tu dkar dang tshad mnyam thags bzang dang //
NK067(ju)002:1108: grangs ni bzhi bcu tham pa tshang ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:1109: spyan ni mthon mthing spyan rdzi ba mchog gi //
NK067(ju)002:1110: 'dra ba 'di dag gsum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK067(ju)002:1112: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni /
NK067(ju)002:1113: de nyid las thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK067(ju)002:1114: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK067(ju)002:1115: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:1116: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK067(ju)002:1117: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK067(ju)002:1118: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK067(ju)002:1119: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK067(ju)002:1120: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khril bag chags //
NK067(ju)002:1122: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK067(ju)002:1123: mtshan ni yongs su rdzogs pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1124: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK067(ju)002:1125: gom snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK067(ju)002:1126: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK067(ju)002:1127: sku zhum med dang rgyas pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1128: shin tu grims pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK067(ju)002:1129: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK067(ju)002:1130: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1131: dku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK067(ju)002:1132: phyang nge ba dang lte ba ni //
NK067(ju)002:1133: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:1134: kun nas lta na sdug pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1135: kun spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK067(ju)002:1136: sme ba gnag bag med pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1137: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'jam dang //
NK067(ju)002:1138: phyag ris mdangs yod zab ring dang //
NK067(ju)002:1139: zhal ni ha cang mi ring dang //
NK067(ju)002:1140: mchu ni bim+pa ltar dmar dang //
NK067(ju)002:1141: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1142: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK067(ju)002:1143: gsung mnyen 'jam dang mche ba zlum //
NK067(ju)002:1144: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1145: byin gyis phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK067(ju)002:1146: mchog tu dag pa dag dang ni //
NK067(ju)002:1147: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /
NK067(ju)002:1149: smin tshugs ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1150: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1151: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan mnyam dang //
NK067(ju)002:1152: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1153: dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1154: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK067(ju)002:1155: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK067(ju)002:1157: mi bshor dri zhib skyes bu yi //
NK067(ju)002:1158: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1159: dpal gyi be'u dang bkra shis ni //
NK067(ju)002:1160: g.yung drung 'khyil bas brgyan pa ste //
NK067(ju)002:1161: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK067(ju)002:1163: de ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang sa
NK067(ju)002:1164: bcu'i sems dpa' la'ang phyogs mthun tsam yod pas thun
NK067(ju)002:1165: mong gi mtshan dpe zhes bshad /
NK067(ju)002:1166: gnyis pa khyad par can gyi mtshan dpe la phyi nang gsang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:1167: dang po phyi'i mtshan dpe ni /
NK067(ju)002:1168: ston pa'i thugs ye shes bzhi me long /
NK067(ju)002:1171: po re re la bzhi bzhir dbye bas ye shes bcu drug gi rtsal sems dpa' bcu drug /
NK067(ju)002:1172: de'i yul chos dbyings bcu drug gi rtsal las sems ma bcu drug ste mtshan so gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:1173: sems dpa' bcu drug la ye shes lnga yi rtags
NK067(ju)002:1174: rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa'i lha brgyad cu ni dpe
NK067(ju)002:1175: byad brgyad cu'o // gnyis pa nang gi mtshan dpe ni /
NK067(ju)002:1176: spyi bo'i 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab so gnyis mtshan so gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:1177: lte ba'i rtsa 'dab re bzhi la stong pa'i rtsa bzhi phri bas drug cu /
NK067(ju)002:1179: snying ga'i rtsa chen bzhi ste brgyad cu la dpe byad brgyad cur bshad do //
NK067(ju)002:1180: gsum pa gsang ba'i mtshan dpe ni /
NK067(ju)002:1181: yab yum gnyis kyi dga' ba bcu drug re re ni mtshan so gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:1182: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug re re la'ang ye
NK067(ju)002:1183: shes lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pas dpe byad brgyad
NK067(ju)002:1184: cu'o // gsum pa sprul sku'i bdag nyid yin pa'i don rtags ni /
NK067(ju)002:1185: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK067(ju)002:1187: mdzad pa'i snang tshul rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing tshad med par rang snang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1188: gnyis pa thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i don rtags ni /
NK067(ju)002:1189: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1191: thabs snying rje chen po dang /
NK067(ju)002:1192: shes rab stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi brdar zhabs gnyis yab rdo rje skyil krung dang /
NK067(ju)002:1193: yum brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1194: gsum pa ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i don rtags ni /
NK067(ju)002:1195: ye shes drug gi phyag ye shes rin che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can /
NK067(ju)002:1197: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug ldan /
NK067(ju)002:1198: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags su phyag mtshan drug 'dzin pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1199: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i mtshan ma rdo rje sogs lnga dang /
NK067(ju)002:1200: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtshan ma dril bu dang drug 'dzin pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1201: bzhi pa rnam thar gsum chub pa'i don rtags su
NK067(ju)002:1202: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum
NK067(ju)002:1203: dang ldan pa / zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:1207: de gsum mtshon pa'i dbu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing gar snang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1208: bzhi pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:1211: dang po gnas kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK067(ju)002:1212: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na /
NK067(ju)002:1216: mtha' dbus med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK067(ju)002:1217: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK067(ju)002:1220: chos dbyings don gyi 'og min dang /
NK067(ju)002:1224: dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min dang lnga las /
NK067(ju)002:1225: dang po don gyi 'og min ni /
NK067(ju)002:1226: chos kyi dbyings la grags te /
NK067(ju)002:1227: rnam rtog dang mtshan ma gang gi'ang 'og tu ma gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1228: gnyis pa rig pa'i 'og min ni /
NK067(ju)002:1229: chos kyi dbyings de rtogs byed kyi rang rig ye shes la bya ste /
NK067(ju)002:1230: gnyis 'dzin gyi 'og tu ma gyur pas so //
NK067(ju)002:1231: gsum pa gsang ba'i 'og min ni /
NK067(ju)002:1233: ston pa gsang ba'i sku'i bzhugs gnas yin zhing /
NK067(ju)002:1234: mtshan rtog gi 'og tu ma gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1235: rgyud gzhan nas rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la bzhugs so //
NK067(ju)002:1237: bzhi pa 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min ni /
NK067(ju)002:1238: gzugs khams gnas rigs bcu bdun gyi ya tha gtsang
NK067(ju)002:1239: rigs lha lnga'i dang po ste gzugs can gyi 'og
NK067(ju)002:1240: tu ma gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1241: lnga pa dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min zhes pa
NK067(ju)002:1242: skabs 'dir bstan pa'i longs sku'i bzhugs gnas 'og min
NK067(ju)002:1243: chen po ste / gtsang ma'i rigs spangs pa'i steng du'o //
NK067(ju)002:1244: gnyis pa gnas kyi ngo bo ni /
NK067(ju)002:1245: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la /
NK067(ju)002:1247: gos pa med pa'i pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la /
NK067(ju)002:1249: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i rtags su gzhal
NK067(ju)002:1250: yas khang dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang ba'o
NK067(ju)002:1251: // de la gnas kyi ngo bo'i chos rnams dbye ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1253: gzhal yas gzhi dang rgyu dang rgya //
NK067(ju)002:1254: dbyibs dang glo 'bur rtse mo dang //
NK067(ju)002:1255: rgyan dang sgo khyud rta babs dang //
NK067(ju)002:1256: mtshan nyid gdan gyi rnam pa ste //
NK067(ju)002:1257: zhes dbye ba bcu gcig las /
NK067(ju)002:1258: dang po gzhal yas khang gi phyi'i 'og gzhi ni /
NK067(ju)002:1259: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la /
NK067(ju)002:1261: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i rgya khyon tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i rnam pa can dang /
NK067(ju)002:1264: sgo dang khyams sogs nas lte ba'i bar gyi nang
NK067(ju)002:1265: gi 'og gzhi rdo rje 'greng bu re res spags
NK067(ju)002:1266: pa ste / theg pa 'og ma las 'phags pa'i don yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1267: gnyis pa rgyu ni ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang zhes pas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:1268: gdul bya'i re ba skong ba'i rtags su rgyu rin
NK067(ju)002:1269: po che sna tshogs las grub pa ye shes nyid
NK067(ju)002:1270: gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang
NK067(ju)002:1271: snang ba'o // gsum pa rgya tshad ni /
NK067(ju)002:1272: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK067(ju)002:1274: phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa chos kyi dbyings
NK067(ju)002:1275: mtha' klas par khyab par rang snang ba'i phyir ro
NK067(ju)002:1277: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK067(ju)002:1280: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan gyis khyab pa dang rgyas pa mnyam pa'i phyir de ltar rang snang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1282: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK067(ju)002:1284: don gru chad las phyir 'phyar ba'i 'bur thabs kyi rnam pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1285: kha dog rigs bzhi'i mdog can gyi rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1286: ye shes re re'ang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhir ldan pa'i rtags su'o //
NK067(ju)002:1288: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK067(ju)002:1289: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad so so ma yin
NK067(ju)002:1290: ngo bo nyid gcig pa ye shes kun tu 'khyil
NK067(ju)002:1292: don ni tshad dpag tu med pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1293: dbyibs bum pa zlum po'i rnam par 'khyil ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:1294: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la mthar thug pa med cing spros pa dang bral ba'i rtags so //
NK067(ju)002:1296: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sogs nas //
NK067(ju)002:1297: rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas klubs pa /
NK067(ju)002:1299: spyir rgyan gyi rnam grangs la bdun las /
NK067(ju)002:1301: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i mthar /
NK067(ju)002:1302: chos nyid mtshon pa rdo rje'i rwa ba zlum pos bskor ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1303: gnyis pa logs rgyan la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:1305: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med kyi rtsal ma 'gags
NK067(ju)002:1306: par rang snang ba'i rtags su pany+tsa re kh+aa'i rtsig
NK067(ju)002:1307: pa'i steng du rin po che'i pha gu dang phreng
NK067(ju)002:1308: ba chun 'phyang shar bu mda' yab sogs rgyan du
NK067(ju)002:1309: mas spras pa'o // gnyis pa 'dod yon gyi rgyan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1310: gzugs rdo rje ma sog 'dod yon lnga'i lha mos phyogs kun tu 'khrigs pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1311: don ni 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnams dag rgyan du rdzogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1313: dbus bum pa zlum po'i steng bre mtshon pa'i phyur
NK067(ju)002:1314: bu'i steng du pad+ma la gnas pa'i 'khor lo rim
NK067(ju)002:1315: pa bcu gsum gyi steng na rin po che'i gdugs
NK067(ju)002:1316: rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1317: gzhan yang phyogs bzhir rta babs kyi rtser gdugs dang 'khor lo ri dwags kyi brten pa /
NK067(ju)002:1318: rnga yab dang ba dan la sogs pas mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1319: bzhi pa sgo dang rta babs kyi rgyan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1320: sgo dang rta babs la glang seng la sogs pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1321: lnga pa sgo'i phyi rol gyi rgyan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1322: sgo'i g.yas g.yon na t+aa la'i ljon pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1323: dpag bsam gyi shing dag la gser gyi thig gus sbrel ba las dril bu'i sgra snyan sgrogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1324: drug pa ngo bo nyid kyi rgyan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1325: bden bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad dang bden gnyis dbyer
NK067(ju)002:1326: med mtshon pa'i bar khyams la sogs pas mdzes pa'o
NK067(ju)002:1327: // bdun pa bdag po'i rgyan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1328: sprul pa'i 'phro 'du bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis gzhal yas khang mdzes par brgyan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1329: brgyad pa sgo yi don ni /
NK067(ju)002:1330: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK067(ju)002:1332: don ni rnam par thar pa bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin
NK067(ju)002:1333: gyis byang chub chen por lhun gyis 'jug pa'i rtags
NK067(ju)002:1334: su phyogs kyis dbye ba'i sgo bzhi dang ldan pa'o
NK067(ju)002:1336: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa /
NK067(ju)002:1338: de la rgyu'i rta babs brgyad dang /
NK067(ju)002:1339: 'bras bu'i rta babs brgyad de bcu drug tu bstan pa yin /
NK067(ju)002:1341: thun mong gi theng pa rnam thar brgyad la 'jug pa'i rtags su /
NK067(ju)002:1342: sgo phub phyi nang gnyis su them skas bzhi bzhi
NK067(ju)002:1343: dang ldan pa'i babs zhon gyi rta babs brgyad dang
NK067(ju)002:1344: ldan pa'o // 'bras bu'i rta babs brgyad ni theg
NK067(ju)002:1345: pa brgyad kyi yon tan rdzogs pa'i rtags su sgo
NK067(ju)002:1346: logs kyi zur bzhi nas ka bas btegs pa'i steng
NK067(ju)002:1347: du rgyan gyi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1348: bcu pa gnas kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK067(ju)002:1349: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu'ang nang du gyur pa /
NK067(ju)002:1351: don chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang las ye shes kyi
NK067(ju)002:1352: rnam 'phrul du snang ba'i gzhal yas khang rgyan dang
NK067(ju)002:1353: bcas pa shel snod du rin po che sna tshogs
NK067(ju)002:1354: bcug pa ltar mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rang bzhin
NK067(ju)002:1355: yin pas de ltar du bshad pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1356: bcu gcig pa gdan khri'i don ni /
NK067(ju)002:1357: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK067(ju)002:1360: pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la /
NK067(ju)002:1363: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan dang /
NK067(ju)002:1364: yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan dang /
NK067(ju)002:1365: sa yi khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:1367: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i phyag rgyas rtog tshogs rgyun
NK067(ju)002:1368: gcod pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bar mi chad du
NK067(ju)002:1369: bskor rtags su shar ba 'khor lo'i gdan /
NK067(ju)002:1371: yon tan gyi rtags su seng ge la sogs pa'i
NK067(ju)002:1372: sems can lnga po re re'ang brgyad brgyad kyi gdan
NK067(ju)002:1374: 'bras bu'i chos mi 'jigs bzhi sogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su de ltar gnas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)002:1375: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK067(ju)002:1376: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi bcom //
NK067(ju)002:1377: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK067(ju)002:1378: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK067(ju)002:1379: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK067(ju)002:1380: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK067(ju)002:1381: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK067(ju)002:1382: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal po'i gsung //
NK067(ju)002:1383: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK067(ju)002:1384: las ni phrin las bzhi yis zhi rgyas dbang drag las rnams kyis //
NK067(ju)002:1385: thogs med las rnams lhun gyis grub //
NK067(ju)002:1388: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK067(ju)002:1391: rgyal ba'i thugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhing thabs shes dbyer med pa'i nyi zla'i gdan /
NK067(ju)002:1392: pad+ma 'dam las skyes kyang de'i dri mas ma gos
NK067(ju)002:1393: pa ltar rtag chad kyi mtha' yi skyon gyis gos
NK067(ju)002:1394: pa med pa'i rtags su pad+ma'i gdan /
NK067(ju)002:1395: re 'dod skong zhing dkor bdun ldan pa'i rtags su
NK067(ju)002:1396: rin po che'i khri rkang mdzod mig bdun ldan rnams
NK067(ju)002:1397: so // lnga pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:1398: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)002:1399: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:1400: dang po rigs kyi yab lnga dang yum lnga las /
NK067(ju)002:1402: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po sogs nas /
NK067(ju)002:1403: 'du byed kyi rgyal po sogs so //
NK067(ju)002:1407: de lhar dag tshul bshad pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:1408: de'i rigs kyi dbye ba bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:1411: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK067(ju)002:1412: 'du byed rnam par shes pa la //
NK067(ju)002:1413: phung po lnga zhes rab tu brjod //
NK067(ju)002:1415: rnam shes kyi phung po ni yul rnam par rig pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshogs brgyad de /
NK067(ju)002:1419: sgo lnga'i rnam shes te brgyad do //
NK067(ju)002:1421: gzugs su rung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi gzugs bco lnga ste rgyu'i gzugs 'byung ba bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:1426: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:1428: rnam pa rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs dang bco lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:1430: nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshor ba bde sdug bar ma gsum mo //
NK067(ju)002:1432: yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi
NK067(ju)002:1433: 'du shes rgya che chung tshad med pa gsum mo
NK067(ju)002:1435: mngon par 'du byed pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1436: de yang sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste /
NK067(ju)002:1441: 'di dag yul nges lnga yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1446: 'di dag dge ba bcu gcig go //
NK067(ju)002:1449: 'di dag rtsa nyon drug yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1455: shes bzhin 20ma yin rnam g.yeng ste //
NK067(ju)002:1458: zhes pa de la lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste /
NK067(ju)002:1460: 'du shes gnyis phri bas lhag ma zhe dgu ni 'du byed kyi phung bor 'jog pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1461: gnyis pa de dag lhar dag tshul bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1462: rtog tshogs phung po lnga'i rang bzhin ye ji bzhin par rigs lnga'i ngo bo yin pa la /
NK067(ju)002:1463: khyad par du rgyud dag pas sangs rgyas lnga'i 'bras bu mngon du byas te mthar phyin pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1464: de lta bu'i rtog pa la rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK067(ju)002:1465: zag med kyi chos bde ba chen po la longs spyod pas na rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:1466: rgyud 'di'i lha la rtog pa'i mtshan gyis mos pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1467: 'bras bu thob pa'i dus na rtog pa nyid ma
NK067(ju)002:1468: spangs ma bsgyur bar lha'i rang bzhin du rnam par
NK067(ju)002:1470: rtog tshogs lhar snang ba'i 'thad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1471: phyi rol gyi dbang du byas na /
NK067(ju)002:1472: rtog tshogs lhar snang ba ye nas yin pa nyid
NK067(ju)002:1473: lam rkyen dang 'phrad na lhar snang rung ma 'gags
NK067(ju)002:1474: pa'i phyir / dper na dngul chus bsdus pa'i gser phye nyid dngul chu'i gong bu ltar snang yang /
NK067(ju)002:1475: me yi rkyen dang 'phrad na gser du 'gyur la /
NK067(ju)002:1476: ma 'phrad na mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:1477: de bzhin du rtog tshogs ye nas lha'i rang bzhin ma yin na /
NK067(ju)002:1478: lam rkyen gyis lhar mi 'gyur te /
NK067(ju)002:1479: rdo ba la gser du bsgoms pas gser du mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:1480: shes bya nang gi dbang du byas pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1481: rnam shes ni thugs kyi bdag nyid /
NK067(ju)002:1483: tshor ba ni yul la longs spyod pa'i yon tan gyi bdag nyid /
NK067(ju)002:1484: 'du shes ni phyi nang gi chos rnams la tha
NK067(ju)002:1485: snyad du 'dogs pa'i brda sprod pa'i phyir gsung gi
NK067(ju)002:1486: bdag nyid / 'du byed ni bya ba byed pa las kyi bdag nyid do //
NK067(ju)002:1487: gsum pa de'i rigs kyi dbye ba bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1488: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo mi bskyod pa ni thugs rdo rje'i rigs dang chos dbyings ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:1489: rnam snang sku bde gshegs rigs dang me long ye shes //
NK067(ju)002:1490: rin 'byung yon tan rin chen rigs dang mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:1491: snang mtha' gsung pad+ma'i rigs dang sor rtog ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:1492: don grub las kyi rigs dang bya grub ye shes so //
NK067(ju)002:1493: de rnams kyi mtshan ma'i sku mdog ni de dag kun kyang mthing ga dang sogs nas /
NK067(ju)002:1496: chos dbyings ye shes dang rdo rje'i rigs mthing ga /
NK067(ju)002:1497: me long ye shes dang bde gshegs rigs dkar po /
NK067(ju)002:1498: mnyam nyid ye shes dang rin chen rigs ser po /
NK067(ju)002:1499: sor rtog ye shes dang pad+ma'i rigs dmar po /
NK067(ju)002:1500: bya grub ye shes dang las kyi rigs ljang gur snang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1501: gnyis pa rigs kyi yum lnga ni /
NK067(ju)002:1502: btsun mo dam pa snang ba'i dbyings dang sogs nas /
NK067(ju)002:1505: de'i don la spyi dang bye brag gnyis so //
NK067(ju)002:1509: yum lnga la btsun mo zhes brjod pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1510: skyed par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK067(ju)002:1511: spyod par bya ba'i yul du gyur pas na de ltar du brjod de /
NK067(ju)002:1512: rtog pa'i dus su 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1513: lha'i dus su rigs kyi yab lngas spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pas so //
NK067(ju)002:1514: yang na yum gyi ngo bo dbyings dang /
NK067(ju)002:1515: yab kyi ngo bo ye shes yin pas dbyings de
NK067(ju)002:1516: nyid ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa'i phyir ro
NK067(ju)002:1517: // dam pa zhes brjod pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1518: yon tan gyi khyad par gzhan las 'phags pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1521: bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1522: gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1523: yum dbyings phyug ma la snang ba zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1524: rtog pa'i dus na nam mkhas go ma phye na
NK067(ju)002:1525: dngos po thams cad snang mi nub pas go 'byed
NK067(ju)002:1527: lha'i dus na chos khams nam mkha' rnam shes kyi yul yin pa ltar /
NK067(ju)002:1528: thugs rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i rigs kyi yum dang /
NK067(ju)002:1529: yum spyan ma la sra ba zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1530: rtog pa'i dus su sra zhing mkhregs pa'i mtshan nyid can sa yi khams /
NK067(ju)002:1531: lha'i dus na brtan cing rten du gyur ba sku'i rigs kyi yum dang /
NK067(ju)002:1532: m+aa ma k+ai la mnyen pa zhes pa /
NK067(ju)002:1533: rtog pa'i dus brlan zhing gsher ba chu'i khams /
NK067(ju)002:1534: lha'i dus na rgyud brlan cing yon tan sdud pa'i rin chen rigs kyi yum dang /
NK067(ju)002:1535: gos dkar mo la dro ba zhes pa /
NK067(ju)002:1536: rtog pa'i dus na tsha zhing sreg pa me yi khams /
NK067(ju)002:1537: de lha'i dus na mtshan 'dzin gyi spu ri shes
NK067(ju)002:1538: rab kyi mes sreg par byed pa pad+ma'i rigs kyi
NK067(ju)002:1539: yum dang / dam tshig sgrol ma la bskyod pa
NK067(ju)002:1540: zhes pa rtog pa'i dus yang zhing g.yo ba rlung
NK067(ju)002:1541: yum dang / gi khams dang / lha'i dus na
NK067(ju)002:1542: rlung gis bskyod 'degs kyi bya ba byed pa ltar
NK067(ju)002:1543: thogs pa med pa'i las can las kyi rigs kyi
NK067(ju)002:1544: yum dang / gi khams dang / yum mo //
NK067(ju)002:1545: gnyis pa rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor la
NK067(ju)002:1546: yum dang / gi khams dang / yum mo // / rgyal sras sems pa'i 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)002:1548: dang po rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:1549: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1553: de yang spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:1555: sems dpa' yab rnams kyi mtshan la /
NK067(ju)002:1556: byang chub chen po rdo rje zhes pa /
NK067(ju)002:1557: mig shes la sogs pa rtog tshogs rnams ye nas
NK067(ju)002:1558: byang chub kyi sems yin pa la yin pa ltar
NK067(ju)002:1559: mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni byang chub chen
NK067(ju)002:1560: po dang / don dam par lha rtog dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir na rdo rje zhes pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1561: sems ma rnams la btsun mo zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1562: yul bzhis rnam shes bzhi bskyed pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1564: dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1565: gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1566: nang sems bzhi po la mthong ba la sogs pa smos pa ni rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK067(ju)002:1567: mig dbang la brten nas mig shes la sogs kyis gzugs sogs mthong ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1568: de lha'i dus na thugs kyi sems dpa' bzhi yin te /
NK067(ju)002:1572: myong ba spyan ras gzigs rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:1573: de dag gi yul bzhi la /
NK067(ju)002:1574: mthong bar bya ba sogs smos pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1576: mig shes sogs kyis mthong bya gzugs sogs yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:1577: de lha'i dus na mthong bar bya ba l+aa s+ya ma /
NK067(ju)002:1578: mnyan par bya ba g+airti ma /
NK067(ju)002:1579: snom par bya ba m+aa le ma /
NK067(ju)002:1580: myong bar bya ba n+airti ma rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:1581: phyi sems bzhi la mthong byed la sogs smos pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1583: rnam shes bzhis yul bzhi mthong ba'i bdag rkyen dbang po bzhis byed pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1584: de dag pa lha'i dus na gsung gi sems dpa' bzhi yin te /
NK067(ju)002:1588: myong byed 'jam dpal rnams su nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)002:1589: phyi sems bzhi po de'i yum la 'das pa sogs smos pa ni rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK067(ju)002:1590: dus bzhis go phye nas dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)002:1593: da lta ba me tog ma /
NK067(ju)002:1595: ma nges pa dri chab ma rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:1596: 'dir dus bzhi po gang yin zhe na /
NK067(ju)002:1597: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka spyad zin pa'i dus ni 'das pa /
NK067(ju)002:1598: rgyu spyad cing 'bras bu ma spyad pa da lta ba /
NK067(ju)002:1599: rgyu 'bras tshogs la ma spyad pa ni ma 'ongs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1600: rgyu 'bras yod la ma tshogs pa ni 'das ma 'ongs gang du yang ma nges pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1601: gnyis pa 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor la /
NK067(ju)002:1602: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg pa dang sogs nas /
