NK067(ju)002:1603: mtshan mar ma yin par zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan /
NK067(ju)002:1604: de la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:1606: yab bzhi la 'joms pa chen po rdo rje zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1607: phyi lus kyi chos bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK067(ju)002:1608: khro bo bzhis log 'dren rnams 'joms pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1609: nang gsang ba'i khams bzhi dang sbyar na bde ba'i
NK067(ju)002:1610: rtog pa lha'am bde bar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa gnyis
NK067(ju)002:1611: ka 'joms pa la thogs pa med pas rdo rje
NK067(ju)002:1612: zhes brjod cing / de 'joms pa'i phrin las gzhan
NK067(ju)002:1613: las khyad par du 'phags pas na chen po zhes
NK067(ju)002:1614: zhes brjod cing / pa'o // yum rnams la btsun mo zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1615: de lta bu'i 'joms byed kyi gnyen po de'ang rtag
NK067(ju)002:1616: chad bdag mtshan bzhis bskyed pa ma yin pa dang
NK067(ju)002:1617: / chos nyid yum gyi ngo bos bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1618: gnyis pa bye brag gi mtshan ni /
NK067(ju)002:1619: sgo ba yab bzhi la reg pa sogs smos pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1622: lus kyi 'dus te reg pas tshor ba skye /
NK067(ju)002:1625: de gnyis 'phrad pas reg shes kyis 'jam rtsub sogs myong ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1627: gsang ba'i yul dbang rnam shes gsum 'dus pas reg pa skye /
NK067(ju)002:1628: reg byed gsang dbang thabs kyi rdo rje dang //
NK067(ju)002:1629: reg bya gsang yul shes rab yum gyi pad+mara reg shes kyis dga' ba nyams su myong ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1630: de lha'i dus na phyi nang gnyis ka'i rtog pa go rim bzhin du /
NK067(ju)002:1631: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1634: gshin rje gshed rnams su dag pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1635: de dag gi yum rnams la /
NK067(ju)002:1636: rtag pa ma yin pa sogs su smos pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1638: phung po mi rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1639: sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin ngar 'dzin pa /
NK067(ju)002:1641: stong par 'dzin pa rnams lha'i dus su /
NK067(ju)002:1645: dril bu ma rnams su dag pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1647: chos kyi dbyings kun tu khyab cing mtha' yas par khyab pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1649: til gyi gong bu bzhin du gang nas khyab cing bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1650: zhes dang de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK067(ju)002:1653: khyab pa'i tshad ni kun tu khyab cing mtha' yas par khyab pa /
NK067(ju)002:1654: til gong til 'bras kyis gang ba bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:1656: 'di tsam zhes brjod kyis mi lang ba'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1657: de rnams dang rang bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs pa yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1658: gnyis pa gdul byar dgos ched du bstan pa khro
NK067(ju)002:1659: bo'i gleng gzhi la'ang phun sum tshogs pa lnga las
NK067(ju)002:1660: / dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni 'di nyid kyi le'u bco lnga pa las /
NK067(ju)002:1661: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK067(ju)002:1662: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyis
NK067(ju)002:1663: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK067(ju)002:1665: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK067(ju)002:1666: po drug pa kun tu bzang po de nyid gdul
NK067(ju)002:1668: 'dul byed khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs mngon par 'du mdzad pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1669: phrin las phyag rgya'i skur bzhengs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1670: gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1671: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas khrag gi rgya mtsho'i
NK067(ju)002:1672: dkyil na keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng
NK067(ju)002:1673: 'bar ba chen po'i klong gi 'khor lo'i dkyil na
NK067(ju)002:1675: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang du bzhugs par dgyes pa /
NK067(ju)002:1676: mkha' rlung gi dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i khrag gi rgya mtsho /
NK067(ju)002:1678: keng rus kyi ri rab brtsegs pa'i steng /
NK067(ju)002:1679: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba chen po'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1680: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1681: gdul bya gdug pa can gyi 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)002:1683: dang po gdul bya gdug pa can gyi 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:1684: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang brtags pa la mngon par zhen pas /
NK067(ju)002:1685: sogs nas 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK067(ju)002:1687: de la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:1688: spyir ma rig pa gnyis kyis sems can thams cad 'khor bar 'khyams pas gol la /
NK067(ju)002:1689: de yang sems can thams cad bden med sgyu ma'i don ma rtogs shing /
NK067(ju)002:1691: rtag par 'dzin pa'i zhen pas bcings nas khams gsum 'khor ba rang rgyud du 'khor ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1693: bye brag ru dra gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs
NK067(ju)002:1694: par sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas
NK067(ju)002:1695: / sbyor sgrol gnyis barlang por spyad pa'i rnam smin
NK067(ju)002:1696: gyis dmyal ba'i sdug basnga mi bzad pa myong shing
NK067(ju)002:1697: / / rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu lha rang rgyud du bsgoms shing /
NK067(ju)002:1698: drag ra la ra la sogs /
NK067(ju)002:1699: sngags rang gar bzlas pas yi dwags kyi rigs srin po bya'i gshog pa can zhig tu skyes so //
NK067(ju)002:1700: gnyis pa 'joms byed gnyen po'i 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:1701: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen por gyur te /
NK067(ju)002:1703: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)002:1706: seng gdong chen mo sogs yul ma brgyad /
NK067(ju)002:1707: rdo rje sring 'gro ma sogs sgo ma bzhi shin tu rngam pa'i gzugs kyis gnas so //
NK067(ju)002:1708: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1709: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo sogs /
NK067(ju)002:1710: dbang mo nyer brgyad rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:1711: bzhi ba chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1712: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa'i /
NK067(ju)002:1713: zhes sogs nas dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol tu bkod do //
NK067(ju)002:1714: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)002:1715: de nyid sbyor sgrol gyi phrin las rmad du byung ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:1716: dang po pho rnams sgrol bas 'dul ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1717: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas gsang ba'i yum dbyings
NK067(ju)002:1718: phyug ma sprul te snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub
NK067(ju)002:1719: kyi sems sprin las khro bo 'chol ba'i tshogs spros
NK067(ju)002:1720: pas gdug pa can skrag ste brgyal bar gyur pa
NK067(ju)002:1721: na / khro tshogs rnams bsdus te /
NK067(ju)002:1722: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang bar byas so //
NK067(ju)002:1723: gdug pa can zhabs 'og tu mnan pas da dung
NK067(ju)002:1724: dgra zlar mthong ste gtum tshigs smras pas slar yang
NK067(ju)002:1725: dpal chen pos ru tra'i ngor sgrol byed rdo rje
NK067(ju)002:1726: srin po dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa'i rnam par
NK067(ju)002:1727: bstan nas gdug pa can gyi dug gsum dag par
NK067(ju)002:1730: gti mug sha'i rnam pa lhag ma ma lus par
NK067(ju)002:1731: zhal du gsol ba ni pho rnams sgrol bas 'dul
NK067(ju)002:1732: ba'o // gnyis pa mo rnams sbyor bas 'dul ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1733: gdug pa can de dag gi chung ma dbang mo
NK067(ju)002:1734: nyer brgyad po dbang du bsdus shing rigs bzhi'i khro
NK067(ju)002:1736: dpal chen po'i sku la brgyad 'khril nas mnyam par
NK067(ju)002:1737: sbyor ba las gnas yul sgo ma rnams re re'ang
NK067(ju)002:1739: so so yang rigs gcig tu bsdus te dkyil 'khor
NK067(ju)002:1740: gyi gnas so sor bkod de phata ces bsgrags pas
NK067(ju)002:1741: dbang mo nyer brgyad rang rang gi gnas su yud
NK067(ju)002:1742: tsam la bakye'o // de nas sngar gsol ba'i ru
NK067(ju)002:1743: tra pho rnams lto bar gnas pa 'og sgo nas
NK067(ju)002:1744: tsam la bakye'o // bton te / mi gtsang ba'i 'dam kyi rgya mtshor chud pa la /
NK067(ju)002:1745: sras mchog rme ba brtsegs pa byung ste /
NK067(ju)002:1746: 'dam kun 'thungs pas gdug can de rnams dran pa
NK067(ju)002:1747: rnyed de snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK067(ju)002:1748: thob ste / bsam yas lhun grub khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhal mngon sum du mthong ngo //
NK067(ju)002:1749: de nas skrag cing bred de zhum pa'i nga ros 'bangs su mchi'o //
NK067(ju)002:1751: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis 'brang dang //
NK067(ju)002:1754: rang gi lus khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du phul lo //
NK067(ju)002:1755: de nas dpal chen pos lag tu rdo rje byin
NK067(ju)002:1756: nas rdo rje sring 'gro ma la sogs ming gi
NK067(ju)002:1757: dbang bskur nas lhag ma len pa'i las kyi bka'
NK067(ju)002:1758: sdod dkyil 'khor gyi khrag khyams la 'god par mdzad
NK067(ju)002:1759: do // lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1760: de'i dus na phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten //
NK067(ju)002:1764: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi gdug pa can thams cad dus gcig tu btul ba'i don yin /
NK067(ju)002:1765: de yang don du gsang ba'i 'og min du /
NK067(ju)002:1766: ston 'khor tshogs nas snying ga'i 'og min du sangs
NK067(ju)002:1767: rgyas pa'i tshe phyi rol du rtags snang de ltar
NK067(ju)002:1769: gsum pa sprul skus 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gzhi la'ang phun sum tshogs pa lnga las /
NK067(ju)002:1770: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1771: 'di nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las /
NK067(ju)002:1772: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK067(ju)002:1773: sogs nas thugs rdo rje las thon te /
NK067(ju)002:1775: thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res /
NK067(ju)002:1777: stong gsum gyi stong chen po re re'i don mdzad
NK067(ju)002:1778: pa yin te thub pa de re re la'ang gdul
NK067(ju)002:1779: bya rigs drug so so'i mthong snang gi dbang gis
NK067(ju)002:1782: lha yi gnas na brgya byin mgon //
NK067(ju)002:1783: lha ma yin na thag bzang ris //
NK067(ju)002:1785: yi dwags gnas na kha 'bar te //
NK067(ju)002:1786: byol song seng ge nyid du smra //
NK067(ju)002:1787: dmyal ba las kyi gshin rje'i mgon //
NK067(ju)002:1789: gnyis pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1795: de dag gi shugs kyis lha min kyang bsdus te /
NK067(ju)002:1796: lha min la rigs lnga yod pas /
NK067(ju)002:1798: smad rigs dud 'gror bsdus pas 'gro ba lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:1799: bye brag 'khor rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1800: gsum pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1801: s+n+rel gzhi dang yas man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa /
NK067(ju)002:1803: mgo gyen bstan du 'gro ba mtho ris /
NK067(ju)002:1804: thur bstan du 'gro ba dmyal ba dang yi dwags /
NK067(ju)002:1805: 'phred bstan du 'gro ba s+n+rel gzhi ste byol song /
NK067(ju)002:1806: de drug po stong gsum 'jig rten gcig gi nang du chud pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1807: de 'dra ba stong la stong spyi phud /
NK067(ju)002:1808: de 'dra ba stong la stong gnyis pa /
NK067(ju)002:1809: de 'dra ba stong la stong gsum pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1810: de rnams sprul sku'i gdul bya'i zhing yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1811: bzhi pa chos phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1814: dang po sku bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1816: mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs pa ston pa'i thub pa /
NK067(ju)002:1818: de yang thub pa'i mdzad pa brgyad bstan pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1819: 'dzam gling bye ba phrag brgya re rer 'dul byed
NK067(ju)002:1820: mchog gi sprul sku yang de snyed 'byung ba thams
NK067(ju)002:1821: cad mdzad pa'i tshul mthun par ston pas na gcig
NK067(ju)002:1822: gi mdzad tshul smos pas thams cad kyi mdzad par
NK067(ju)002:1824: 'o skol gyi ston pa 'di nyid kyi sgo nas brjod de /
NK067(ju)002:1825: dga' ldan gyi gnas su dam pa tog dkar por skye ba bzhes te /
NK067(ju)002:1826: gzigs pa lngas gzigs nas mo lug gi lo chu
NK067(ju)002:1827: stod zla ba'i nya la glang po che'i rnam pas
NK067(ju)002:1828: yum sgyu 'phrul ma gso sbyong la gnas pa'i lhums
NK067(ju)002:1829: su zhugs te / zla ba bcu phal cher rdzogs
NK067(ju)002:1830: pa lcags sprel sa ga'i tshes bdun rgyu skar rgyal
NK067(ju)002:1831: la babs pa'i tshe lum+bi n+ai'i 'tshal du yum gyi
NK067(ju)002:1832: rtsibs logs g.yas pa nas mngal gyi dri ma med
NK067(ju)002:1834: yi ge sogs slob pa ltar mdzad nas bzo'i gnas la byang bar gyur cing /
NK067(ju)002:1835: sh+aakya rnams sgyu rtsal gyis pham par mdzad de /
NK067(ju)002:1836: sa 'tsho ma btsun mo'i 'khor brgyad khri bzhi stong
NK067(ju)002:1837: dang bcas pa bdag gir bzhes nas lo nyi shu
NK067(ju)002:1838: rtsa dgu'i bar khab tu bzhugs pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1839: de nas khyim spangs te mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du rab tu byung ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1840: de nas chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du lo
NK067(ju)002:1841: drug gi bar dka' thub mdzad pas sku shin tu
NK067(ju)002:1842: rid pa la grong pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas
NK067(ju)002:1843: ba stong gi 'o ma nying khur byas pa sbrang
NK067(ju)002:1844: rtsi dang sbyar ba drangs pa gsol ba'i mod la
NK067(ju)002:1845: sku gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar gyur pa
NK067(ju)002:1846: dang / de nas rdo rje gdan du skyes bu
NK067(ju)002:1847: chen po'i stabs kyis gshegs r+ts+wa 'tshong bkra shis las
NK067(ju)002:1848: r+ts+wa bslangs pa la stan mdzad nas /
NK067(ju)002:1849: byang chub kyi shing drung du skyil mo krung gis bzhugs te /
NK067(ju)002:1850: dgung lo so lnga pa shing rta sa ga'i nya'i
NK067(ju)002:1851: tho rangs bsam gtan bzhi pa la brten nas sgrib
NK067(ju)002:1852: gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa ma lus pa spangs
NK067(ju)002:1853: shing / shes bya thams cad thugs su chud de mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1854: de'i snga logs nya de'i srod kyi dus su smin
NK067(ju)002:1855: mtshams nas 'od zer bkye ba la sogs pa'i sgo
NK067(ju)002:1857: sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag bdun gyi bar du chos ma gsungs pa la /
NK067(ju)002:1858: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis bskul te w+aa r+aa
NK067(ju)002:1859: na s+air lnga sde las brtsams nas bka' dang po
NK067(ju)002:1861: bya rgod phung po'i ri bo la sogs par bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1862: yangs pa can la sogs par bka' tha ma don
NK067(ju)002:1863: dam rnams par nges pa ste chos kyi 'khor lo
NK067(ju)002:1864: rnam pa gsum bskor ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1865: mnyan yod du mu stegs rnams btul ba dang sangs
NK067(ju)002:1866: rgyas ma thag shing t+aa la bdun srid du 'phags
NK067(ju)002:1867: pa sogs cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1868: mthar dgung lo brgyad cu rtsa gcig pa lcags 'brug
NK067(ju)002:1869: sa ga'i nya la gyad yul r+ts+wa can gyi gnas
NK067(ju)002:1870: shing s+aa la zung gi rtsa bar rdo rje lta
NK067(ju)002:1871: bu'i sku bshig nas mya ngan las 'das ba'i tshul
NK067(ju)002:1872: dang sku gdung ring bsrel la sogs pa rnam 'phrul
NK067(ju)002:1873: mtha' yas par ston pa'i thub pa gang gi sku'i
NK067(ju)002:1874: mdzad pa de dag gi bsod nams thun mong ma
NK067(ju)002:1875: yin pa gzhan las 'phags par bstan pas na sku
NK067(ju)002:1877: de rnams bsod nams chen po'i mthu las byung zhing
NK067(ju)002:1878: de mthong ba'i gdul bya rnams bsod nams chen por
NK067(ju)002:1880: gnyis pa thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1881: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa /
NK067(ju)002:1883: mngon shes drug dang ldan pa /
NK067(ju)002:1885: sangs rgyas rnams ni sgrib med mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK067(ju)002:1886: mnga' bas 'gro ba rnams kyi sngoon gyi gnas dran
NK067(ju)002:1889: ma nges pa'i gnas te dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa'i mngon shes /
NK067(ju)002:1890: gzhan sems 'gyu ba mtha' dag mkhyen pa'i mngon shes /
NK067(ju)002:1891: nye ring med pa'i gzugs dang /
NK067(ju)002:1892: 'chi 'pho skye ba thams cad gzigs pa'i spyan gyi mngon shes /
NK067(ju)002:1893: sgra che chung la mi ltos par thams cad gsan pa'i snyan gyi mngon shes /
NK067(ju)002:1894: gang 'dul mos pa bzhin sprul sgyur sna tshogs ston pa bya ba grub pa'i mngon shes /
NK067(ju)002:1895: zag med mngon shes kyis ji ltar spyad kyang ma gos pa zag zad kyi mngon shes /
NK067(ju)002:1896: de drug de'i rjes su 'gro zhing mkhyen pa'i don yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1897: gsum pa rdzu 'phrul bsam gyi mi khyab pas 'dul ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1898: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK067(ju)002:1902: de yang gdul bya rnams 'dul phyir lha mi'i rgyal po sogs /
NK067(ju)002:1903: rigs mthun dang zhi khro phra men sogs rnam rol du ma'i sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1904: so so'i sgra skad dang mthun par chos ston pa'i gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:1905: de dag ni rdzu 'phrul gyi spyod pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:1906: bzhi pa gsung rig pas 'dul ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1911: de la'ang mdor bstan dang rgyas bshad mjug bsdu ba gsum gyis bstan cing /
NK067(ju)002:1912: rigs can lnga'i lha mi nyan rang byang sems dang /
NK067(ju)002:1915: theg pa'i rim pa lnga bstan /
NK067(ju)002:1916: de thams cad kyang gsung gi rig byed las byung
NK067(ju)002:1917: bas gdul bya 'dul ba'i chos sgo bsam mi khyab
NK067(ju)002:1919: lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:1920: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku de byon pa'i dus sgron me'i bskal pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:1921: bskal pa de ma gtogs par bskal pa gzhan la 'byon pa ma yin no //
NK067(ju)002:1923: gnyis pa rkyen gleng slong ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1924: de yang gleng gzhi tshogs nas /
NK067(ju)002:1927: de la'ang thun mong ma yin pa dang thun mong gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:1929: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng slong ni /
NK067(ju)002:1930: ston pa yab yum lhan cig pa'i 'khor la zab dbang bskur ba'i sbyor bas mdun bsus te /
NK067(ju)002:1931: thabs kyi cha bzung ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1932: shes rab kyi cha bzung ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1933: shes rab kyi cha bzung ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:1934: thabs shes dbyer med kyi cha bzung ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:1935: dang po yab kyis thabs kyi cha bzung ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1936: 'di nyid kyi le'u gnyis pa las /
NK067(ju)002:1937: e ma hoh rdo rje phung po yan lag ni //
NK067(ju)002:1938: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK067(ju)002:1939: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK067(ju)002:1940: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK067(ju)002:1942: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK067(ju)002:1944: de'i tshe 'khor rnams kyi lhag pa kun rdzob kyi
NK067(ju)002:1945: bden pa mthong nas chos thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil
NK067(ju)002:1946: 'khor gcig gi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa la
NK067(ju)002:1947: ngo mtshar ba'o // yum gyis shes rab kyi cha bzung ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:1948: kye ma hoh phyogs bcu'i stong khams ye nas dben //
NK067(ju)002:1949: srid pa gsum ni dag pa'i zhing //
NK067(ju)002:1950: snyigs ma lnga ni bde ldan gnas //
NK067(ju)002:1951: phung po lnga ni rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK067(ju)002:1953: btsal kyang rgyal bas mi brnyes so //
NK067(ju)002:1955: 'khor rnams kyi phyogs bcu'i stong khams dang /
NK067(ju)002:1958: phung po lnga ste tha snyad bzhis bsdus pa'i chos
NK067(ju)002:1959: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs shing lhag
NK067(ju)002:1960: pa don dam gyi bden pa mthong ngo //
NK067(ju)002:1961: des 'khor thun mong ba rnams kyi dbang thob pas
NK067(ju)002:1962: don dam rtog med kyi ye shes rgyud la skyes
NK067(ju)002:1963: kyang / ston pa'i dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ye
NK067(ju)002:1964: shes chen po da dung ma myong ba'i phyir spyod
NK067(ju)002:1965: yul ma yin pas na gsang ba'i dbang zhes bya'o
NK067(ju)002:1966: kyang / // de nas thabs shes dbyer med kyi cha bzung nas /
NK067(ju)002:1967: dbang phyi ma gnyis bskur bas yab yum mnyam par
NK067(ju)002:1968: sbyor ba'i dkar dmar byang sems kyis rgyu byas te
NK067(ju)002:1969: / e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK067(ju)002:1970: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK067(ju)002:1971: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK067(ju)002:1972: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK067(ju)002:1973: ces sogs kyi tshigs bcad lnga ste /
NK067(ju)002:1975: gzhi rang bzhin gyi sems bskyed /
NK067(ju)002:1976: bgrod pa lam gyi sems bskyed /
NK067(ju)002:1977: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:1979: e ma hoh zhes pa ngo mtshar ba'i tshig ste /
NK067(ju)002:1980: gang na rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rang bzhin ye
NK067(ju)002:1981: shes lngar dag pa'i gnas la ngo mtshar zhing gzhan
NK067(ju)002:1982: las rmad du byung ba'i chos nyid 'di ni rdzogs
NK067(ju)002:1983: pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba zab
NK067(ju)002:1984: mo ste / phal gyi spyod yul ma yin pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:1986: sems nyid gdod nas skye ba med pa las 'khrul
NK067(ju)002:1987: ngor rtog bcas kyi sems thams cad rgyu rkyen las
NK067(ju)002:1989: de ltar skyes par snang tsam nyid na don la
NK067(ju)002:1990: de lta bur skye ba grub pa med pa 'di
NK067(ju)002:1991: ni kun gzhi nyid chos dbyings ye shes su bskyed
NK067(ju)002:1992: pa'o // de bzhin du snang ba thams cad 'gags
NK067(ju)002:1993: pa nyid na don dam 'gags pa med pa'i zung
NK067(ju)002:1994: 'jug rtog med rang gsal ba 'di ni kun gzhi'i
NK067(ju)002:1995: rnam shes me long lta bu'i ye shes su'o //
NK067(ju)002:1996: rten gang la gnas pa ltar snang tsam nyid na
NK067(ju)002:1997: don la gnas pa med pa'i zung 'jug dngos po'i
NK067(ju)002:1998: gshis tha dad phyogs ris bral ba 'di ni nyon
NK067(ju)002:1999: mongs pa can gyi yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye
NK067(ju)002:2000: shes su'o // yul tha dad du dmigs pa nyid
NK067(ju)002:2001: na don la dmigs pa med pa'i zung 'jug yul
NK067(ju)002:2002: yul can gnyis med gsal la ma 'dres pa ni
NK067(ju)002:2003: yid so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su'o //
NK067(ju)002:2004: gang du 'gro ba dang 'ong ba ltar snang tsam
NK067(ju)002:2005: nyid na don la 'gro 'ong med pa'i zung 'jug
NK067(ju)002:2006: sems nyid ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa ni sgo
NK067(ju)002:2007: lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su bskyed pa'o
NK067(ju)002:2008: // gnyis pa la grol lam dang thabs lam gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2010: e ma hohngo mtshar rmad du byung ba zung 'jug
NK067(ju)002:2011: spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i chos nyid rdzogs
NK067(ju)002:2012: pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba ni
NK067(ju)002:2013: 'di lta ste / don dam par skye 'gags gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong med pa'i ngang las /
NK067(ju)002:2014: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad skye 'gags la sogs par snang la /
NK067(ju)002:2015: de ltar skyes pa la sogs par snang dus nyid
NK067(ju)002:2016: nas don dam par skye ba la sogs pa med
NK067(ju)002:2017: pa'i ngo bo lhag pa bden pa dbyer med du
NK067(ju)002:2018: la bzla ba lnga po 'di ni ye shes lnga
NK067(ju)002:2019: dang sbyar na stong pa nyid la sogs pa ste
NK067(ju)002:2020: / de ltar rtogs pa'i blo ni ye shes so //
NK067(ju)002:2021: de dag sems lnga dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK067(ju)002:2022: chos thams cad thog mar skye ba med na mthar 'gag pa dang bar du gnas pa med la /
NK067(ju)002:2023: de med pas rang spyi'i mtshan nyid dmigs pa med cing /
NK067(ju)002:2024: gnas dmigs med pas 'gro 'ong kyang med mod kyi /
NK067(ju)002:2025: de ltar na'ang de'i ngang las rig pa sgyu ma
NK067(ju)002:2026: tsam du thams cad skye 'gag la sogs pa ltar
NK067(ju)002:2027: snang ba'i bden gnyis mtshon tshul gyi ldog cha nas
NK067(ju)002:2028: tha dad kyang ngo bo dbyer med pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2029: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med pa ni bden
NK067(ju)002:2030: pa dbyer med kyi don la sems dang por 'go
NK067(ju)002:2031: ldang ba g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK067(ju)002:2032: de bzhin du 'khrugs sdebs kyi rim pas dmigs pa
NK067(ju)002:2033: sogs don de khong du chud par smon pa byang
NK067(ju)002:2035: 'gag pa sogs dbyer med kyi don la 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK067(ju)002:2036: gnas pa sogs dbyer med kyi don la gnas pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK067(ju)002:2037: 'gro 'ong sogs dbyer med kyi don mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK067(ju)002:2038: de yang lam pa'i blo khyad kyi dbyer med kyi
NK067(ju)002:2039: bden pa la sems lnga dus gcig la rdzogs pa
NK067(ju)002:2041: rim par bskyed pa rim gyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2043: e ma hoh zhes pa ngam pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2044: gang la na 'dod chags chen po'i spyod pa 'di ni spyad kyang mi 'ching bas ngo mtshar zhing /
NK067(ju)002:2045: des bla na med pa'i 'bras bu mngon du byed
NK067(ju)002:2046: pa'i myur lam gzhan las ches rmad du byung ba'i
NK067(ju)002:2047: chos rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi brnag
NK067(ju)002:2049: khe nyen dang bcas pa'i thabs kyi lam yin pa'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:2051: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa rten med kyi ye
NK067(ju)002:2052: shes la skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong med pa
NK067(ju)002:2053: las yab yum gnyis su med par rol pa'i sbyor
NK067(ju)002:2054: bas dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi
NK067(ju)002:2055: lam nyams su blangs pa'i tshe /
NK067(ju)002:2056: rtsa gnas thams cad nas thig le g.yos pas bde
NK067(ju)002:2057: ba 'go ldang ba'i tshul du skyes pa ni g.yo
NK067(ju)002:2059: bde ba snga ma 'gags shing phyi ma la 'jug pa 'jig 'jug byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)002:2060: bde ba snga ma la ltos nas phyi ma la smon pa smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)002:2061: rten can gyi bde ba rang sa na mi gnas
NK067(ju)002:2062: pa'i tshul gyis gnas pa gnas pa byang chub kyi
NK067(ju)002:2063: sems / 'gro 'ong thams cad dang bral ba mthar phyin byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)002:2064: de ltar yas babs kyi dga' ba bzhi'i mthar /
NK067(ju)002:2065: byang sems yum gyi pad+ma'i ze'u 'brur zhal mjal bas
NK067(ju)002:2066: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong zhing
NK067(ju)002:2067: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2070: slar yang mas brtan gyi dga' bzhi'i mthar byang sems
NK067(ju)002:2071: dkar dmar ro gcig tu 'dres pa gyen du ldog
NK067(ju)002:2072: ste spyi bor son pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK067(ju)002:2073: shes nyams su myong zhing bde ba chen po'i dbang
NK067(ju)002:2074: thob pa'o // de nas dkar cha spyi bor dag pas sku rdo rje thob /
NK067(ju)002:2075: dmar cha me yi rang bzhin rdo rje nor bu'i
NK067(ju)002:2076: rtser 'gags pas dmar cha dag pas gsung rdo rje
NK067(ju)002:2077: thob / de gnyis bar gyi 'brel byed pa rlung dag pas thugs rdo rje /
NK067(ju)002:2078: de gsum gyi 'gyur bde myong byed kyi shes rig dag pa ye shes rdo rje ste /
NK067(ju)002:2079: sku bzhi ye shes lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pas ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2080: gsum pa mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed ni /
NK067(ju)002:2081: e ma hohngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos zab
NK067(ju)002:2082: dbang gsum thob pas lhan cig pa rnams rang don
NK067(ju)002:2083: du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga po kun gyi
NK067(ju)002:2084: bdag nyid du sangs rgyas te /
NK067(ju)002:2085: ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa 'di
NK067(ju)002:2086: ni 'khor thun mong ba'i spyod yul ma yin pas
NK067(ju)002:2087: gsang ba ste / skye ba med las zhes sogs kyis dbyings ye zung 'jug chos kyi sku dang /
NK067(ju)002:2088: 'gag pa sogs kyis sku gsum dbyer med gsal stong zung 'jug mngon byang gi sku dang /
NK067(ju)002:2089: gnas pa sogs kyis dag pa'i gdul bya la gzugs
NK067(ju)002:2090: sku'i rnam par snang yang mtha' la mi gnas pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2091: zung 'jug longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK067(ju)002:2092: dmigs pa sogs kyis sku gsum so sor snang yang
NK067(ju)002:2093: mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su dbyer mi phyed pa rdo
NK067(ju)002:2094: rje'i sku dang / 'gro 'ong sogs kyis skal ba
NK067(ju)002:2095: dang 'tshams par 'char nub tu ston kyang don la
NK067(ju)002:2097: de dag ni thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng slong ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:2098: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng slong ni /
NK067(ju)002:2099: de ltar ston 'khor dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pas rang don du rgyud zhu ma dgos kyang /
NK067(ju)002:2100: e ma ho ye nas gsang ba'i chos /
NK067(ju)002:2101: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK067(ju)002:2102: ngo bo nyid kyi rab tu gsang //
NK067(ju)002:2103: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK067(ju)002:2104: zhes gsang ba bzhis chod pa'i gdul bya rnams thugs rjes bzung bar zhus pas /
NK067(ju)002:2105: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo
NK067(ju)002:2106: gcig yin kyang 'gro ba'i rnam rtog ma rig pa
NK067(ju)002:2107: las 'gro ba lnga'i ris bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK067(ju)002:2108: smin pa la sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po
NK067(ju)002:2109: skyes nas / e ma ho bde bshegs snying po las //
NK067(ju)002:2110: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK067(ju)002:2112: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK067(ju)002:2113: ces ston pas snying rje skyes nas rgyud 'chad par zhal gyis bzhes pa'o /
NK067(ju)002:2114: gsum pa 'bras bu yongs shes rgyud don la /
NK067(ju)002:2115: rgyud gsum gyi rnam gzhag spyir bstan pa /
NK067(ju)002:2116: lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2119: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de //
NK067(ju)002:2121: zhes pas spyir rgyun chags pa'i don gyis na rgyud ces bshad de /
NK067(ju)002:2122: de'ang sems can nas sangs rgyas kyi bar du sems
NK067(ju)002:2123: nyid rang bzhin rnam dag de pi wang gi rgyud
NK067(ju)002:2124: ltar breng chags su gnas pas na rgyun chags pa
NK067(ju)002:2125: zhes bshad / de nyid thabs kyi rkyen gyis zin pa dang ma zin pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2126: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du snang ba yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2127: gang rtogs par bya ba gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud /
NK067(ju)002:2128: gang gis rtogs byed thabs sam lam gyi rgyud /
NK067(ju)002:2129: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)002:2131: bcing med rnam par grol med pa //
NK067(ju)002:2132: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK067(ju)002:2134: sems kyi chos nyid 'di 'khor ba'i gnas skabs su bcing ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:2135: mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas skabs su grol ba
NK067(ju)002:2136: ltar snang yang don la bcing ba med pas grol
NK067(ju)002:2138: bcing grol med pa'i gnas lugs rang rig gi byang
NK067(ju)002:2139: chub kyi sems bden pa dbyer med blo yi spyod
NK067(ju)002:2140: yul dang bral bar ye nas gnas pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2141: de la spang bya'i sgrib gnyis spang rgyu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2142: thob bya'i yon tan gsar du thob rgyu med par
NK067(ju)002:2143: lhun grub tu yod pas byang chub kyi sems zhes
NK067(ju)002:2144: bya / de nyid don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2145: sems nyid me long nag ling nge ba lta bu dbyings don dam /
NK067(ju)002:2146: de nyid dwangs gsal sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba ye shes don dam /
NK067(ju)002:2147: me long la gzugs brnyan shar ba bzhin sems nyid
NK067(ju)002:2148: sgrib pa dang bral ba'i klong na sku dang ye
NK067(ju)002:2149: shes kyi yon tan 'char rung du gnas pa 'bras
NK067(ju)002:2150: bu'i don dam / de la sku gsung thugs yon
NK067(ju)002:2151: tan lngar phye ba'i sems nyid don dam dkor bdun
NK067(ju)002:2152: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa de
NK067(ju)002:2153: ni lhag pa don dam gyi bden pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2154: de'i rtsal snang snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi
NK067(ju)002:2155: dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba ni lhag pa kun
NK067(ju)002:2157: de gnyis kyang ngo bo dbyer med pa gser dang gser gyi kha dog ser po dang /
NK067(ju)002:2158: g.yu dang g.yu'i kha dog sngon po dang /
NK067(ju)002:2159: mar me dang mar me'i 'od lta bu zung 'jug
NK067(ju)002:2160: ngo bo gcig tu gnas pa ni lhag pa bden
NK067(ju)002:2162: de nyid blo yis bsam pa'i yul las 'das /
NK067(ju)002:2163: ngag gis brjod pa'i yul las 'das pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2164: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK067(ju)002:2166: de nyid bcos ma glo bur gyi chos ma yin
NK067(ju)002:2167: par sems nyid de'i rang bzhin ye gdod ma nas
NK067(ju)002:2169: de la mdo rgyud rnams su ming gi rnam grangs du ma zhig gsungs pa yod de /
NK067(ju)002:2170: bye brag tu smra bas ni srid pa dang srid
NK067(ju)002:2171: pa'i yo byad la ma chags pa'i sems byung chog
NK067(ju)002:2174: sems kyi sa bon zag med ye shes 'byung rung gi nus pa la 'dod /
NK067(ju)002:2176: thog ma med pa nas sems rgyud la gnas pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2177: zag med kyi chos skyed byed kyi nus pa chos
NK067(ju)002:2179: de gsum gyis bde gshegs snying po 'dus byas su 'dod pas dngos por smra ba'i grub mtha'o //
NK067(ju)002:2180: dbu ma pa ni dri bcas bde gshegs snying po
NK067(ju)002:2181: rigs su 'dod pa mthun la ngos 'dzin lugs mi
NK067(ju)002:2183: 'dir ni sems nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyi rnam
NK067(ju)002:2184: par dag pa stong gsal 'gag med kun khyab kyi
NK067(ju)002:2185: ngo bo 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba la bde bar
NK067(ju)002:2186: gshegs pa snying po zhes theg chen gyi mdo sde
NK067(ju)002:2187: rnams las 'byung ba ltar sngags su yang kri yas
NK067(ju)002:2188: bdag gi de kho na nyid /
NK067(ju)002:2189: u pa dang yo ga gnyis kyis don dam mtshan
NK067(ju)002:2190: ma med pa'i byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings
NK067(ju)002:2192: ma h+aa yo gas bden gnyis dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po'o //
NK067(ju)002:2193: a nu yo gas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su
NK067(ju)002:2194: med pa'i sras rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK067(ju)002:2195: 'khor / a ti yo gas ngo bo rang bzhin
NK067(ju)002:2196: thugs rje gsum sogs tha snyad mang du 'jug pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2197: 'khor / gazhi'o // de nyid gzhi lam 'bras gsum
NK067(ju)002:2198: gang rung gi ldog cha dang ma bstun na rang
NK067(ju)002:2199: bzhin dang gnas lugs las ming gi tha snyad gang
NK067(ju)002:2201: dang bstun na dri ma cung zad kyang ma spangs
NK067(ju)002:2203: dri ma sbyong bzhin pa'i gnas skabs la lam /
NK067(ju)002:2204: dri ma mtha' dag bral ba'i gnas skabs la 'bras bur 'jog /
NK067(ju)002:2207: tha snyad gnyis 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams kun //
NK067(ju)002:2208: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bshad //
NK067(ju)002:2210: de la dbye na ngo bo'i gzhi dang /
NK067(ju)002:2212: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid ni dri ma sbyong ba'i gzhi nor bu lta bu /
NK067(ju)002:2213: de nyid sgrib byed kyi 'dam rdzab lta bu ni btags pa'i gzhi ste /
NK067(ju)002:2214: med snang 'khor ba'i chos thams cad sbyang bya'i dri ma 'dam rdzab lta bu yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:2215: de la btags gzhi zhes pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2216: 'khrul pa'i rnam shes kyi rgyun ma zad bar du rgyun chags pa tsam yin zhing /
NK067(ju)002:2217: 'bras bu thob pa'i dus zad nas rang sangs la
NK067(ju)002:2218: 'gro ba'i phyir bcos ma glo bur gyi chos yin
NK067(ju)002:2219: no // stong nyid med dgag kyang gzhi yi rgyud
NK067(ju)002:2220: ji bzhin pa ma yin kyang btags pa tsam yin
NK067(ju)002:2221: no // te / ka ba ka ba'i ngo bos stong pa lta bu /
NK067(ju)002:2222: chos rnams skye med tsam du zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:2223: de rnams kyis gzhi'i rgyud bshad pa song nas /
NK067(ju)002:2224: gnyis pa lam gyi rgyud ni /
NK067(ju)002:2225: rgyu'i rgyud de dri ma dang bral bar byed pa'i thabs te /
NK067(ju)002:2226: lam rgyud de yang rgyun chags shing 'brel ba yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2227: gzhi shes par byed pas mar 'brel /
NK067(ju)002:2228: 'bras bu thob par byed pas yar 'brel /
NK067(ju)002:2229: gzhi 'bras bar gyi shes thob bya byed 'brel ba can du gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:2231: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK067(ju)002:2232: sems lnga skyes par bstan pa yin //
NK067(ju)002:2233: zhes pas sems lnga'i sgo nas lam gyi ngo bo skye ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:2234: de la sems skye tshul la'ang gsum ste /
NK067(ju)002:2235: gzhi yi sa nas sems skye ba ni lam gang
NK067(ju)002:2236: du yang ma zhugs pa'i sa nas skye ba dang
NK067(ju)002:2237: / lam las skye ba ni nyan rang sogs kyi
NK067(ju)002:2238: theg pa la zhugs nas slar lam de bor nas
NK067(ju)002:2240: 'bras bu'i dus skye ba ni theg pa 'og ma'i 'bras bu'i bar du bslabs nas /
NK067(ju)002:2241: de nas sngags lam 'dir 'jug pa rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:2244: gong ma'i yon tan mthong bas de la 'jug 'dod
NK067(ju)002:2245: kyi sems dang por skyes pa g.yo ldang byang chub
NK067(ju)002:2246: kyi sems / theg pa de'i yon tan thob na snyam pa smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)002:2247: de la 'jug pa 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems yin la /
NK067(ju)002:2248: de la gnas pa gnas pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)002:2249: de'i 'bras bu thob pa mthar phyin byang chub kyi sems /
NK067(ju)002:2250: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor bla med 'di ni khyad par can gyi rgyu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2251: nye ba'i lam mam thabs rgyud yin la /
NK067(ju)002:2252: khyad par rgyud ces pa theg chen dbu ma sogs
NK067(ju)002:2253: la bden gnyis zung 'jug zer kyang rnal ma'i don
NK067(ju)002:2254: ma myong / thabs bde ba chen po'i khyad par med pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:2255: nye ba'i lam zhes pa lam 'di nyid la zhugs
NK067(ju)002:2256: nas theg pa gzhan snon mi dgos par 'di nyid
NK067(ju)002:2257: kho nas 'bras bu la sbyor bas so //
NK067(ju)002:2259: theg pa gzhan du dug gsum spang byar byed la /
NK067(ju)002:2260: 'dir dmigs med lta ba'i gzer gyi 'dod chags bde stong /
NK067(ju)002:2262: gti mug rig stong gi ngo bor lam du khyer
NK067(ju)002:2263: nas dug gsum ma spangs par sangs rgyas pa'i thabs
NK067(ju)002:2265: khyad par gyi lam de la dbye na gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:2267: grol lam le'u bcu gsum pa las rdzogs par bstan pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2270: ngo mtshar ngan 'gror thar pa'i thabs //
NK067(ju)002:2271: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK067(ju)002:2272: sgyu mar snang ba mig g.yor tshul //
NK067(ju)002:2273: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK067(ju)002:2274: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK067(ju)002:2276: bcing byed kyi las la spyad pas grol ba'i 'bras bu thob ba ni thabs lam yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2277: de yang dug gsum ma spangs pa'i thog bardzisa kyi spyod pa'i brtul zhugs te /
NK067(ju)002:2280: rna bar chu ni zhugs gyur na //
NK067(ju)002:2281: chu nyid kyis ni 'don par bya //
NK067(ju)002:2283: slar yang chu snon ma blugs nas bton pas thon 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK067(ju)002:2284: dug gsum la lta ba'i gdengs dang ldan pas spyad
NK067(ju)002:2285: na mi 'ching bar ma zad grol ba'i 'bras bu
NK067(ju)002:2287: dngul chu'i sbyor bas lcags khams yud tsam gyis gser du bsgyur ba bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:2288: de yang khe nyen gnyis ka'i dper mtshungs te /
NK067(ju)002:2289: de nyid dngul chu'i sbyor ba la mkhas pa zhig
NK067(ju)002:2290: gis gnas skabs lnga'i sgo nas lcags gser du 'gyur
NK067(ju)002:2291: la / sbyor ba mi shes pa zha ga gis
NK067(ju)002:2292: byas na gser du mi 'gyur ba'i thog dngul chu
NK067(ju)002:2293: yang chud zos su 'gro ba bzhin /
NK067(ju)002:2294: thabs dang mi ldan pa'i sbyor sgrol gyi las la
NK067(ju)002:2295: spyad pas grol ba'i 'bras bu mi thob par ma
NK067(ju)002:2296: zad ngan song du ltung ba'i nyen chen po yod
NK067(ju)002:2297: do // thabs lam de la dbye na gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:2298: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK067(ju)002:2300: steng sgo dang 'og sgo gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2302: steng sgo 'khor lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor bas sogs te /
NK067(ju)002:2304: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK067(ju)002:2305: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK067(ju)002:2306: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK067(ju)002:2308: 'khor lo gsum gnyis drug yin cing //
NK067(ju)002:2309: srong shing gsum ni rtsa dbu rkyang ro gsum ste /
NK067(ju)002:2310: lus kyi dbus su srog shing ltar gnas pa de
NK067(ju)002:2311: la brten nas spyi bo'i 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab so
NK067(ju)002:2312: gnyis / mgrin par brgyad gnyis bcu drug /
NK067(ju)002:2314: lte bar drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:2315: de'i 'og tu sbar bya me'i 'khor lo gru gsum ram gyis mtshan pa /
NK067(ju)002:2316: de'i 'og tu sbar byed rlung gi 'khor lo gzhu'i dbyibs yam gis mtshan pa dang drug gnas shing /
NK067(ju)002:2317: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK067(ju)002:2318: zhes pa steng rlung mnan pa lte 'og tu sleb pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2319: 'og rlung bskums pa'i rkyen gyis sum mdo'i rlung dang
NK067(ju)002:2320: bcas rlung gi dkyil 'khor g.yos pas me yi dkyil
NK067(ju)002:2321: 'khor sbar / me rlung gnyis dbu ma'i lam brgyud
NK067(ju)002:2322: nas spyi bo'i ham yig nam mkha'i ba zhes tha
NK067(ju)002:2324: ba las 'o ma 'jo ba ltar ham yig las
NK067(ju)002:2325: byang sems dngul chu'i rdog pa ltar 'dzag pas spyi
NK067(ju)002:2328: de bzhin mgrin pa snying ga lte ba rnams su
NK067(ju)002:2329: babs pas dga' bzhi'i ye shes skye ba la bslab
NK067(ju)002:2330: pa ni / thabs lam steng sgo'i lam rim gyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2331: de la spyi dang khyad par gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2332: khyad par ba ni le'u bcu gsum pa'i dngos bstan sgra ji bzhin pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2333: gnyis pa thabs lam 'og sgo mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas zhes pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2334: 'di nyid kyi le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2335: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK067(ju)002:2336: dbye ba'am yang na mi dbye bar //
NK067(ju)002:2337: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK067(ju)002:2338: sgrub pa ni sgrub chen po //
NK067(ju)002:2340: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK067(ju)002:2342: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i sgo nas ston pa la /
NK067(ju)002:2343: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i yum btsal ba dang brtag pa sogs bsnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK067(ju)002:2344: brda bzhis bskul te phyag rgya bzhi dang 'du shes
NK067(ju)002:2345: gsum ldan gyi snyoms par 'jug pa ni nye bar
NK067(ju)002:2347: de nas byang sems spyi bo nas mgrin pa snying
NK067(ju)002:2348: ga lte ba rnams su rim gyi dbab pas dga'
NK067(ju)002:2349: bzhi'i rim pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes dbab
NK067(ju)002:2350: bzung gi sbyor bas nyams su myong ba sgrub pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2351: yan lag / de nas byang sems ldog khyab kyi
NK067(ju)002:2352: sbyor bas dkar dmar ro gcig tu 'dres pa yum
NK067(ju)002:2353: gyi rtsa kha kha mu kha'i rtse nas gyen du
NK067(ju)002:2354: ldog pa lte ba nas spyi bo'i bar du khyab
NK067(ju)002:2355: pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong
NK067(ju)002:2356: ba ni sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag ste /
NK067(ju)002:2357: skad cig la bde stong gi ye shes btsan thabs
NK067(ju)002:2358: su skyes pas sa lam cig chod du rdzogs pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2359: thabs lam cig car ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:2361: phun sum tshogs pa lhun grub rnams //
NK067(ju)002:2362: gsang dbang mchog gis sbyin bar byed //
NK067(ju)002:2366: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK067(ju)002:2367: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor bas //
NK067(ju)002:2368: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK067(ju)002:2370: gtso bo shes rab rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas sogs te /
NK067(ju)002:2371: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis gsung rab kyi mtha' rgya bcad nas thos pa'i rgya mtsho bsags /
NK067(ju)002:2372: bsam pa'i shes rab kyis thos don bsam pas dpyad cing brtags la /
NK067(ju)002:2373: sgom pa'i shes rab kyi sems nyid rnal ma'i don
NK067(ju)002:2374: la ma bcos par mnyam par gzhag pas rang rgyud
NK067(ju)002:2375: kyi 'ching ba rang sangs su song nas chos nyid
NK067(ju)002:2376: kyi klong du grol ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:2377: khe nyen chung ba rin po che koo stu b+ha zhes pa de dang mtshungs la /
NK067(ju)002:2378: de ni rdo phal pa dang lhan cig tu bzhag na /
NK067(ju)002:2379: de rim gyis rin po che'i rigs su 'gyur la /
NK067(ju)002:2380: grol lam yang de dang 'dra bas thabs lam lta
NK067(ju)002:2381: bu'i myur khyad med kyang 'bras bur sbyor ba la
NK067(ju)002:2383: de la dbye na rim gyis pa dang cig car ba gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2384: dbang po yang rab kyis rtogs goms thams cad dbyer med gcig chod du byed pa zhig yod de /
NK067(ju)002:2385: de ni cig car ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:2386: dbang dus su grol ba in+d+ra b+hu ti lta bu'o //
NK067(ju)002:2387: rim gyis rtogs goms thams cad mthar phyin par byed pa ni rim gyis pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2391: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK067(ju)002:2392: nus mthu can du gang 'gyur ba //
NK067(ju)002:2393: rig 'dzin rgya ba'i zhing du grags //
NK067(ju)002:2395: dang po rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK067(ju)002:2396: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK067(ju)002:2397: lam 'gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:2400: gang gi dmigs med mi shes pa //
NK067(ju)002:2402: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK067(ju)002:2405: gzhi dang gtan tshigs grub pa'i don //
NK067(ju)002:2407: gzhal bya 'jal byed kyis lta ba gtan la phab pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2408: gzhal bya ni 'khor 'das gnyis so sor zhen pa'i zhen pa sgro btags dang bcas pa yin la /
NK067(ju)002:2411: de nyid dngos lnga tshul dang tshig /
NK067(ju)002:2412: ces pas le'u bdun pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2413: e ma ho ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK067(ju)002:2415: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK067(ju)002:2416: zhes pas chos sku skye med don gyi gsung bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2417: gsung gcig dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK067(ju)002:2419: thams cad gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK067(ju)002:2420: ces pas longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2421: rgyud mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK067(ju)002:2423: ji skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK067(ju)002:2424: zhes pas mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2425: theg pa mchog dman thams cad dang //
NK067(ju)002:2427: gsungs pa nyid na brjod du med //
NK067(ju)002:2428: ces pas dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2429: brjod med de nyid sna tshogs sgra //
NK067(ju)002:2431: de ni gsung mchog rgyal po yin //
NK067(ju)002:2432: zhes pas sprul sku tshangs pa dbyangs kyi gsung bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2434: sngon byung dngos lnga'i gtan tshigs //
NK067(ju)002:2436: tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs dang gsum las //
NK067(ju)002:2438: ston pa chos kyi skus 'khor ye shes rgya mtsho
NK067(ju)002:2439: la skye med don gyi gsung gis brda sprod pa
NK067(ju)002:2440: dang / longs skus 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho la dgongs pa brda'i gsung gis brda sprod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2441: sprul skus 'khor mos pa rgya mtsho la brjod pa tshig gi gsung gis brda sprod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2442: rdo rje'i skus dbyer med rdo rje'i 'khor la rdo rje'i gsung gis brda sprod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2443: mngon byang gi skus 'khor rgyal ba rgya mtsho la
NK067(ju)002:2444: rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung gis brda sprod pa
NK067(ju)002:2445: ste / sngon byung du ston pa sku lngas rang
NK067(ju)002:2446: rang gi 'khor lnga la gsung lnga'i sgo nas chos
NK067(ju)002:2447: nyid kyi don dngos su gtan la phab pa ni
NK067(ju)002:2450: yang dag rdzogs sangs rgyas ston pa //
NK067(ju)002:2452: gsung lnga bstan pas de kho na //
NK067(ju)002:2455: gnyis pa rjes 'jug tshul lnga'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)002:2456: le'u bdun pa'i gong gi 'phro las /
NK067(ju)002:2457: theg pa mchog dman bsam yas kyang //
NK067(ju)002:2459: gdul bya'i thabs su so sor thos //
NK067(ju)002:2460: zhes pas gsung gi byed las bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2461: ji ltar gsung rab kun brjod kyang //
NK067(ju)002:2463: dper na brag cha'i sgra bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:2464: zhes pas gsung gi rnam grangs bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2465: sku lnga de dag gi gsung lnga dang tshul mthun pa'i brda don te /
NK067(ju)002:2466: skye med mtshon pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2467: sgrib pa ngos 'dzin pa me long nang gi byad gzugs lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2468: rang rig mngon gsal rang gsal nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2469: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung mtshon pa grags stong dbyer med brag cha lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2470: brjod pa tshig gi gsung mtshon pa kun yid 'jug pa tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi sgra lta bu ste /
NK067(ju)002:2472: brjod dang 'dra ba'i brda sprod pas //
NK067(ju)002:2473: ngo bo nyid kyis bshad pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)002:2474: ma 'ongs don du gtan tshigs nges //
NK067(ju)002:2476: gsum pa tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)002:2477: sngar gyi tshig lnga po de tshig tu dngos su brjod pa ni tshig lnga'i gtan tshigs te /
NK067(ju)002:2479: ngo bo snang tshig rang snang tshig /
NK067(ju)002:2480: ldem dgongs tshig dang bkri drang tshig /
NK067(ju)002:2481: 'dod rkyen tshig dang rdo rje'i tshig /
NK067(ju)002:2482: rang rig mngon gsal tshig gis mtshon //
NK067(ju)002:2484: de rnams bsdu na dpyad du med pas go ba sku bzhi'i gtan tshigs te /
NK067(ju)002:2485: brtag dpyad la ma ltos par don go ba'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)002:2486: dpyad du yod pas go ba ni sprul sku'i gtan tshigs te /
NK067(ju)002:2487: brtag dpyad la brten nas don go dgos pa'i phyir te /
NK067(ju)002:2489: de ltar mod kyang bsdu na gnyis //
NK067(ju)002:2490: bzhi rjes mi dpyod gcig rjes dpyod //
NK067(ju)002:2492: de ltar dpyad du yod pa sprul sku'i gtan tshigs la tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshigs dang /
NK067(ju)002:2493: sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2496: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs /
NK067(ju)002:2498: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs dang bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:2500: 'di nyid kyi le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2501: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK067(ju)002:2502: byin gyis brlabsa dang mngon sum par //
NK067(ju)002:2503: rab tu rtogs pa bzhi po yis //
NK067(ju)002:2504: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK067(ju)002:2506: rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis chos thams cad bden
NK067(ju)002:2507: pa dbyer med du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa
NK067(ju)002:2508: ste / de yang 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba'i gnyis 'dzin gyi zhen pa de /
NK067(ju)002:2509: gnyis med ye shes su gtan la 'bebs par byed pa la rgyu gcig 1pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2512: mngon sum pa'i gtan 4tshigs rnams kyis gzhal bas /
NK067(ju)002:2517: mtshan nyid blo bral 4du gtan la pheb pa grub mtha' yin la /
NK067(ju)002:2519: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi chos so cog chos can sems
NK067(ju)002:2520: nyid rang byung gi ye shes kyi dbyings su rgyu
NK067(ju)002:2522: de rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa gnyis kyis 'khor 'das gnyis so sor snang ba tsam las /
NK067(ju)002:2523: gnyis su ma grub pa'i phyir rang bzhin skye med du gtan la phab /
NK067(ju)002:2524: de ni rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK067(ju)002:2525: rang bzhin skye med chos can /
NK067(ju)002:2526: sems nyid skye ba med pa de yi gdangs rtsal 'gags pa med pa /
NK067(ju)002:2527: sku dang ye shes su rang snang ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:2528: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid mtshon byed
NK067(ju)002:2529: yi ge du mar snang ba'i mtshon pa'i phyir rol
NK067(ju)002:2530: pa 'gags pa med par gtan la phab /
NK067(ju)002:2531: rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gags med gnyis chos can /
NK067(ju)002:2532: de gnyis ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs pa'i byin rlabs shugs las 'byung ba yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2533: lhag pa don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:2534: de'i snang cha snod bcud sku dang ye shes su
NK067(ju)002:2535: rang snang ba'i ngo bo dbyer med du gtan la
NK067(ju)002:2536: phab / ngo bo dbyer med de yang rang rig
NK067(ju)002:2537: mngon sum du yul med rang gsal bsam brjod dang
NK067(ju)002:2538: bral bar rtogs pa'i phyir mtshan nyid blo bral du
NK067(ju)002:2539: phab / gtan la phab / gtan tshigs bzhi po
NK067(ju)002:2540: des gzhal bas chos thams cad rang rig mngon sum
NK067(ju)002:2541: du rdzogs par gtan la phab pas dag pa rab
NK067(ju)002:2542: 'byams kyi snang ba la dbang bsgyur bas na rgyal
NK067(ju)002:2544: gnyis pa dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)002:2546: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK067(ju)002:2548: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams chos can /
NK067(ju)002:2549: ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs pa yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2550: dag pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:2552: snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar rnam par dag pa /
NK067(ju)002:2553: bcud phung pho lnga yab lngar rnam par dag pa /
NK067(ju)002:2554: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:2558: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK067(ju)002:2559: rnam dag bla med theg pa'i mchog /
NK067(ju)002:2560: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:2561: gsum pa mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)002:2563: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK067(ju)002:2564: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK067(ju)002:2566: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams chos can /
NK067(ju)002:2567: ye nas chos kyi skur sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2568: mnyam pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:2569: dang po thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK067(ju)002:2570: mi la mir snang ba la yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK067(ju)002:2571: tho yor la mir snang ba log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis ka snang ba sgyu mar mnyam pa1dang /
NK067(ju)002:2572: myu gu bdag las mi skye bar rtog pa phyogs gcig chod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2573: myu gu bdag las kyang mi skye /
NK067(ju)002:2574: gzhan las kyang mi skye ba mtha' bzhi'i spros pa
NK067(ju)002:2575: chod pa de gnyis ka skye med du mnyam 2pa
NK067(ju)002:2576: ni / thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis so //
NK067(ju)002:2577: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK067(ju)002:2578: snang la don byed nus pa yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK067(ju)002:2579: don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis
NK067(ju)002:2580: ka sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam
NK067(ju)002:2581: 1pa dang / chos thams cad rang gi ngo bos
NK067(ju)002:2582: stong pa'i med dgag gi stong nyid rnam grangs pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2583: 1pa dang / don dam dang / sems nyid khas
NK067(ju)002:2584: len thams cad dang bral ba'i dbyings ye shes zung
NK067(ju)002:2585: 'jug ma yin dgag gi stong nyid rnam grangs ma
NK067(ju)002:2587: gnyis ka don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du
NK067(ju)002:2588: lhun gyis grub pa ni lhag pa'i mnyam 2pa gnyis
NK067(ju)002:2589: so // de'ang le'u gsum pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2590: a hoh srid rtsa'i nyes dmigs bdag tu rtog las 'phros //
NK067(ju)002:2592: gzhan na med de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK067(ju)002:2593: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2594: bzhi pa bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)002:2596: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK067(ju)002:2598: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK067(ju)002:2600: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad chos can snang lugs
NK067(ju)002:2601: la du mar snang yang yin lugs la de ltar
NK067(ju)002:2602: ma yin te / sems nyid skye med rang byung
NK067(ju)002:2603: gi ye shes chen po gcig gi bdag nyid du
NK067(ju)002:2604: ye nas gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:2605: gnyis pa sgra mthun don spags kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK067(ju)002:2606: thun mong gi theg par dug lnga spong sbyong byed pa de /
NK067(ju)002:2607: theg pa 'dir rang bzhin ma grub par blta bas don spags pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2608: de gtan tshigs kyis bsgrub na /
NK067(ju)002:2610: yang dag par ma grub ste /
NK067(ju)002:2611: rang rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i phyir zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK067(ju)002:2612: de ltar 'jal byed gtan tshigs rnams kyi gtan la
NK067(ju)002:2613: phab pas rang bzhin rgyu'i rgyud gnas lugs kyi don
NK067(ju)002:2614: mngon sum du rtogs pa ni grub mtha' ste /
NK067(ju)002:2616: rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK067(ju)002:2617: sgra rten yid la byed min par //
NK067(ju)002:2618: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral ba //
NK067(ju)002:2619: rang gsal gsum bral mi bsgul bar //
NK067(ju)002:2620: nges par gdengs su gang byas pa //
NK067(ju)002:2621: thos bsam brten pas lta mthar phyin //
NK067(ju)002:2624: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK067(ju)002:2625: rnal 'byor sa la sleb pa yin //
NK067(ju)002:2627: gang dag sngags kyi grub mtha' ni /
NK067(ju)002:2628: thabs kho nas khyad par du 'phags so //
NK067(ju)002:2631: rgyu'i theg chen gyis bden gnyis zung 'jug tsam bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)002:2632: snod bcud dag mnyam chen por sku dang ye shes
NK067(ju)002:2633: kyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs pa sngags kyi thun mong
NK067(ju)002:2634: ma yin pa'i lta ba yin la /
NK067(ju)002:2635: khas len thams cad dang bral ba'i gnas lugs de bzhin nyid rgyu'i theg chen du bshad pa /
NK067(ju)002:2636: sngags su rgyu'i rgyud du bzhag kyang /
NK067(ju)002:2637: de la mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen pos khyad par du byas pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2638: sngags kyi lta ba'i khyad par yin no //
NK067(ju)002:2639: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)002:2640: mos sgom dang nges rdzogs gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2642: don spyi'i rnam pa mos pa lam byed tsam bya ba yin /
NK067(ju)002:2644: lam so so'i ting nge 'dzin nyams lnga mthar phyin pa la bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2646: bi ma la'i phyag rgya bsam gtan gyi 'grel bar /
NK067(ju)002:2647: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lnga //
NK067(ju)002:2648: bsam gtan nyams kyi skye tshul yin //
NK067(ju)002:2650: de la dang po g.yo ba'i nyams ni /
NK067(ju)002:2651: gnas pa dang po ri gzar gyi 'bab chu ltar
NK067(ju)002:2652: sems skad cig kyang mi gnas par rnam rtog sngar
NK067(ju)002:2653: bas mang du song ba lta bu ste /
NK067(ju)002:2654: de yang mang du song ba ma yin te /
NK067(ju)002:2655: sngar rnam rtog la rtsis gdab ma byas pas ma tshor ba /
NK067(ju)002:2656: da de'i ngos zin pas cung zad sems zin pa'i 'bras bu'o gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:2657: gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams ni /
NK067(ju)002:2658: de la skyon yon du ma bltas pas rgyun mthud de bsgoms pas /
NK067(ju)002:2659: dpe rong khung dog po'i 'bab chu lta bu ste /
NK067(ju)002:2660: rnam rtog 'phro mu nas yud tsam re rtog med
NK067(ju)002:2661: du zhi mal le gnas pa zhig 'byung ste thob
NK067(ju)002:2662: pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog ngal sos pa'i nyams zhes
NK067(ju)002:2663: bya'o // gsum pa goms pa'i nyams ni /
NK067(ju)002:2664: de'i rgyun mthud de bsgoms pas /
NK067(ju)002:2665: dpe rgan pos byis pa'i rtsed mo la lad mo
NK067(ju)002:2666: byed mi nus pa rgan po'i spyod pa lta bu
NK067(ju)002:2667: ste / phal cher rtog med du gnas pa las res 'ga' rtog pa yud tsam re 'byung ste /
NK067(ju)002:2668: goms pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog gi thang chad pa'i nyams zhes bya gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:2669: bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams ni /
NK067(ju)002:2670: de nas kyang yun bsrings te bsgoms pas /
NK067(ju)002:2671: dpe mtsho chung ser bus bskyod pa ltar /
NK067(ju)002:2672: phal cher rtog med du 'byams su nyal le gsal
NK067(ju)002:2673: sing nger gnas pa las rkyen drag pos cung zad
NK067(ju)002:2674: g.yo ba de / brtan pa'i nyams sam rnam rtog gis bskyod du yod pa'i nyams zhes bya'o gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:2675: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams ni /
NK067(ju)002:2677: dpe mtsho chen rlabs dang bral ba'am ri bo chen
NK067(ju)002:2678: po ltar gnas pa la rkyen gang gis kyang gnod
NK067(ju)002:2679: mi nus par ma zad slar la bogs 'byin zhing
NK067(ju)002:2680: / btang 'gro bzhag sdod rang dbang du 'byor bas
NK067(ju)002:2681: mthar phyin pa'i nyams sam rang dbang du 'byor ba'i
NK067(ju)002:2682: / nyams zhes bya'o // nges rdzogs kyi lam 'di cung zad bshad na /
NK067(ju)002:2684: srid pa rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK067(ju)002:2685: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK067(ju)002:2686: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK067(ju)002:2687: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK067(ju)002:2688: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK067(ju)002:2689: skye ba'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK067(ju)002:2691: skye 'chi bar do gsum sbyang ba'i lam rdzogs par bstan pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2692: 'chi ba 'od gsal dang mthun pa'i lam stong pa chen po /
NK067(ju)002:2693: bar do dang mthun pa'i lam snying rje sgyu ma /
NK067(ju)002:2694: skye ba'i rim pa gsum po dang mthun par phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK067(ju)002:2696: tshom bu tshogs sgrub dang lnga las /
NK067(ju)002:2697: de nyid rags pa bskyed rim gyis sbyong ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:2698: phra ba rdzogs rim gyis sbyong tshul gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2699: dang po bskyed rim gyis sbyong tshul la lnga las /
NK067(ju)002:2700: dang po 'chi srid kyi bag chags sbyong byed stong pa chen po'i lam bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2702: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK067(ju)002:2703: rtogs pas dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK067(ju)002:2705: gang gis glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK067(ju)002:2706: mnyam par bzhag pas btul nas su //
NK067(ju)002:2710: sbyong byed lam bshad pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2712: lus can rnams 'chi ba'i tshe phyi nang gi thim
NK067(ju)002:2713: rim rnams rdzogs pa'i mthar 'chi srid chos sku'i 'od
NK067(ju)002:2715: snang ba thim dang rtog pa thim /
NK067(ju)002:2716: phra ba thim dang rags pa thim //
NK067(ju)002:2717: thim pa'i rjes la goms pa yi //
NK067(ju)002:2720: phra rags thim lugs mang du gsungs kyang /
NK067(ju)002:2721: dang po sa chu la thim pas /
NK067(ju)002:2722: phyi rtags lus bsgul bskyon mi nus shing zung mi thub /
NK067(ju)002:2723: lus sa la bying snyam byed /
NK067(ju)002:2724: nang rtags su smig rgyu lta bu sngo mer mer ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:2726: char zim dang chu g.yo ba lta bu 'byung /
NK067(ju)002:2728: phyi rtags kha sna skam zhing lce rkan phug tu 'gro /
NK067(ju)002:2729: nang rtags du ba 'phyur ba dang du ldang chags pa lta bu 'byung /
NK067(ju)002:2731: phyi'i rtags su lus kyi drod mtha' nas yal zhing /
NK067(ju)002:2733: nang rtags srin bu me khyer lta bu dmar tsig tsig dmar phrom phrom 'byung /
NK067(ju)002:2734: rlung rnam shes la thim pas /
NK067(ju)002:2735: phyi rtags su dbugs phyir ring du rgyu zhing /
NK067(ju)002:2736: nang du sdud mi shes pas rags pas rgyu ba chad /
NK067(ju)002:2738: sgron me'i phreng ba lta bu 'byung /
NK067(ju)002:2739: de ltar thim rim de rnams lus kyi gnas su
NK067(ju)002:2740: sa la sogs pa'i 'byung ba rnams med par 'gyur
NK067(ju)002:2741: ba'am gnas 'pho ba'i don ma yin /
NK067(ju)002:2742: dbu ma'i ye shes kyi rlung stobs su gyur bas 'byung ba so so'i las rlung bcom pas /
NK067(ju)002:2743: rten thim pas brten pa yang nges par thim pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2744: sra ba sogs su snang ba'i rnam shes sogs rang
NK067(ju)002:2745: gi bag chags dbu ma la bzhag pas 'gags te
NK067(ju)002:2746: / rus pa sogs sra ba shas che ba'i khams
NK067(ju)002:2747: rten rlung dang brten pa rnam shes bral bar byas
NK067(ju)002:2748: / te / sa'i dwangs ma chu'i dwangs ma sogs la thim pa'i don yin /
NK067(ju)002:2749: rlung rnam shes la thim pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2750: rlung gi dwangs mas srog rtsa rags pa'i bar gyi
NK067(ju)002:2751: lus thams cad dor bas srog rtsa'i nang gi 'od
NK067(ju)002:2752: lnga'i sbu gu can gyi rtsa lnga la zhugs nas
NK067(ju)002:2753: yid kyi snang ba dang ro gcig tu 'dres pa
NK067(ju)002:2754: yin / rnam shes nam mkha' la thim pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2755: rnam shes dngos med du gyur pa'i don ma yin /
NK067(ju)002:2756: rnam shes mkha' ltar dwangs shing mtshon du med pa'i don yin /
NK067(ju)002:2757: de ltar phra rags nyer lnga thim rjes /
NK067(ju)002:2758: dbu ma'i yar sne'i khams dkar cha'i dwangs ma thur
NK067(ju)002:2759: du babs nas snying gar sleb pa na thabs kyi
NK067(ju)002:2760: rang bzhin zhe sdang las gyur ba'i rtog pa so
NK067(ju)002:2761: gsum 'gags / de'i tshe khams dkar po dang 'brel
NK067(ju)002:2762: ba'i dbang gis phyi rtags su nam mkha' la zla
NK067(ju)002:2763: 'od kyi khyab pa lta bu skya lam pa 'byung
NK067(ju)002:2764: gsum 'gags / / gzung ba'i rnam rtog rags pa bral ba stong pa'i 'od gsal /
NK067(ju)002:2765: sems shin tu gsal bar snang bas na snang ba'i
NK067(ju)002:2766: ye shes zhes bya ba skad cig ma dang po'o
NK067(ju)002:2767: // de nas dbu ma'i mar sne khams dmar cha
NK067(ju)002:2768: gyen du song nas snang ba'i ye shes mched pa
NK067(ju)002:2769: la thim pas shes rab kyi rang bzhin 'dod chags
NK067(ju)002:2770: las gyur pa'i rtog pa bzhi bcu 'gags /
NK067(ju)002:2771: de'i tshe khams dmar po dang 'brel ba'i dbang gis
NK067(ju)002:2772: phyi rtags nam mkha' la nyi 'od khyab pa bzhin
NK067(ju)002:2774: 'dzin pa'i rnam rtog rags pa bral bas ches stong pa'i 'od gsal /
NK067(ju)002:2775: sems shin tu gsal bar snang bas snang ba mched
NK067(ju)002:2776: pa'i ye shes zhes bya ba skad cig ma gnyis
NK067(ju)002:2777: pa'o // dwangs ma dkar dmar snying gar 'phrad pas mched pa'i ye shes thob pa la thim /
NK067(ju)002:2778: gti mug gi rtog pa bdun 'gags /
NK067(ju)002:2779: dkar dmar gyi nus pa dbyings su yal te /
NK067(ju)002:2780: srog rlung gi cha shas lus pa'i dbang gis phyi
NK067(ju)002:2781: rtags su nam mkha' la mun nag gis khyab pa
NK067(ju)002:2783: shin tu phra ba'i gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams
NK067(ju)002:2784: cad dang bral bas stong pa chen po'i 'od gsal
NK067(ju)002:2785: / gnyis 'dzin gyi mtshan ma thams cad dang bral
NK067(ju)002:2786: bas sems 'gags pa la nye bas thob pa'i ye
NK067(ju)002:2787: shes zhes bya ba skad cig ma gsum pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:2788: de nas snying ga'i rtsa dar dkar gyi skud pa
NK067(ju)002:2789: 'dra ba'i nang du a ham rdzogs par thim pas
NK067(ju)002:2790: thob pa'i ye shes kyang 'chi ba 'od gsal la
NK067(ju)002:2791: thim pas / tshe 'dis bsdus pa'i rnam rtog dang
NK067(ju)002:2792: kun rdzob kyi bag chags thams cad 'od gsal du
NK067(ju)002:2793: thim pas / thim / tshe rabs gzhan gyis bsdus pa rnams ma shar /
NK067(ju)002:2794: re zhig gzung 'dzin gyi snang ba dang snang ba
NK067(ju)002:2795: gsum yang 'gags pas phyi rtags su rkyen bral gyi
NK067(ju)002:2796: nam mkha' g.ya' dag pa lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2797: nang rtags su rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin la yud tsam gnas pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2798: thams cad stong pa'i 'od gsal nye bar thob pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2799: ye shes zhes bya ba skad cig ma bzhi pa
NK067(ju)002:2800: yin la de yan ni sbyang bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:2801: gnyis pa sbyong byed kyi lam ni /
NK067(ju)002:2802: 'chi srid chos sku'i 'od gsal de nyid lam du 'khyer nas 'chi srid dag pa chos sku'o //
NK067(ju)002:2803: snyam pa'i gzhi 'bras sbrel ba'i nga rgyal dang bcas te /
NK067(ju)002:2804: snang grags 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK067(ju)002:2805: stong nyid spros bral de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge
NK067(ju)002:2807: stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor yin la /
NK067(ju)002:2808: de bsgoms pas mar 'chi ba'i bag chags dag 1par byed /
NK067(ju)002:2809: yar chos sku spros bral gyi rigs kyi nus pa gsos 'debs pas 'bras bur rdzogs 2par byed /
NK067(ju)002:2810: bar du don gyi 'od gsal rgyud la skye ba'i
NK067(ju)002:2811: gzhi bting bas lam gong ma'i smin byed du 3'gro
NK067(ju)002:2812: // gnyis pa bar do dang rjes su mthun pa snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK067(ju)002:2814: rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK067(ju)002:2815: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK067(ju)002:2817: de la'ang gnyis te sbyang bya 'chi srid chos sku'i
NK067(ju)002:2818: 'od gsal de nyid ngos ma zin par nub pa'i
NK067(ju)002:2819: skad cig la / phyi ma'i bag chags sad byed kyi rkyen ci rigs pas bskul nas /
NK067(ju)002:2820: rlung sems phra ba'i 'byung bzhi dang bcas pa'i bar
NK067(ju)002:2821: do'i gzugs dwangs shing thogs med par 'grub par byed
NK067(ju)002:2824: gnyis pa kun snang nam mkha'i dang //
NK067(ju)002:2825: snying rje gsum gyi khyab pa'i phyir //
NK067(ju)002:2826: khyab bdag chen po'i ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK067(ju)002:2828: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba rnams la
NK067(ju)002:2829: 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje mkha' khyab
NK067(ju)002:2830: tu bsgom pa ni snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor
NK067(ju)002:2831: te / lam 'dis mar bar do'i yid lus sgyu ma lta bu'i bag chags dag par 1byed /
NK067(ju)002:2832: yar chos sku spros bral las longs sku mtshan dpes
NK067(ju)002:2833: brgyan pa'i rigs kyi nus pa gsos 'debs pas 'bras
NK067(ju)002:2835: bar du don gyi 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi
NK067(ju)002:2836: lha skur ldang ba'i mtshams sbyor snying rje chen po
NK067(ju)002:2837: rgyud la skye ba'i gzhi 'ding bas lam gong ma'i
NK067(ju)002:2839: gsum pa skye ba'i rim pa gsum sbyong byed phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK067(ju)002:2841: tshom bu tshogs sgrub gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:2842: dang po phyag rgya gcig pa la'ang phra rags gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2843: dang po phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2845: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK067(ju)002:2846: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK067(ju)002:2849: sbyang bya bar do'i sems can de phyi ma'i skye ba len par nye ba na /
NK067(ju)002:2850: skye gnas la sred pa skye ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:2851: bardzusa te skye na gnas la sred pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2852: drod gsher las skye na dro grang la sred pa skye /
NK067(ju)002:2853: sgo nga las skye na ro la sred pa skye /
NK067(ju)002:2854: mngal las skye na pha ma'i 'du 'phrod la sred pa skye /
NK067(ju)002:2855: gang du skye 'gyur gyi gnas der skad cig gis
NK067(ju)002:2856: 'jug ma rag gi bar do'i rlung sems de yin
NK067(ju)002:2857: la / sbyong byed kyi lam ni /
NK067(ju)002:2858: 'di nyid kyi le'u bzhi pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2860: rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK067(ju)002:2861: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams 'phros //
NK067(ju)002:2862: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK067(ju)002:2863: bsdus kyang 'phel 'grib med par brta na //
NK067(ju)002:2865: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa'i rang rig a
NK067(ju)002:2866: dkar po gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan par
NK067(ju)002:2867: bsgoms pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:2868: gnyis pa rags pa lha sku la bslab pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2870: thabs las thabs byung sogs nas /
NK067(ju)002:2871: 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK067(ju)002:2872: ces pa'i bar gyis 'og gi phyag rgya spros bcas kyang bstan /
NK067(ju)002:2874: sbyang bya bar do'i sems can de /
NK067(ju)002:2875: pha ma'i khu khrag gi dbus su zhugs pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2876: lus ngag yid gsum gyi rten khu rdul rlung gsum bskyed pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:2877: pha ma gnyis kyi reg pa sra ba de nyams su myong bas sa khams grub /
NK067(ju)002:2878: khu ba gsher bas chu khams grub /
NK067(ju)002:2879: bskyod pa las drod skye bas me khams grub /
NK067(ju)002:2880: rtsa gnas thams cad nas byang sems g.yo bas rlung khams grub /
NK067(ju)002:2881: chags pa'i bde bas nam mkha'i khams grub /
NK067(ju)002:2882: rnam shes ye shes kyi khams dang drug go //
NK067(ju)002:2883: de yang bdun dang po la mer mer po /
NK067(ju)002:2884: de nas rim par gnyis pa la nur nur /
NK067(ju)002:2885: gsum pa la tar tar po /
NK067(ju)002:2886: bzhi pa la dbyibs gsal bas gor gor te zhag nyer brgyad /
NK067(ju)002:2887: bdun phrag lnga pa'i mkhrang 'gyur gyi zhag dang po la /
NK067(ju)002:2888: ma dang 'brel ba'i lte bar rang sor phyed dang bcu gsum gyi tshad can gyi dbu ma chags /
NK067(ju)002:2889: de'i nang du srog rlung steng 'og gi sne gnyis su dkar dmar gyi thig le gnyis bcas grub /
NK067(ju)002:2890: zhag gnyis 20pa la rlung bcu'i rten snying ga'i rtsa 'khor chags /
NK067(ju)002:2891: de nas zhag re la rtsa nyis brgya re chags pas dbu rkyang ro gsum gyi rigs las /
NK067(ju)002:2892: rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis chags /
NK067(ju)002:2893: de nas lte ba'i rtsa 'khor chags nas nya yi rnam pa lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2894: de nas yan la dod pas ru sbal lta bu /
NK067(ju)002:2895: de nas rim par tshigs rnams kyi bar rtsa yi 'khor lo dang /
NK067(ju)002:2896: sha khrag rus tshig rnams chags te /
NK067(ju)002:2897: de yan chad du brgyal ba ltar snang med du gnas pa yin /
NK067(ju)002:2898: zla ba drug nas yid kyi rnam shes skye bas
NK067(ju)002:2899: sngon gyi skye ba dran pa sogs tshor ba myong
NK067(ju)002:2900: / bdun pa nas skra dang ba spu skye zhing dbang rten rnams kyang 'grub /
NK067(ju)002:2901: brgyad pa la dbang po rdzogs shing bkres skom dang ldan pas bshang gci 'byung /
NK067(ju)002:2902: dgu pa'i mthar sdug bsngal zhing skyo ba skye ste /
NK067(ju)002:2903: de ltar zla dgu zhag bcu nas btsa' ba yin no //
NK067(ju)002:2904: zhar la sems can spyi mthun gyi las snang du
NK067(ju)002:2905: grub pa'i 'byung bzhi'i dkyil 'khor ri rab bcas dang
NK067(ju)002:2906: sems can rnams rgyu zhing longs spyod pa'i gnas yul
NK067(ju)002:2907: dang khang khyim la sogs pa'i zhen rtog /
NK067(ju)002:2908: sbyong byed gzhal yas gling bzhir bshad pa bzhin bsgoms pas sbyangs la /
NK067(ju)002:2911: yul khang khyim gyi bag chags dag 1par byed /
NK067(ju)002:2912: yar sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag cing 'bras bu rdzogs 2par byed /
NK067(ju)002:2913: bar du 'byung rim gzhal yas bcas bsgoms pa des
NK067(ju)002:2914: lus kyi rtsa thig rlung gsum dul nas rdzogs rim
NK067(ju)002:2915: gyi ye shes rgyud la skye bas lam gong ma'i
NK067(ju)002:2917: gong du bshad pa'i sbyang bya de sbyong byed phyag
NK067(ju)002:2918: rgya gcig pa rags pa lha sku la bslab pa
NK067(ju)002:2919: ni / cho ga gsum bskyed dang /
NK067(ju)002:2920: mngon byang lnga bskyed gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:2922: gzhal yas khang gi dbus su gdan nyi mas rdul /
NK067(ju)002:2924: sa bon a yig gdan steng du babs pas bar
NK067(ju)002:2925: do'i rnam shes khu rdul sems gsum 'dres pa pha
NK067(ju)002:2926: ma'i 'du 'phrod kyi khams lnga nyams su myong ba
NK067(ju)002:2927: rigs so so'i sa bon phyag mtshan du gyur bas
NK067(ju)002:2929: mngal gyi lus de nyid rlung gis 'phel mes smin chus sdud sas sra bar byas /
NK067(ju)002:2930: nam mkhas go phyes nas phung khams skye mched grub pa de sbyong /
NK067(ju)002:2931: 'od kyi gong bu de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2932: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed pas mngal du lus grub pa'i bag chag sbyong bar byed /
NK067(ju)002:2933: gzhan sgong skyes la sogs kyi bag chags dang sbyar na sa bon gyis dri za'i sems /
NK067(ju)002:2934: phyag mtshan gyis khu khrag dbus su zhugs pa /
NK067(ju)002:2935: spro bsdu'i 'od kyi gong bus ni sgo nga /
NK067(ju)002:2936: drod gsher la gdan gyi nyi ma drod /
NK067(ju)002:2938: sa bon phyag mtshan ni bar do'i rnam shes spro bsdu dang /
NK067(ju)002:2939: sku yongs su rdzogs pas de gsum 'dus pa'i drod gsher gyi dbus su lus grub pa sbyong /
NK067(ju)002:2940: bardzusa skyes la gdan ni skye gnas /
NK067(ju)002:2941: sa bon phyag mtshan ni bar do'i rlung sems /
NK067(ju)002:2942: spro bsdu ni gnas lus la sred len gyi mthus gsos btab pa /
NK067(ju)002:2943: sku yongs su rdzogs pas ni lus skad cig gis 'grub pa ni sbyong ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:2944: gnyis pa mngon byang lnga bskyed pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:2945: khu ba mtshon byed zla ba me long ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:2946: rdul mtshon byed nyi ma mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:2947: dkar dmar gyi dbus su rnam shes zhugs pa mtshon byed sa bon phyag mtshan sor rtog ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:2948: khu rdul sems gsum gcig tu 'dres pa mtshon byed 'od zer spro bsdu bya grub ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:2949: mngal du lus grub pa dang sku yongs su rdzogs pa mtshon byed chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK067(ju)002:2950: de ltar phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha de bsgoms pas
NK067(ju)002:2951: mar ma'i mngal du zhugs pa nas btsa' ba'i bar
NK067(ju)002:2953: yar longs sku sprul skur shar ba'i lhums zhugs nas
NK067(ju)002:2954: bltams pa'i bar gyi 'bras bu 2 rdzogs par byed
NK067(ju)002:2955: / bar du snying rje chen po zung 'jug gi
NK067(ju)002:2956: lha skur snang ba'i gzhi bting bas lam gong ma'i
NK067(ju)002:2958: gnyis pa skye ba'i rim pa bar ma sbyong byed phyag rgya spros bcas la'ang /
NK067(ju)002:2962: zhal phyag spro ba dang bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:2963: dang po zhi ba la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa /
NK067(ju)002:2964: rigs lnga rigs chung yab yum lnga bcu /
NK067(ju)002:2965: sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug /
NK067(ju)002:2967: bya byed kun tu bzang po dang /
NK067(ju)002:2969: gnyis thub drug bcas brgyad cu rtsa gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:2970: 'bring po rigs lnga yab yum sems dpa' yab yum sgo ba yab yum /
NK067(ju)002:2971: bya byed thub drug bcas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:2972: bsdus pa rigs lnga yab yum bcu sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK067(ju)002:2973: khro bo la dkyil 'khor rgyas pa khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum rigs chung bcas lnga bcu /
NK067(ju)002:2974: gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK067(ju)002:2975: khro bcu yab yum nyi shu bcas brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK067(ju)002:2976: 'bring po khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum gnas yul
NK067(ju)002:2977: sgo skyong sogs sngar ltar bgrangs pas don brgyad bsdus
NK067(ju)002:2978: pa khro bcu yab yum nyi shu phri bas lnga
NK067(ju)002:2980: gnyis pa tshom bu spro ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:2981: 'di nyid kyi le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK067(ju)002:2982: lnga dang lnga yi sbyor ba yi //
NK067(ju)002:2984: tshom bu gcig pa'i lha rnams bsgom //
NK067(ju)002:2986: zhi ba la tshom bu gcig pa /
NK067(ju)002:2989: dang po mi bskyod pa yab yum la rdo rje'i rigs chung yab yum zung bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:2990: sgo ba yab yum brgyad dang bco brgyad ni tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:2991: dbus su mi bskyod pa yab yum dang /
NK067(ju)002:2992: shar nub tu rnam snang dang snang mtha' yab yum
NK067(ju)002:2993: bcas la rang rang gi rigs chung gis bskor bas
NK067(ju)002:2994: sum cu la khro bo bcu las steng 'og gi
NK067(ju)002:2995: khro bo spangs pas yab yum bcu drug bsnan pas
NK067(ju)002:2996: lha zhe drug ni tshom bu gsum pa /
NK067(ju)002:2997: rigs lnga po rigs chung dang bcas pa'i steng khro
NK067(ju)002:2998: bcu yab yum la nyi shu bsnan pas bdun cu
NK067(ju)002:3000: khro bo la yang le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3001: khro bo khro mo'i tshogs chen po //
NK067(ju)002:3003: dngos grub las rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK067(ju)002:3004: ces ba'i bar gyi bstan te /
NK067(ju)002:3005: gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo rnams kyi steng du
NK067(ju)002:3006: tshom bu gcig pa'i skabs su dbus su rdo rje
NK067(ju)002:3007: khrag 'thung yab yum la rdo rjee'i rigs chung khro
NK067(ju)002:3008: bo yab yum brgyad kyi mtha' bskor du khro bcu
NK067(ju)002:3009: yab yum nyi shu bsnan pas don brgyad /
NK067(ju)002:3010: tshom bu gsum par de'i steng du shar nub tu
NK067(ju)002:3011: bud+d+ha dang pad+ma khrag 'thung yab yum gnyis rigs chung
NK067(ju)002:3013: tshom bu lnga par de'i steng du lho byang du
NK067(ju)002:3014: rat+na dang karma khrag 'thung yab yum gnyis rigs chung
NK067(ju)002:3015: bcas bsnan pas lha brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK067(ju)002:3016: gsum pa grangs spro ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3017: snang ba rnam 'byed la bslab pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3018: de yang le'u brgyad pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3019: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK067(ju)002:3020: de nyid yan lag spros dag ste //
NK067(ju)002:3024: dang po zhi ba la'ang stong la bslab pa /
NK067(ju)002:3025: nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa /
NK067(ju)002:3026: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3027: dang po ni yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu rtsa
NK067(ju)002:3028: lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgom pa ste
NK067(ju)002:3029: / bdag nyid mi bskyod pa yab yum yab kyi
NK067(ju)002:3030: yan lag lnga la byed pa po dang rgyal ba
NK067(ju)002:3031: / rigs bzhi / mig rna ba sna lce'i g.yas kyi cha la nang sems bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3032: g.yon gyi cha la phyi sems bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3033: rkang lag gi mthil bzhi la sgo ba bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3034: yum gyi gnas de rnams su de dag gi yum rnams bsgom /
NK067(ju)002:3035: yab kyi mtshog ma sogs gnas drug tu thub drug bsgom /
NK067(ju)002:3036: de rnams la thabs lha bzhi bcu zhes bshad /
NK067(ju)002:3037: de rnams la shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu /
NK067(ju)002:3038: thabs lha bzhi bcu la sku gsung thugs byin rlabs kyi lha gsum re /
NK067(ju)002:3039: thabs lha dang byin rlabs kyi lha gnyis la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga re ste brgyad brgya /
NK067(ju)002:3040: kun dril bas stong phrag gcig go //
NK067(ju)002:3043: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gi //
NK067(ju)002:3044: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin te //
NK067(ju)002:3047: mi bskyod pa la ji ltar bsgoms pa de bzhin rgyal ba rigs bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3050: sgo ba bzhi ste yab yum so bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3051: thub drug de rnams re re la yang de ltar bsgoms pas nyi khri bzhi stong la bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3054: de la sogs te bsam mi khyab //
NK067(ju)002:3056: de ltar mi bskyod pa gtso bor byas pa'i dbus
NK067(ju)002:3057: kyi dkyil 'khor la yan lag gi lha bsgoms pa
NK067(ju)002:3058: de bzhin shar gyi glo 'bur la rnam snang gtso
NK067(ju)002:3059: bor byas te dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsgom pa
NK067(ju)002:3060: sogs rigs 'gre bas bsam gyis mi khyab par spro
NK067(ju)002:3061: ba'o // gnyis pa khro bo la /
NK067(ju)002:3063: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu /
NK067(ju)002:3064: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3065: dang po ni gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka'i yan lag lngar khrag 'thung yab lnga /
NK067(ju)002:3066: yum badz+ra kro d+h+ai'i yan lag lnga la yum lnga /
NK067(ju)002:3067: yab kyi dbang rten gyi nang rtsar gnas ma brgyad /
NK067(ju)002:3069: mthil bzhi la sgo ba bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3070: sgal tshigs nyer brgyad la dbang mo nyer brgyad de thabs lha nga brgyad /
NK067(ju)002:3071: de rnams la shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems
NK067(ju)002:3072: dpa' re re dang byin rlabs kyi lha gsum te
NK067(ju)002:3073: / byin rlabs dang thabs lha gnyis re re la dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga re /
NK067(ju)002:3074: kun dril bas stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu la bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3075: gnyis pa khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum bcu sngar ltar dang /
NK067(ju)002:3076: gnas yul sgo skyong dbang mo rnams kyi mgo'i g.yas dang /
NK067(ju)002:3077: rkang lag gi g.yas kyi mdun rgyab rnams la yab rnams bsgom /
NK067(ju)002:3078: mgo'i g.yon dang rkang lag g.yon gyi mdun rgyab rnams
NK067(ju)002:3079: la yum rnams bsgoms pas lha re re la'ang stong
NK067(ju)002:3080: bzhi brgya lnga bcu re bsgoms pas bdun khri drug
NK067(ju)002:3081: stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu la bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3082: gsum pa bsam yas lhun grub khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la bslab pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3083: sngar zhi ba'i skabs dang mtshungs so //
NK067(ju)002:3084: bzhi pa zhal phyag spro ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3085: zhi khro gnyis la rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum ste /
NK067(ju)002:3086: zhi ba la rgyas par bshad rgyud rdo rje nas
NK067(ju)002:3087: thub drug dang yum rnams ma gtogs zhal gsum phyag
NK067(ju)002:3088: drug / 'bring po rigs lnga tsam mam gtso bo zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK067(ju)002:3089: bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3090: khro bo la rgyas par gtso bo la dbu phyag grangs med /
