NK067(ju)002:3091: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad sogs bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)002:3092: da lta rgyas par rigs lnga he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK067(ju)002:3093: 'bring por gtso bo zhal gsum phyag drug pa bsdus pa thams cad zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3094: de ltar phyag rgya spros bcas kyi lam bsgoms pas
NK067(ju)002:3095: byis pa de nar son nas 'dod pas gdung ba
NK067(ju)002:3096: don du gnyer nas chung ma len pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3097: sgo gsum gyi nus pa 'phel bas rang rigs kyi
NK067(ju)002:3098: bya ba la dbang bsgyur ba'i bag chags dag par
NK067(ju)002:3099: 1byed / yar sangs rgyas sprul skus gdul bya rnams
NK067(ju)002:3100: byang chub la 'god pa'i rigs kyi nus pa gsos
NK067(ju)002:3102: bar du phyag rgya spros bcas de bsgoms pas zung
NK067(ju)002:3103: 'jug gi lha sku'i rtsal snang gong 'phel du 'char
NK067(ju)002:3104: ba'i gzhi bting bas lam gong ma'i smin 3byed du
NK067(ju)002:3105: 'gro // gsum pa skye ba'i rim pa tha ma sbyong byed tshom bu tshogs sgrub la gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3106: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK067(ju)002:3107: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba /
NK067(ju)002:3108: 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus ba stan pa gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3109: dang po rtsa rgyud le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3110: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK067(ju)002:3114: de la gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3116: bskor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa //
NK067(ju)002:3118: bdag dbang bar chad med pa'i gnas su tshogs kyi khang pa steng 'og gnyis bskor khang bcas dang /
NK067(ju)002:3119: bar khang du tshom bu gang bsgom pa'i dkyil 'khor bris pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3120: gnyis pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3122: sgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes grangs ni //
NK067(ju)002:3123: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK067(ju)002:3126: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad nas brtsam //
NK067(ju)002:3127: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK067(ju)002:3128: byang chub spyad pa spyod phyir dang //
NK067(ju)002:3129: gsang mchog dngos grub myur ba'i phyir //
NK067(ju)002:3130: gza' skar shis pa blang bar bya //
NK067(ju)002:3132: gsum pa yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3134: rkyen bzlog sman gyi yo byad /
NK067(ju)002:3135: sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad /
NK067(ju)002:3136: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad rnams bsags la cha
NK067(ju)002:3137: gsum du bgos pa'i cha gcig sngon du mchod sbyin
NK067(ju)002:3138: bya / cha gcig mjug gi dga' ston du bzhag /
NK067(ju)002:3139: cha gcig byin gyis brlabsa la sgrub pa'i cha rkyen bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:3140: bzhi pa sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:3141: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3143: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK067(ju)002:3144: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK067(ju)002:3146: rnal 'byor mthar ldan shin tu bsten //
NK067(ju)002:3148: gnyis pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3150: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK067(ju)002:3151: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK067(ju)002:3152: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK067(ju)002:3154: spyir yon tan drug ldan gyi 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)002:3155: bye brag slob dpon dang dgongs pa mnyam pa'i rdo rje rgyal tshab /
NK067(ju)002:3156: skad gdangs che zhing las khrigs la mkhas pa'i karma gdangs chen /
NK067(ju)002:3157: sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa'i las bzhi'i gzungs ma /
NK067(ju)002:3158: mig rnon gyis mi ma yin mthong ldog nus pa'i rdo rje spyan pa /
NK067(ju)002:3159: drod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje bya rog /
NK067(ju)002:3160: sgrol ba'i las la mkhas pa'i king ka ra /
NK067(ju)002:3161: g.yos la mkhas pa'i rdo rje byan po /
NK067(ju)002:3162: phyi nang gi brda sbyor la mkhas pa'i rdul phyag skyes bu rnams te /
NK067(ju)002:3163: tshom bu dang 'brel ba'i 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3164: lnga pa sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3166: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK067(ju)002:3168: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK067(ju)002:3169: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)002:3173: phyag rgya gcig pa phra rags gnyis //
NK067(ju)002:3174: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi cho ga lnga ni rdzogs pa ste brtan pa thob par byas shing /
NK067(ju)002:3180: sbyor sgrol te sgrub rdzas kyi yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3181: sngags kyi yan lag lnga ni /
NK067(ju)002:3183: snying gar ye shes sems bsgom snying gar nyi zla'i dkyil //
NK067(ju)002:3184: dam tshig phyag rgya bzhag ste de steng yig 'bru bzhag /
NK067(ju)002:3185: zlos tshe spro bsdus bzlas pa sngags kyi yan lag yin //
NK067(ju)002:3187: de ltar sgrub pa'i cha rkyen cho ga thams cad chad lhag med par sgrub pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3188: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3190: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK067(ju)002:3191: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK067(ju)002:3192: zhes pas lam dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3193: sgrub pa'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi /
NK067(ju)002:3194: sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3195: dang po ni lam bgrod tshul rim gyis pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK067(ju)002:3196: lta ba rtogs nas stong chen dang kun ting la gnas pa bsnyen pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3197: phyag rgya gcig spros ni nye bsnyen dang /
NK067(ju)002:3198: tshogs sgrub ni sgrub pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3199: de 'bras mthong lam thob ma rag pa ni sgrub pa chen po /
NK067(ju)002:3201: bar chad med pa'i lam pa tshogs sgrub pa'i dbang
NK067(ju)002:3202: du byas pa'i bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ni tshogs
NK067(ju)002:3204: rgyud le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3205: rdo rje'i rigs su thams cad dkyil //
NK067(ju)002:3207: gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK067(ju)002:3208: zhes pa'i bar gyis tshom bu gcig pa bsgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK067(ju)002:3209: yang na sku gsung thugs nyid de //
NK067(ju)002:3211: rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas //
NK067(ju)002:3212: zhes pa'i bar gyi tshom bu gsum pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3213: sngags 'chang dngos grub yang dag ni //
NK067(ju)002:3215: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK067(ju)002:3216: zhes pa'i bar gyi tshom bu lnga pa sgrub pa'i
NK067(ju)002:3217: thabs rnams bstan cing tshom bu de gsum gang rung
NK067(ju)002:3220: rnal 'byor thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK067(ju)002:3222: ting 'dzin yan lag so sor gsal //
NK067(ju)002:3223: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan pa ltar /
NK067(ju)002:3224: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gnas so sor rnal 'byor pho mo brang sprad nas 'dug ste /
NK067(ju)002:3225: lha yab yum so sor nga rgyal brtan po la
NK067(ju)002:3226: sems rtse gcig pas rim pa shoms dang 'brel ba'i
NK067(ju)002:3227: nub dang po 'go 'dzin gyi tshul du bya ba
NK067(ju)002:3228: bsnyen pa / ji tsam bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs phyed tshun chad nye bsnyen /
NK067(ju)002:3229: de gnyis la 'od zer dkar po'i 'phro 'dus snod dag par byed pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3230: zhag tha ma ma gtogs phyed phan chad 'od zer
NK067(ju)002:3231: dmar po'i 'phro 'dus dngos grub bskul zhing bsdus bas
NK067(ju)002:3232: bcud dag par byed pa sgrub pa /
NK067(ju)002:3233: zhag tha ma 'od zer mthing ga tshur bsdus nas
NK067(ju)002:3234: rgyud dag par byed pa'i sgo nas srod kyi cha
NK067(ju)002:3235: la lha las dngos grub blang /
NK067(ju)002:3236: nam gung ta na ste k+aa li'i mdzad spyod kyis sgrol ba las dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3238: zhing gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK067(ju)002:3240: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK067(ju)002:3241: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan pa bzhin dang /
NK067(ju)002:3242: tho rangs yum dang sbyor ba'i ga na ste /
NK067(ju)002:3243: +aa li'i mdzad spyod kyis yum gyi mkha' las dngos grub len pa sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK067(ju)002:3245: lha mo klu mo rigs ngan mo //
NK067(ju)002:3247: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK067(ju)002:3248: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan pa ltar ro //
NK067(ju)002:3249: gsum pa sgrub pa chen po'i sa der dngos grub
NK067(ju)002:3250: yum gyi mkha' las blang ba'i dbang du byas te
NK067(ju)002:3251: sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis nyams
NK067(ju)002:3252: su blang ba ni sngar thabs lam cig car ba'i
NK067(ju)002:3253: skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:3254: gsum pa 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3255: de ltar zla ba drug spog chog dang bcas pas rig 'dzin gyi 'bras bu 'grub ste /
NK067(ju)002:3256: 'di bskyed rim gyi lam yin pas thun mong gi
NK067(ju)002:3257: dngos grub la las rgya dang ye rgya'i khyad par
NK067(ju)002:3259: gzugs kyi rig 'dzin gang rigs la sbyor bas so //
NK067(ju)002:3260: lam 'dis 'khor ba'i bag chags gang dag na bskyed
NK067(ju)002:3261: pa'i rim pa gsum pa ste de nas byis pa
NK067(ju)002:3262: de rgan po rnams dang blo gros mnyam pas khe
NK067(ju)002:3263: drag dang / spyad ris la sogs kyi bag chags dag par 1byed /
NK067(ju)002:3264: yar sangs rgyas rnams mchod sprin mtha' yas pa'i rol
NK067(ju)002:3265: mo la dgyes dgur spyod pa'i rigs kyi nus pa
NK067(ju)002:3267: bar du tshogs sgrub kyi lam de bsgom pas bde stong gi lha sku 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:3268: mchog gi 'bras bu la myur du sbyor ba'i gzhi 'ding bas lam gong ma'i smin 3byed du 'gro /
NK067(ju)002:3269: gnyis pa lam gyi gzhung shing rdzogs rim ltar bshad na /
NK067(ju)002:3270: rgyud le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3272: zhes pas rang rig pa ye nas rang bzhin gyis
NK067(ju)002:3273: rnam par dag pa'i dkyil 'khor lhag pa bden pa
NK067(ju)002:3274: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba lta ba'i ngo
NK067(ju)002:3275: bo gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor de nyid gtan tshigs
NK067(ju)002:3276: rnams kyis gtan la phab pas yul med rang gsal
NK067(ju)002:3277: du rtogs pa ni grub mtha' /
NK067(ju)002:3278: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)002:3282: ye shes dgyes la mchod pa 'bul //
NK067(ju)002:3283: zhes pa'i bar gyis lam gyi rnal 'byor lnga bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3284: dang po stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK067(ju)002:3285: de yang lus can rnams 'chi ba'i tshe 'byung ba
NK067(ju)002:3286: lnga dkar dmar nag gsum rim par thim nas rnam
NK067(ju)002:3287: par mi rtog pa'i 'od gsal 'char te /
NK067(ju)002:3289: 'gro ba ma lus thams cad dag /
NK067(ju)002:3290: gnas pa'i stobs ni zad pa na //
NK067(ju)002:3291: 'dus pa lnga yi rim pa yi //
NK067(ju)002:3292: bag chags snyigs ma rang zad nas //
NK067(ju)002:3293: 'od gsal stong par snang bas na //
NK067(ju)002:3294: re dogs med pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:3296: de lam du khyer te de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam bsgom tshul yang /
NK067(ju)002:3297: lta bas gtan la 'bebs pa gzhir bzhag ste /
NK067(ju)002:3298: bsam gtan la tsher ma mi 'byung ba'i gnas su
NK067(ju)002:3299: lus gnad rnam par snang mdzad kyi chos bdun dang
NK067(ju)002:3300: ldan pas rig pa ma bcos pa'i ngang du so
NK067(ju)002:3301: mar 'jog pa rig pa spyi blugs dang /
NK067(ju)002:3302: sngar gyi thos bsam gyi lta ba dran par byas
NK067(ju)002:3303: nas de'i ngang 'jog pa mthong ba'i rjes la 'jog
NK067(ju)002:3304: pa ste / 'jog thabs gnyis po gang rung gis
NK067(ju)002:3305: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam
NK067(ju)002:3306: par 'jog pa nyin mo'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK067(ju)002:3307: mtshan mo'i gnyid mthug gi 'od gsal 'dzin pa'i man
NK067(ju)002:3308: ngag gnyis sbrel te nyin mtshan kha sbyor du nyams
NK067(ju)002:3309: su len pa'i sgo nas nyams lnga mthar phyin par
NK067(ju)002:3310: bslab pa'o // gnyis pa snying rje sgyu ma'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK067(ju)002:3311: sngar gyi 'chi kha'i 'od gsal ngos ma zin pa
NK067(ju)002:3312: las snang gsum 'byung lnga'i bgrod pa go bzlog gi
NK067(ju)002:3313: tshul du langs te bar do'i yid lus sgyu ma
NK067(ju)002:3316: bar ma sgyu ma'i lus thob pas //
NK067(ju)002:3317: ma spangs longs spyod rdzogs par bshad //
NK067(ju)002:3319: de lam du khyer nas de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam sgom tshul yang /
NK067(ju)002:3320: sngar gyi stong chen 'od gsal gyi ngang du sems 'gags pas /
NK067(ju)002:3325: dkar dmar nag gsum la sogs pa'i stong gzugs kyi snang ba shar ba na /
NK067(ju)002:3326: nyin gyi rnal 'byor srid pa'i snang ba de dang /
NK067(ju)002:3327: mtshan mo rmi lam gyi snang ba thams cad sgyu
NK067(ju)002:3328: ma chu zla ltar mthong ba la dmigs med kyi
NK067(ju)002:3329: snying rje ma 'gags par shar ba la goms shing
NK067(ju)002:3331: gsum pa phyag rgya gcig pa'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK067(ju)002:3332: skye ba'i rim pa dang po'i bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam ste /
NK067(ju)002:3333: snang ba ris med la snying rje chen po'i 'phen
NK067(ju)002:3334: pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyis chu dwangs pa la
NK067(ju)002:3335: gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar zhu bde dang mtshungs ldan
NK067(ju)002:3336: du gyur pa'i lha sku phyag rgya gcig pas gang
NK067(ju)002:3337: shar gyi snang ba thams cad la rgyas thebs pa'o
NK067(ju)002:3338: // bzhi pa phyag rgya spros bcas ni /
NK067(ju)002:3339: skye ba'i rim pa bar ma'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyi de dang mthun pa'i lam ste /
NK067(ju)002:3340: sngar gyi lha snang de las ches cher 'phel bas
NK067(ju)002:3341: snang ba thams cad zung 'jug gi lha gtso 'khor
NK067(ju)002:3342: dang tshom bu'i rnam par mngon sum du spros te
NK067(ju)002:3343: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'char ba la goms par
NK067(ju)002:3344: byed pa'o // lnga pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub ni /
NK067(ju)002:3345: skye ba'i rim pa gsum pa'i bag chags sbyong ba'i phyir de dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam ste /
NK067(ju)002:3346: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung gi sgo
NK067(ju)002:3347: nas spros bcas bskyed rim dang phyogs mthun du sgrub
NK067(ju)002:3348: pa'am / spros med rnal 'byor pho mo gtso bo yab yum tshogs pa la brten pa'am /
NK067(ju)002:3349: shin tu spros med yab mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po dang /
NK067(ju)002:3350: yum rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid dang kha sbyor du sgrub pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3351: gang ltar yang blo rab 'bring tha gsum gyi dbye bas zla ba drug gam /
NK067(ju)002:3352: lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:3353: lo gcig zla ba bzhi rnams kyis nang gi mngon
NK067(ju)002:3354: byang lnga la brten nas zag med mthong lam rnam
NK067(ju)002:3355: gnyis gang rung la sbyor bar byed pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3357: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK067(ju)002:3358: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK067(ju)002:3359: dbang bsgyu rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK067(ju)002:3361: zhar la zag ldog yod med kyi mu bzhi ni /
NK067(ju)002:3362: de la zag ldog gnyis ka yod pa'i mu ni /
NK067(ju)002:3363: stong 1pa chen po snying rje sgyu ma 2phyag rgya gcig 3spros rnams te tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi'o //
NK067(ju)002:3364: zag pa yod la ldog ba med pa'i mu ni /
NK067(ju)002:3365: sbyor lam tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste /
NK067(ju)002:3366: spyod pa'i dus grangs nges pas zag med la dngos
NK067(ju)002:3367: su sbyor ba'i bar chad med lam yin pa'i phyir
NK067(ju)002:3368: ro // zag pa med la ldog pa yod pa'i mu ni /
NK067(ju)002:3369: dman lam sngon song gi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa
NK067(ju)002:3370: sngags kyi tshogs lam la gnas pa lta bu ste
NK067(ju)002:3371: / rang don la chags pas ldog par srid do //
NK067(ju)002:3372: spyir zag pa zhes pa ni mngon pa sogs las zag pa'i sgo drug bshad kyang /
NK067(ju)002:3373: 'dir zag pa'i gtso bo dang yan lag gnyis la /
NK067(ju)002:3374: gtso bo kun nas nyon mongs dang bcas pa'i las
NK067(ju)002:3375: kyis khams gsum 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams
NK067(ju)002:3378: yan lag ni lus rang dbang med par len pa skye gnas kyi zag pa /
NK067(ju)002:3379: khams bde mi bde rang dbang med par myong ba khams gyi zag pa /
NK067(ju)002:3380: rang dbang med par lus 'dor ba lus kyi zag pa gsum mo //
NK067(ju)002:3381: gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la'ang gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:3383: 'di nyid kyi le'u bcu gnyis pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3384: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK067(ju)002:3387: zhes pa'i bar gyis yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i 'bras bu bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3392: a li k+aa li'i yo byad la spyad pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK067(ju)002:3393: gnyis pa lam 'gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi ni /
NK067(ju)002:3395: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi //
NK067(ju)002:3397: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK067(ju)002:3400: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK067(ju)002:3402: thim pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3403: zhes pa'i bar gyis mthong lam tshe dbang nas rim gyis phyag chen dang /
NK067(ju)002:3404: lhun grub nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor zhing /
NK067(ju)002:3405: thod rgal ba tshe dbang nas lhun grub rig 'dzin nam /
NK067(ju)002:3406: shin tu blo chen po lam gzhan ma brgyud par
NK067(ju)002:3407: sku lnga lhun grub rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par
NK067(ju)002:3408: byed pa dang / 'bras dus kyi sku dang ye shes zhing khams thams cad bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3409: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin gyi //
NK067(ju)002:3411: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK067(ju)002:3412: zhes pa'i bar gyis 'bad rtsol med pa'i phrin las bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3413: shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK067(ju)002:3415: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK067(ju)002:3416: ces pa'i bar gyi ye shes rol pa sgyu ma lta bu'i phrin las don mdzad pa bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3417: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK067(ju)002:3419: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK067(ju)002:3420: zhes pa'i bar gyis sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye shes spros mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing /
NK067(ju)002:3421: de nyid sems can la thugs rje'i gzigs pa yul
NK067(ju)002:3422: dbyer med par 'brel ba'i ji lta ba dang ji
NK067(ju)002:3423: snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi tshul rnams bstan no
NK067(ju)002:3424: // de ltar zag ldog gnyis ka med pa'i mthong
NK067(ju)002:3425: sgom mthar lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rig 'dzin bzhi
NK067(ju)002:3426: // ste / mthong lam pa la blo yi nus
NK067(ju)002:3427: stobs che chung gis 'byung ba snyigs rnam smin gyi
NK067(ju)002:3428: ma'i lus ye shes kyi mes sbyong bar mi nus
NK067(ju)002:3430: sbyang bar nus pa skye 'jig med pa dwangs ma'i
NK067(ju)002:3431: lus su gyur pa lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK067(ju)002:3433: de la rnam smin rig 'dzin lus rnam smin gyi
NK067(ju)002:3434: lus phung po dang ma bral bar yid 'od gsal
NK067(ju)002:3436: lus rgya bral ma thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor nges pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3437: mdzad spyod bkod pa dkyil 'khor la brten nas bdag don tshogs gnyis rdzogs par mdzad /
NK067(ju)002:3438: gzhan don phrin las bzhi mthar phyin par mdzad /
NK067(ju)002:3439: zag med lha yi spyan sogs mngon shes kyi yon tan dang ldan /
NK067(ju)002:3440: gling bzhi pa tsam du sku dngos kyis 'gro don mdzad /
NK067(ju)002:3441: sprul gzugs ston tshul tshe dbang rig 'dzin dang cha 'dra ba tsam mo //
NK067(ju)002:3442: mthong lam tshe dbang rig 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)002:3443: lus sems gnyis ka 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin
NK067(ju)002:3444: zhing phra yang la sogs 'ja' lus kyi yon tan
NK067(ju)002:3445: khyad par can dang ldan pa'i rdo rje'i lus te
NK067(ju)002:3447: sman gyi bcud len la brten pa /
NK067(ju)002:3448: thig le dbab bzung la brten pa /
NK067(ju)002:3449: sgron ma rlung gi 'khor lo la brten pa /
NK067(ju)002:3450: lam mchog yogs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang dang bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:3452: sa dang po'i rtogs pa khyad par can rgyud la skyes pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3453: mdzad spyod ni bdag don du kun 'gro'i dri ma sbyang /
NK067(ju)002:3455: phrin las bzhi sogs kyi 'gro don mdzad cing /
NK067(ju)002:3457: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi //
NK067(ju)002:3458: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK067(ju)002:3459: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK067(ju)002:3461: mngon shes ni dbang shes nyer lngas gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgyar dus gcig 'gro don mdzad pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3462: sgom lam phyag chen rig 'dzin ni /
NK067(ju)002:3463: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku can te /
NK067(ju)002:3464: de la nang gses kyis dbye na /
NK067(ju)002:3465: sa gnyis pa nas lnga pa'i bar rdo rje'i rig 'dzin te /
NK067(ju)002:3466: rtogs pa'i ye shes rdo rje lta bus rang sa'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3467: sa drug pa sher phyin gtso bor spyod cing chos 'khor bskor ba'i phyir dang /
NK067(ju)002:3468: sa bdun pa'ang thabs la mkhas pa'i phyir /
NK067(ju)002:3469: de gnyis ka la 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin zhes bya /
NK067(ju)002:3470: sa brgyad par mi rtog pa'i ye shes la dbang bsgyur bas rin po che'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK067(ju)002:3471: sa dgu par ma chags pa'i zhing sbyong bas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin /
NK067(ju)002:3472: sa bcu bar phrin las phun sum tshogs pas 'gro
NK067(ju)002:3473: don mdzad pa'i phyir ral gri'i rig 'dzin zhes bya'o
NK067(ju)002:3474: // cha byas kyang zung 'jug gi lha sku mtshan dpe rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK067(ju)002:3475: bdag don lhan cig gnas pa'i dri ma sbyong /
NK067(ju)002:3476: gzhan don rngon pa dang smad 'tshong ma sogs gang 'dul gyi sprul gzugs ston /
NK067(ju)002:3477: mngon shes kyang dbang shes nyer lnga'i yon tan tshe dbang dang 'dra na'ang /
NK067(ju)002:3478: 'dir gsal brtan gyis khyad par du 'phags shing longs sku'i zhing dang mnyam par 'gro don mdzad do //
NK067(ju)002:3479: de ltar sa bcu'i rnam grol lam tshun chad sgom
NK067(ju)002:3480: lam phyag chen rig 'dzin du bsdus shing sa bcu'i
NK067(ju)002:3481: khyad par lam mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin ni
NK067(ju)002:3482: / sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang gi cha
NK067(ju)002:3483: lugs 'dzin pa drug pa'i rgyal tshab mdzad pa gsang
NK067(ju)002:3486: bdag don rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin te
NK067(ju)002:3487: nang gi mngon byang gis shes sgrib phra ba dang
NK067(ju)002:3488: snang gsum khu rdul sems gsum gyi dri ma sbyangs
NK067(ju)002:3489: / gzhan don rjes thob la sangs rgyas dang cha 'dra ba'i 'gro don mdzad /
NK067(ju)002:3490: sprul gzugs kyang mdzad pa bcu gnyis sogs mchog gi sprul sku dang phyogs mthun ston /
NK067(ju)002:3491: mngon shes kyang ji snyed mkhyen pa'i yul sangs rgyas
NK067(ju)002:3492: nyid dang cha 'dra bas nam mkha'i khyab tshad kyi
NK067(ju)002:3493: 'gro ba'i don ci rigs pa mdzad do //
NK067(ju)002:3494: zhar la rgyu'i theg pa'i 'phags pa rnams dang dgongs pa mnyam tshul dang /
NK067(ju)002:3495: sa yi mu tshod mthun tshul ni /
NK067(ju)002:3496: rnam smin rig 'dzin dang rgyu'i theg pa'i mthong lam
NK067(ju)002:3497: rab dga' la gnas pa'i sems dpa' gnyis dgongs pa
NK067(ju)002:3498: mnyam / gzhan pa tshe dbang sogs ni rgyu'i theg
NK067(ju)002:3499: pa'i sa dang po dang brgyad pa dang bcu pa
NK067(ju)002:3500: rnams dang lam gyi mu tshod mtshungs kyang /
NK067(ju)002:3501: dgongs pa rgyu'i theg pa'i sa brgyad pa dang tshe dbang /
NK067(ju)002:3503: mi slob pa'i sa kun tu 'od dang lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis dgongs pa mnyam mo //
NK067(ju)002:3504: da ni thod rgal 'byung mi 'byung gi mtshams ni /
NK067(ju)002:3505: rnam smin nas thod rgal du sbyor ba mi srid
NK067(ju)002:3506: de ngang gis blo chung bas stong nyid snying rje
NK067(ju)002:3507: dbyer med sgom mi nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:3508: gzhan du cig char pa ma yin pa'i lam pa
NK067(ju)002:3509: blo che ba 'ga' zhig phyag rgya gcig spros gnyis
NK067(ju)002:3511: tshe dbang nas lhun grub dang /
NK067(ju)002:3512: tshe dbang phyag chen gnyis nas sangs rgyas kyi sar
NK067(ju)002:3513: thod rgal lam gzhan bar nas bor te sbyor ba'ang
NK067(ju)002:3515: de dag la ngang gis blo che ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:3516: zung 'jug gi lam sgom pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3517: lam gzhan bar nas bor du yod pa ste thod rgal 'byung ba'i chos gsum tshang ba'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:3518: de ltar na tshogs sgrub nas thod rgal 'byung ngam snyam na mi 'byung ste /
NK067(ju)002:3519: zag med kyi lam gyi dbye sa dang 'du sa
NK067(ju)002:3520: mthong lam yin par gsungs pas lam gzhan bar nas
NK067(ju)002:3521: bor du med pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:3522: gsum pa gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud ni /
NK067(ju)002:3524: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK067(ju)002:3526: ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs pa'i //
NK067(ju)002:3527: zhes pa'i bar gyis sku lnga'i mtshan nyid bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3528: de tshe mi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK067(ju)002:3530: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:3531: zhes pa'i bar gyi sku ji ltar snang ba'i tshul bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3532: de tshe 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK067(ju)002:3534: sku yis chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK067(ju)002:3535: zhes pa'i bar gyis sku'i phrin las bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3536: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK067(ju)002:3538: bla med byang chub yang dag thob //
NK067(ju)002:3539: ces pa'i bar gyis 'khor gyi sgrib pa sbyangs nas grol tshul bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3540: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK067(ju)002:3541: longs sku zad med yid bzhin gter //
NK067(ju)002:3542: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK067(ju)002:3543: ces pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsum bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3544: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK067(ju)002:3546: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog ces pa'i bar
NK067(ju)002:3547: gyis sngags kyi mthar thug gi sa'i khyad par bstan
NK067(ju)002:3548: / skye 'chi med pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK067(ju)002:3550: de tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK067(ju)002:3551: zhes pa'i bar gyis 'bras bu'i sku lnga bstan to //
NK067(ju)002:3552: de yang sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK067(ju)002:3554: lhun grub ji bzhin mngon byas pa'ang //
NK067(ju)002:3555: btags pa tsam las gnyis med de //
NK067(ju)002:3556: de phyir la de brjod do //
NK067(ju)002:3558: sbyang gzhi rgyu'i rgyud bde gshegs snying po gdod nas
NK067(ju)002:3559: rang la rang chas su bzhugs pa 'dam gyi dbus
NK067(ju)002:3561: sbyang bya med snang glo bur dri ma nor bu sgrib byed kyi 'dam rdzab lta bu /
NK067(ju)002:3562: sbyong byed rim pa gnyis kyi lam bkru byed kyi chu dang 'dag rdzas bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:3564: lam gyi dri ma sbyangs pa las gzhi la yod
NK067(ju)002:3565: pa'i yon tan mngon du gyur pa mthar thug pa
NK067(ju)002:3566: ste / 'dam rdzab las grol ba'i nor bu las 'dod dgu'i char 'bebs pa bzhin no //
NK067(ju)002:3568: mchog gi go 'phang don du gnyer ba rnams /
NK067(ju)002:3569: bsod nams yongs su rdzogs pas na 'bras bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:3570: nam yang rgyun chad med pas rgyud do //
NK067(ju)002:3572: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga la lnga lngar dbye ba'i 'bras chos nyer lnga ste /
NK067(ju)002:3580: chos sku skye med don gyi gasung /
NK067(ju)002:3581: longs sku dgongs pa brda yi gasung /
NK067(ju)002:3582: sprul sku tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi gasung /
NK067(ju)002:3583: mngon byang gi rig pa byin rlabs kyi gasung /
NK067(ju)002:3584: dbyer med rdo rje'i gasung dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:3586: chos sku'i thugs chos dbyingsa ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:3587: longs sku'i thugs mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:3588: sprul sku'i thugs bya grub ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:3589: mngon byang gi sku'i thugs me long ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:3590: rdo rje'i sku'i thugs sor rtog ye shes lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:3592: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams /
NK067(ju)002:3593: rgya tshad bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK067(ju)002:3596: dgyes dgur spyod pa'i longs spyod dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:3598: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub dang lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:3601: mdzad pa phrin las gsum du 'du zhing /
NK067(ju)002:3602: dang po rten sku la gsum mam lnga ste /
NK067(ju)002:3603: chos sku ni dbyings spros bral nam mamkha'a lta bu'i
NK067(ju)002:3604: klong du thugs rje ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK067(ju)002:3606: longs sku ni de las shar ba'i thugs rje ye shes kyi sku'o //
NK067(ju)002:3607: sprul sku ni so so'i mos pa dang mthun par
NK067(ju)002:3608: gong gi sku gnyis kyi gzugs brnyan 'gro ba'i sems
NK067(ju)002:3609: gtsang mar shar ba yin la /
NK067(ju)002:3610: sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres pa'i cha nas mngon byang sku dang /
NK067(ju)002:3611: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje'i sku gnyis bsnan pas sku lnga'o //
NK067(ju)002:3612: skabs 'dir zur pa rnams chos longs sprul gsum sku mtshan nyid pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3613: gzhan gnyis rnam pa'i ldog cha dang /
NK067(ju)002:3614: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i sgo nas bzhag pa'i sku btags pa ba yin gsungs /
NK067(ju)002:3615: kun mkhyen klong chen pas ni /
NK067(ju)002:3616: chos sku mngon byang rdo rje'i sku gsum sangs rgyas
NK067(ju)002:3617: rang snang gi sku yin pas mtshan nyid pa yin
NK067(ju)002:3618: la / longs sprul gnyis gdul bya'i snang bas bsdus
NK067(ju)002:3619: pa'i sku btags pa pa'o gsungs pa la 'thad par
NK067(ju)002:3620: la / mngon / gnyis pa brten pa ye shes ni /
NK067(ju)002:3621: de ltar sku lnga mngon du gyur ba'i tshe tshogs brgyad gnas gyur gyi ye shes lnga ste /
NK067(ju)002:3622: kun gzhi 'byed pa med pa'i cha nas de nyid
NK067(ju)002:3623: gnas gyur pa ci yang mi dmigs pa spros pa
NK067(ju)002:3624: thams cad dang bral ba chos dbyings ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:3625: kun gzhi'i rnam shes gsal la mi rtog pa'i cha
NK067(ju)002:3626: nas de nyid gnas gyur pa me long ngos gnyis
NK067(ju)002:3627: pa ltar rang bzhin gyi chos thams cad gsal la
NK067(ju)002:3628: spu ris mi phyed pa me long lta bu'i ye
NK067(ju)002:3629: shes / nyon yid kyis phyi nang gi chos thams
NK067(ju)002:3630: cad la blang dor 'byed pa'i cha nas de nyid
NK067(ju)002:3631: gnas gyur pa 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam
NK067(ju)002:3632: pa nyid du gzigs pas srid zhi'i mtha' la mi
NK067(ju)002:3633: gnas pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK067(ju)002:3634: rnam shes drug 'gags ma thag par yid kyis dpyod
NK067(ju)002:3635: pa med par rtog pa'i cha de nyid gnas gyur
NK067(ju)002:3636: pa chos can ma lus sa ler gzigs pa sor
NK067(ju)002:3637: rtog ye shes / sgo nga'i rnam shes kyis bya
NK067(ju)002:3638: ba thams cad sgrub pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas
NK067(ju)002:3639: gyur pa 'gro don mdzad pa la thogs med kyi
NK067(ju)002:3640: phrin las bya grub ye shes so //
NK067(ju)002:3641: ye shes de gnyis su bsdu na /
NK067(ju)002:3642: zur pa rnams chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK067(ju)002:3643: gzhan bzhi po rten brten pa'i cha nas ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes su bzhed /
NK067(ju)002:3646: mnyam nyid ye shes gnyis gnas lugs gzigs pa'i cha nas ji lta ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:3649: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i cha nas ji snyed pa'i ye shes so //
NK067(ju)002:3650: zhes gsungs te ji ltar bshad kyang khyad par ma mchis so //
NK067(ju)002:3651: gsum pa mdzad pa phrin las ni /
NK067(ju)002:3652: de ltar nyon sgrib dang shes sgrib de'i bag chags
NK067(ju)002:3653: kyi yul snang gsum phra ba'i dri ma dang bcas
NK067(ju)002:3654: spangs pas spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3655: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pas shes bya thams cad
NK067(ju)002:3656: mngon sum du gzigs pas rtogs pa phun sum tshogs
NK067(ju)002:3657: pa ste / spangs rtogs mthar phyin pa'i sgo nas
NK067(ju)002:3658: gdul bya so so'i skal ba dang 'tshams par phrin
NK067(ju)002:3659: las kyi sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa dus las
NK067(ju)002:3661: gnyis pa lam gyi cha rkyen rgyud kyi dngos po bcu bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3662: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam tshig /
NK067(ju)002:3663: mchod sngags ting 'dzin phrin sgrub kyis //
NK067(ju)002:3664: gsang sngags rgyud kyi dbye ba bya //
NK067(ju)002:3675: 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag 10rgya ste bcu'o //
NK067(ju)002:3676: dang po lta ba la yang gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3677: ngo bo ni spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i cha nas dbu ma dang /
NK067(ju)002:3678: chos thams cad sems kyi rol rtsal tsam du 'du
NK067(ju)002:3679: ba'i cha nas sems tsam pa dang phyogs mtshungs kyang
NK067(ju)002:3680: / sngags kyi lta ba de dag las khyad par du 'phags te /
NK067(ju)002:3681: sems nyid gdod ma nas dkor bdun ngo bo nyid
NK067(ju)002:3682: du lhun gyis grub pa lhag pa don dam bden
NK067(ju)002:3683: pa dang / de'i rtsal snang snod bcud sku dang
NK067(ju)002:3684: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas 'khor
NK067(ju)002:3685: 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam pa nyid du rdzogs
NK067(ju)002:3686: pa lhag pa kun rdzob bden pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3687: de gnyis kyang phyogs su lhung ba ma yin par bden gnyis ngo bo dbyer med par gnas shing /
NK067(ju)002:3688: der 'dzin gyi bsam brjod las kyang 'das pas na
NK067(ju)002:3689: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK067(ju)002:3690: ba zhes tha snyad du btags te /
NK067(ju)002:3691: lhag pa zhes pa'ang khyad par 'phags pa'i don lhag par ston pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3692: phar phyin theg pa nas don dam par 'khor 'das
NK067(ju)002:3693: mnyam pa nyid du bzhed pa dang phyogs mtshungs kyang
NK067(ju)002:3694: 'dir ni kun rdzob tu'ang chos thams cad la mi
NK067(ju)002:3695: gnyis pa'i bsam brjod dang bral bas na rgyu'i theg
NK067(ju)002:3696: pa las khyad par du 'phags pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:3698: drish+ta'i sgra las lta ba la 'jug ste /
NK067(ju)002:3699: gnas lugs kyi don la de dang rjes su mthun pa'i shes rab kyi mig gis lta ba ste /
NK067(ju)002:3701: dbang rab la gong du bshad pa'i gtan tshigs bzhi po de rnams kyis rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:3702: dbang 'bring la rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i rtags la brten nas rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3703: 'di ltar ma dag pa'i 'jig rten 'di yang rang
NK067(ju)002:3704: gi rig pa ye shes lnga yi cho 'phrul yin
NK067(ju)002:3705: te / de'i rtags su sus kyang ma byas par
NK067(ju)002:3706: yul lnga 'byung ba lnga kha dog lnga sogs rang
NK067(ju)002:3708: 'bras bu'i rtags ni sems nyid la 'bras bu sku
NK067(ju)002:3709: dang ye shes rang chas su bzhugs pa'i mtshon byed
NK067(ju)002:3710: chu tshon sogs kyi dpe'i dkyil 'khor la brten nas
NK067(ju)002:3711: rtogs pa'o // dbang rtul la nye ring gnyis las
NK067(ju)002:3712: nye ba ni thos bsam gyis mi go ba'i rigs
NK067(ju)002:3713: la dmigs pa phra mo bstan pas nang gi rtsa
NK067(ju)002:3714: mdud grol nas gnas lugs rtogs pa klu sgrub kyi
NK067(ju)002:3715: slob ma sh+r+ai g+ai pa lta bu'o //
NK067(ju)002:3717: re zhig rtogs pa'i skal ba med pa rnams /
NK067(ju)002:3718: sgrib sbyang gi phyir bde bar gshegs pa'i mchod rten
NK067(ju)002:3719: la bskor ba byed pa dang mnyam du rten 'brel
NK067(ju)002:3720: snying po bzla zhing bsags sbyang la 'bad pas rtogs
NK067(ju)002:3721: par 'gyur ba rje tsong kha pa'i bla ma don
NK067(ju)002:3730: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK067(ju)002:3738: zhes pa'i bar rnams kyis bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3741: lam pa'i sgo gsum gyi bya bar gyur pa thabs
NK067(ju)002:3742: shes khyad par can gyi sgo nas zin par spyod
NK067(ju)002:3743: pa ste / de la mnyam gzhag rjes thob gnyis kyi /
NK067(ju)002:3744: dang po mnyam gzhag gi spyod pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3745: sngar bshad pa'i lam lnga rig 'dzin bzhi'i skabs kyi
NK067(ju)002:3746: so so'i ting nge 'dzin la rtse gcig tu gnas
NK067(ju)002:3747: pa de yin / rjes thob kyi spyod pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3748: 'og tu 'chad pa'i spyod pa gsum la sogs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3750: lta ba bdag med kyis zin pa'i shes rab dang /
NK067(ju)002:3751: thabs snying rje chen po zung 'jug gi sgo nas spyad pas sgo gsum dag par 'gyur pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3753: tsar+ya'i sgra las spyod pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3754: ta na dang ga na la sogs dus tshod dang 'brel bar tshul bzhin du spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3756: las dang po'i dus su bag yod kyi spyod pa dge sbyong gzhon nu'i spyod pa lta bu dang /
NK067(ju)002:3757: de nas cung zad brtan pa thob pas mnyam rjes
NK067(ju)002:3758: bsre nus pas rtogs pa rkyen thub tu spyod pa
NK067(ju)002:3759: smyon pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3760: brtan pa cher thob nas gzhan phan kho na la
NK067(ju)002:3761: bslabs pa rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi spyod pa lta
NK067(ju)002:3762: bu ste spyod tshul gsum mo //
NK067(ju)002:3763: bye brag thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3764: grol lam bag yod kyi spyod pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:3766: dang po lta ba gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus dad brtson gyi spyod pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:3767: dad pas thos bsam la zhugs nas le lo med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis mthar phyin par spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3768: shes rab dang mthun pa'i spyod pa stong pa chen po ste /
NK067(ju)002:3769: mnyam bzhag tu stong pa chen po bsgom zhing rjes thob tu de'i rang gdangs skyong ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3770: thabs dang mthun pa'i spyod pa snying rje sgyu ma ste /
NK067(ju)002:3771: mnyam bzhag tu snying rje sgyu ma lta bu bsgom zhing /
NK067(ju)002:3772: rjes thob spyod yul thams cad sgyu mar lta ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3773: phyogs gcig pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3775: mnyam bzhag tu phyag rgya gcig pa'i lha bsgom zhing rjes thob tu de nyid lam du khyer ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3776: spros pa dang bcas pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3777: mnyam rjes gnyis kar spyod yul thams cad du lha yi rang bzhin du bslab pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3779: tshogs sgrub kyi skabs te mnyam rjes gnyis kar yo byad lnga la ma chags par spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3780: rdzu 'phrul kyii spyod pa ni rig 'dzin bzhi'i gnas skabs su rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3781: sprul bsgyur gyis 'gro don mdzad pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3782: de ltar grol lam rim gyis pa'i spyod pa bdun bshad nas /
NK067(ju)002:3783: gcig car ba'i spyod pa ni chos thams cad la blang dor med pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3784: gsum pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:3785: rgyud 'di'i le'u dang pos zhi ba rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa sngar bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK067(ju)002:3787: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK067(ju)002:3789: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK067(ju)002:3790: ces pa'i bar gyis lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3792: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor sngar bshad pa ltar dang /
NK067(ju)002:3796: ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK067(ju)002:3797: zhes pa'i bar gyi lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK067(ju)002:3799: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK067(ju)002:3801: phyag rgya til 'bru tsam du bri //
NK067(ju)002:3802: sogs kyis zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan /
NK067(ju)002:3803: le'u bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pas tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3806: bkod pa lha'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par snang ba la 'jog /
NK067(ju)002:3811: de len cing thob par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK067(ju)002:3818: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdun du phye 8nas 'chad de /
NK067(ju)002:3819: dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la'ang /
NK067(ju)002:3821: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:3823: chos thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK067(ju)002:3825: rang rig pa'i ye shes mngon du gyur pas 'og
NK067(ju)002:3826: min gyi gnas su sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral
NK067(ju)002:3827: med pa'i dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3828: gnyis pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:3829: don dam pa'i gzugs brnyan kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor du shar ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3830: gsum pa lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:3832: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK067(ju)002:3833: tshon dang bri dang rnam pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:3834: rab gnas sbyin sreg dkyil 'khor du //
NK067(ju)002:3835: 'jug dang zhugs pa'i yon tan no //
NK067(ju)002:3837: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa la'ang //
NK067(ju)002:3839: rang gi mtshan nyid la brtag pa2 /
NK067(ju)002:3846: dang po gzhi la brtag pa'i /
NK067(ju)002:3849: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mang dang //
NK067(ju)002:3850: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing //
NK067(ju)002:3851: mnyam zhing 'o kha'i chu ltar dwangs //
NK067(ju)002:3852: nyi ma shin tu gnas pa ni //
NK067(ju)002:3853: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK067(ju)002:3855: bar gyi sgros la brtag pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3857: mtshams kyi dgra la brtag pa gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:3860: shar lho gzhol zhing 'jam pa la //
NK067(ju)002:3861: mtho dang 'dud pa nub byang yin //
NK067(ju)002:3865: gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse dang //
NK067(ju)002:3866: srin mo ngus pa'i mchil rjes dang //
NK067(ju)002:3867: gnod sbyin khros pa'i sbar rjes dang //
NK067(ju)002:3869: zhes pa shar lho nas g.yas skor gyi mtshams bzhir med pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3870: gsum pa 'og gi sa gzhi la brtag pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3872: lhun stug ri bo nags tshal ldan //
NK067(ju)002:3873: rab tu mnyam zhing snum bag can //
NK067(ju)002:3874: chu bo dbang gi phyogs nas 'bab //
NK067(ju)002:3875: cung zad kyis ni rlung nyung zhing //
NK067(ju)002:3876: me tog shing tshal bya skad brtag /
NK067(ju)002:3878: gnyis pas rang gi mtshan nyid brtag pa la bzang ngan gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:3881: bkra shis r+ts+wa dang me tog shing //
NK067(ju)002:3882: gnag dang kha dog ldan pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3887: thang ka sog le lta bu dang //
NK067(ju)002:3888: dma' dang bo ba'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK067(ju)002:3892: gram pa thal ba shing sol dang //
NK067(ju)002:3893: gyo mo rus pa gseg ma sogs //
NK067(ju)002:3896: ngan pa'i skyon med na slong bar bya ste /
NK067(ju)002:3897: de yang snang ba mi dang mi snang ba lha las bslang ba gnyis kyi /
NK067(ju)002:3898: dang po ni sa de'i bdag por gyur pa'i rgyal po sogs la rin byin te slong /
NK067(ju)002:3899: gnyis pa ni sangs rgyas dang sa yi lha mo la slong ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3900: bzhi pa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3901: pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i dbang mchog gi phur pa gdab pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3902: lnga pa sbyang ba la bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:3903: dang po las dang bya bas sbyong ba lto 'phye
NK067(ju)002:3904: brtags pa'i lto ba nas sa brkos la sa ro
NK067(ju)002:3905: rnams bsal te / dong chus bkang la gom pa
NK067(ju)002:3906: lnga bcu phyin nas tshur log ste bltas pas chu
NK067(ju)002:3907: rnams bsal te / ma brin bzang / de nyid du gter gzhug cing stegs bu bcas la /
NK067(ju)002:3909: 'bru lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NK067(ju)002:3910: snying po lnga dang sman sna lnga //
NK067(ju)002:3911: bdud rtsi lnga nyid rab mnyam la //
NK067(ju)002:3912: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK067(ju)002:3914: rdzas sum cus skyang nul bya /
NK067(ju)002:3915: gnyis pa mes sbyang ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3917: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyong ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3918: lag g.yas nyi dkyil la 'bru lnga bkod de /
NK067(ju)002:3919: +amo badz+ra ha na ha na kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK067(ju)002:3920: ces brjod pa dang bstun lan gsum gdab pas sbyong ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3921: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyong ba la gnyis te /
NK067(ju)002:3922: dang po stong pa nyid kyis sbyong ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3924: mtshan bcas kyis sbyong ba zhi khro gang byed kyi
NK067(ju)002:3925: dkyil 'khor 'byung ba rim brtsegs nas bzung ste gsal
NK067(ju)002:3926: gdab pa'o // drug pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3927: slob dpon rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs shing rdo rje'i
NK067(ju)002:3928: 'gros kyi dkyil 'khor bskor zhing shar sgo nas zhugs
NK067(ju)002:3929: pas dbus su 'dug pa la yum bzhi'i nga rgyal
NK067(ju)002:3930: 'dzin pa'i phyogs kyi slob ma bzhis /
NK067(ju)002:3931: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i /
NK067(ju)002:3932: sogs kyis gsol ba btab pas /
NK067(ju)002:3933: slob dpon gyis nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i rgyal ba rnams
NK067(ju)002:3934: kyi byin rlabs bsdus nas zhe sdang rdo rje'i nga
NK067(ju)002:3935: rgyal gyis 'bar ba'i sdang mig dang bcas te /
NK067(ju)002:3936: rdo rje 'dzin pa nyi ma sogs dang /
NK067(ju)002:3937: sum+b+ha'i sngags brjod cing rdo rje'i 'gros kyi bskor bas
NK067(ju)002:3938: sa gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlab
NK067(ju)002:3939: pa'o // bdun pa bsrung ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:3940: mtshon cha lngas mtshams gcod pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3942: lha yab yum rol pa'i 'od sa gzhi la thim
NK067(ju)002:3943: pas dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du gsal bar bsam
NK067(ju)002:3944: pa'o // gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshad ni /
NK067(ju)002:3946: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK067(ju)002:3947: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK067(ju)002:3948: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad //
NK067(ju)002:3950: yang na khru ni bcu drug dang //
NK067(ju)002:3951: nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lnga bya //
NK067(ju)002:3952: yang na rgyang grags dpag tshad dam //
NK067(ju)002:3956: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK067(ju)002:3958: phur bu srad bu tshon phye dang //
NK067(ju)002:3960: mkhas ldan chen pos bsgrims te bya //
NK067(ju)002:3961: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)002:3962: de'ang thig ces pa mi 'gyur ba'i don dang /
NK067(ju)002:3963: de la gying phur dang bskor phur gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:3964: srad bu la yang gnyis las /
NK067(ju)002:3965: ye thig zhi ba la pad+ma'i rgyus pa /
NK067(ju)002:3967: gnyis ka'i dam thig ni ras bal gtsang ma dpa' bo'i rin gyis nyos pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:3968: ye thig gi skud pa kha dog lnga tshan lnga bsgril ba'i nyer lnga'am lnga bsgril bya /
NK067(ju)002:3969: dam thig gi skud pa dgu bsgril lam gsum bsgril du bya'o //
NK067(ju)002:3970: gdab tshul kyang dam thig sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin du gsal btab nas /
NK067(ju)002:3971: de gsum re re la'ang ye shes lnga dang ldan
NK067(ju)002:3972: par bya phyir ye thig dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi'i nam
NK067(ju)002:3974: 'debs tshul kyang skor phyogs ma 'khrul bar gdab bo //
NK067(ju)002:3977: ma mthong rmongs la bstan phyir tshon //
NK067(ju)002:3979: 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du dgye //
NK067(ju)002:3983: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK067(ju)002:3984: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK067(ju)002:3985: gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi pa'i //
NK067(ju)002:3986: bar khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya //
NK067(ju)002:3988: dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang rung gis 'dul ba'i cho ga bzhin du bya ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:3989: drug pa rnam pa 'god pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:3991: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang 'god //
NK067(ju)002:3996: bdun pa rab gnas ni gsum las /
NK067(ju)002:3997: dang po yan lag gi rab gnas /
NK067(ju)002:4002: yan lag can gyi rab gnas /
NK067(ju)002:4005: lha sta gon gsum gyis bstan no //
NK067(ju)002:4006: dkyil 'khor rab gnas las khrigs dgu la sogs pa'i sgo nas so //
NK067(ju)002:4009: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan par //
NK067(ju)002:4010: zhal du gyur ba'i me bos la //
NK067(ju)002:4011: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK067(ju)002:4012: las bzhi'i mchod pa rab tu sbyin //
NK067(ju)002:4014: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:4016: thog mar slob dpon rang nyid zhugs rjes slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug par bya ste /
NK067(ju)002:4017: 'di nyid kyi le'u dgu pa las /
NK067(ju)002:4018: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK067(ju)002:4019: de nas slob ma 'jug par bya //
NK067(ju)002:4022: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK067(ju)002:4023: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK067(ju)002:4024: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK067(ju)002:4025: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang //
NK067(ju)002:4026: bsgrags dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK067(ju)002:4027: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK067(ju)002:4029: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK067(ju)002:4032: bcu pa zhugs pa'i yon tan ni //
NK067(ju)002:4034: byas te dad ldan rab bzhug na //
NK067(ju)002:4037: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:4039: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK067(ju)002:4041: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' sgom //
NK067(ju)002:4043: ting 'dzin rol mo mtha' yas mchog /
NK067(ju)002:4045: nye bar gyur ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK067(ju)002:4046: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan cing /
NK067(ju)002:4047: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rang rig ma bcos pa'i
NK067(ju)002:4048: don la mnyam par gzhag pa'i rtsal ye shes lngar
NK067(ju)002:4051: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK067(ju)002:4052: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK067(ju)002:4053: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK067(ju)002:4056: lnga pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:4057: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis las sngon 'gro las bdun
NK067(ju)002:4058: nas bzung go bgo lus srung gi bar ting nge
NK067(ju)002:4059: 'dzin gyi dmigs pa'i 'phro 'du mang pos lhag par
NK067(ju)002:4060: bsgrub dgos pas na lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK067(ju)002:4062: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:4063: phyi byang chub kyi sems rtsa dang rlung /
NK067(ju)002:4064: nang byang chub kyi sems thig le /
NK067(ju)002:4065: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ye shes dang gsum mo //
NK067(ju)002:4067: sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK067(ju)002:4068: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK067(ju)002:4069: srog shing gsum dang 'khor lo bzhi //
NK067(ju)002:4070: zhes rtsa dang rlung la sbyang gzhi ye shes kyi rlung dang /
NK067(ju)002:4071: sbyang bya las kyi rlung gnyis /
NK067(ju)002:4072: las rlung la rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus
NK067(ju)002:4073: pa'i rlung bcu snar rgyu ba'i rlung dang bcas pa'o
NK067(ju)002:4075: snying ga na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le sogs ye shes kyi thig le dang /
NK067(ju)002:4076: rnam shes kyi thig le snyigs ma dang bcas pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:4078: steng 'og gi sgo la brten nas bde chen gyi ye shes bskyed pa'o //
NK067(ju)002:4079: bdun pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK067(ju)002:4080: zhi khro gnyis ka la tshom bu gcig gsum lnga
NK067(ju)002:4081: pa gsum po gang rung la brten pa gong du
NK067(ju)002:4084: le'u dgu pa las phan dbang gang du bskur ba'i
NK067(ju)002:4085: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa gong
NK067(ju)002:4086: du song nas / gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK067(ju)002:4087: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK067(ju)002:4089: sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya //
NK067(ju)002:4091: yang na thal mo rab bsnol la //
NK067(ju)002:4093: mkhas pas cho ga ji bzhin bya //
NK067(ju)002:4095: sen zlum tsam gyi nyi zla la //
NK067(ju)002:4097: phyag rgya til 'bru tsam du bri //
NK067(ju)002:4098: zhes pa'i bar rnams kyis bstan /
NK067(ju)002:4101: rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi las /
NK067(ju)002:4103: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu gdod nas rang chas su bzhugs pa'i chos nyid do //
NK067(ju)002:4104: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni rab gnas dang ldan pa'i dbang rdzas rnams so //
NK067(ju)002:4106: phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur rung ba'i snod
NK067(ju)002:4107: ldan slob ma rgyu'i rkyen dbang gsum bskur nus pa'i
NK067(ju)002:4108: slob dpon tshad ldan bdag po'i rkyen /
NK067(ju)002:4109: rdzas sngags ting nge 'dzin gsum 'dzom pa'i nus pa khyad par can dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK067(ju)002:4110: dbang snga ma snga mas go phye nas phyi ma
NK067(ju)002:4111: phyi ma 'byung ba de ma thag pa'i rkyen no
NK067(ju)002:4112: // de ltar rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi tshogs pa
NK067(ju)002:4113: la brten nas go 'phang gi ye shes rgyud la
NK067(ju)002:4114: 'jog pa'i las kyis thar ba'i myu gu mngon du
NK067(ju)002:4115: // bskyed pa'am / skye nges kyi nus rung du smin par byed pa ni dbang gi ngo bo'o //
NK067(ju)002:4118: mngon par gtor ba'am blugs pa ste /
NK067(ju)002:4119: dbang gis sgo gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud pa'i cha nas mngon par gtor ba dang /
NK067(ju)002:4120: 'bras bu ye shes kyi nus pa rgyud la 'jog
NK067(ju)002:4121: pa'i cha nas mngon par blugs pa'i don gyis na
NK067(ju)002:4123: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK067(ju)002:4124: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK067(ju)002:4126: yang na snod kyi dbang gi bzhi ste /
NK067(ju)002:4128: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK067(ju)002:4129: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK067(ju)002:4130: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK067(ju)002:4131: snying rjes chud ma zos par gzung //
NK067(ju)002:4133: dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu ni /
NK067(ju)002:4134: le'u bcu pa'i phan dbang gi 'khrugs sdeb ni /
NK067(ju)002:4135: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK067(ju)002:4136: bum pa con pan phreng ba ste //
NK067(ju)002:4137: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK067(ju)002:4138: bza' btung dbang rnams rim bzhin bskur //
NK067(ju)002:4142: nyan byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK067(ju)002:4144: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa spyod //
NK067(ju)002:4145: ces pa'i bar gyis so so'i bsam rgyud dang bsgrags tshig bcas bstan /
NK067(ju)002:4146: de la lnga ste bdag don nus pa la nyan pa'i dbang dang lha sgom pa'i dbang /
NK067(ju)002:4147: gzhan don nus pa la 'chad pa dang phrin las kyi dbang /
NK067(ju)002:4148: gnyis ka'i don nus pa la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:4151: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las /
NK067(ju)002:4153: rtse nas bstim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK067(ju)002:4154: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK067(ju)002:4157: dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang gsum po spyod rigs mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la bskur ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:4159: nus dbang gis sa bon nus ldan du smin /
NK067(ju)002:4160: gsang dbang gis dbang don gyi ye shes rgyud la myong /
NK067(ju)002:4161: sher dbang gis de kho na nyid rgyud la brtan par byed /
NK067(ju)002:4162: bde ba chen po'i dbang gis mchog gi dngos grub thob par byed do //
NK067(ju)002:4165: phyi dbang lus la bskur ba ste //
NK067(ju)002:4166: khyad par snying po dbu rgyan bum //
NK067(ju)002:4167: gdugs dang cod pan phreng ba mgo //
NK067(ju)002:4168: go cha lus te rgyal mtshan lag /
NK067(ju)002:4169: bza' btung ngag gi lam du'o //
NK067(ju)002:4170: phyag rgya spyi bo'am snying ga ste //
NK067(ju)002:4174: rdzas ni glegs bam rgya gram dang //
NK067(ju)002:4175: 'khor lo phreng ba rdo rje dril //
NK067(ju)002:4176: 'byung ldan don yod snang mtha' yas //
NK067(ju)002:4177: yi dam rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan //
NK067(ju)002:4181: rdzas ni skabs kyi phyag rgya ma //
NK067(ju)002:4186: sems kyi dkyil nas drangs pa'i chu //
NK067(ju)002:4187: khyod kyi lce la bzhag pa 'di //
NK067(ju)002:4188: snying gi dkyil du bzung bar byos //
NK067(ju)002:4192: rno la ngar btags nus pa bzhin //
NK067(ju)002:4193: nus pa skyes pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK067(ju)002:4195: dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK067(ju)002:4197: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK067(ju)002:4198: dbang rnams thob par ma byas la //
NK067(ju)002:4199: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa ni //
NK067(ju)002:4204: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK067(ju)002:4205: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:4206: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK067(ju)002:4207: mtho ris thar ba'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK067(ju)002:4209: dbang bskur zhus pa'i yon 'bul ba'i tshul le'u dgu pa las /
NK067(ju)002:4210: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK067(ju)002:4212: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //

NK067(ju)002:4214: lnga pa mi 'da' ba dam tshig ni /

NK067(ju)002:4219: ces pa'i bar gyi shes rab chen pos zin pa'i tshul dang /
NK067(ju)002:4224: nyams na bskang tshul rnams bstan cing /
NK067(ju)002:4227: gang bsrung bya'i don khyad par can rtsa ba dang
NK067(ju)002:4228: yan lag gi dam tshig rnams las nam yang mi
NK067(ju)002:4229: 'da' bar sdom byed kyi bsam pa rgyun chags pa

NK067(ju)002:4257: dbyer med rtogs goms kyi sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung
NK067(ju)002:4258: thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:4259: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK067(ju)002:4261: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang /
NK067(ju)002:4262: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud dgrol //
NK067(ju)002:4263: man ngag lung gi slob dpon drug /
NK067(ju)002:4264: ces pa ltar drug po bkur thabs drug gi sgo nas bskur dgos te /
NK067(ju)002:4266: yum la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //

NK067(ju)002:4268: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul gyis te //
NK067(ju)002:4270: khyad par dbang bskur rgyud bshad man ngag gnang ba

NK067(ju)002:4273: gsum pa sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi rgyun mi bcad pa ni /

NK067(ju)002:4275: nyi mtshan thun drug tu phye ba'i dus drug dang /
NK067(ju)002:4276: 'bring gis zla ba gcig la dus drug gam bzhir dbye ba /
NK067(ju)002:4277: tha mas zla re'am ra ba'i dus tsam la brtson dgos pa yin te /
NK067(ju)002:4279: rab kyis chu bo'i gzhung bzhin nam //
NK067(ju)002:4280: nyin gsum mtshan gsum gnyis gcig tu //
NK067(ju)002:4281: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzla //
NK067(ju)002:4282: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK067(ju)002:4283: dus bzhi'i bar du mi bcad cing //
NK067(ju)002:4284: tha ma bya ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK067(ju)002:4285: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK067(ju)002:4286: brtson pas 'bad de mi byed na //
NK067(ju)002:4287: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK067(ju)002:4288: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin du //

NK067(ju)002:4293: ring ba'i mched sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la zhugs so cog /

NK067(ju)002:4296: dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus pa ma gcig gi spun lta bur byams par bya ba'o //
NK067(ju)002:4297: lnga pa gsang ba mi smra ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK067(ju)002:4299: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK067(ju)002:4300: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK067(ju)002:4302: zhes gsang ba'i yul bstan nas /
NK067(ju)002:4307: gsang bar gnyer gtad pa dang bcu las /
NK067(ju)002:4310: lta zab spyod pa barlang po dang //
NK067(ju)002:4311: lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags gsang //
NK067(ju)002:4312: zhes gnas skabs thams cad gsang dgos pa'o //

NK067(ju)002:4335: log pa'i dug lnga yang mi spang ste /
NK067(ju)002:4336: spang bya'i rang bzhin ma sgrub pas smig rgyu la chu rags mi dgos pa bzhin no //

NK067(ju)002:4347: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye //

NK067(ju)002:4351: bas brgya lnga bcu sngar gyi bcu dang bsdoms pas

NK067(ju)002:4353: dang po bla med mi spang ba la sum cur dbye ba ni /
NK067(ju)002:4355: byang chub sems ni bla med lha //
